(36, 4, 29, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-04-28', '2056', 'Communication Manager', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Standard Vertical Communication', 'Major', '23/04 MD received an email to notify him there has been no diesel for two weeks. Crucial information that was long overdue. which raises the question\n1. How is it possible to take two full weeks before raising it or getting a solution\n2. How were the tasks accomplished with no diesel\n3. Do we have the right staff\n4. And finally, its quite clear someone is not doing his job', 'closed', '2021-06-09', NULL, '2021-07-05', '2021-07-16', '2021-06-21', 'This was addressed by having a second supplier for fuel and weekly sharing of stock reports and maintenance of minimum stock of 800ltr', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-04-28 11:15:56', '2021-07-23 16:04:36'),
(37, 4, 16, NULL, 23, 3, NULL, '2021-04-30', '8328', 'Communication Manager', 'Human resource manager', 'Head Office', 'HR', 'Electronic Employee sheet', 'Major', 'Nyongoro: SMP Stephen Obonyo noticed that the mail concerning the sheet was first send without the link. He then felt that there were not enough clear explanations on how to handle the matter.', 'closed', '2021-05-20', NULL, '2021-06-08', '2021-06-09', '2021-06-04', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 07:18:04', '2021-06-08 15:04:15'),
(38, 3, 8, NULL, 8, 18, NULL, '2021-04-30', '6546', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'BGF Audit 2020; Auditor Joseph Masambo', 'Major', '7 Forks: Destruction of the trees by the domestic animals; Farmers are not taking care of their livestock especially the goats which sneak into the farms and devour the Mukau trees. This has led to losses of many trees.', 'closed', '2021-05-06', NULL, '2021-05-25', '2021-12-31', '2021-05-23', '1. Emphasis is to work with groups and implement activities that shall boost ownership of the program by the farmers. E.g farmer group competition and satellite nurseries.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 07:21:25', '2022-08-10 16:16:13'),
(39, 3, 8, NULL, 8, 18, NULL, '2021-04-30', '3305', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'BGF Audit 2020; Auditor Joseph Masambo', 'Major', '7 Forks: Unpruned trees. trees not pruned according to the work instructions', 'closed', '2021-05-06', NULL, '2021-06-05', '2021-06-30', '2021-06-03', '1. Give time frames for farmers to prune after the trainings are done.\n2. Immediate follow up through groups to ensure that farmers have pruned.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 07:24:18', '2021-07-05 13:58:26'),
(40, 4, 5, NULL, 5, 2, NULL, '2021-04-30', '9823', 'Communication Manager', 'DFO & Quality Coordinator', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Notice board not been ordered yet.', 'Minor', 'Dokolo: SLM: Harriet Auma: today the notice board has not been ordered. ', 'closed', '2021-06-09', NULL, '2021-07-05', '2021-08-31', '2021-06-21', 'The supplier is affected by the government curfew. Please extend the completion date to 31.07.2021', 'Notice Board was delivered.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 07:26:03', '2022-01-27 18:27:41'),
(41, 3, 8, NULL, 8, 18, NULL, '2021-04-30', '6486', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'BGF Audit 2020; Auditor Joseph Masambo', 'Major', '7 Forks: Lack of adequate technical support during succession of staff in BGF farmer territories. The farmers in these areas had felt neglected, most lost trust with BGF and stopped caring of the trees. Most farmers groups in this group are non- existent and inactive as there was no adequate supervision and follow up. As noted earlier, even the record keeping was not updated for these farmers', 'closed', '2021-05-06', NULL, '2021-05-25', '2021-12-31', '2021-05-23', '1. Working with groups more for information sharing/communication whenever there are any changes.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 07:27:19', '2022-08-10 16:18:48'),
