(43, 3, 8, NULL, 8, 18, NULL, '2021-04-30', '2157', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'BGF Audit 2020; Auditor Joseph Masambo', 'Major', '7 Forks: Distribution of planting seedlings during dry period: Seedling distribution was done in periods where there was no adequate rainfall. The farmers had total losses and some farmers resorted to try and save the seedlings by creating their own home nurseries. The nurseries also didn’t survive either due to the farmers’ lack of knowledge in maintaining nurseries and overgrowth of seedlings.', 'closed', '2021-05-06', NULL, '2021-07-05', '2021-07-09', '2021-05-23', '1. Work with groups that are willing to water their seedlings in dry periods', 'M&E checked on the progress of working with groups. Some farmers are still not group members while other groups e.g Ngoche members are withdrawing from the program.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 07:34:29', '2021-07-05 10:47:49'),
(44, 3, 8, NULL, 8, 3, NULL, '2021-04-30', '5192', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'BGF Audit 2020; Auditor Joseph Masambo', 'Major', 'Nyongoro: The total number of the trees surviving was 305,383 trees, different from the figure maintained by the Finance department by 316,087 trees since the records in Finance department shows 621,470 trees. A further review of previous records provided for the audit as at the end of the 2018 financial year, December 31, 2018, the surviving trees at the Nyongoro site plantation was 443,004.', 'closed', '2021-05-06', NULL, '2021-06-04', '2021-10-31', '2021-06-03', '1. Even with good digital systems, we still need to work with committed personnel who are honest. The ultimate solution therefore is to get a team that can be trusted to provide correct information at all times.', 'Current tree counting verification is ongoing. 16% and 18% Variances are observed in compartments G104 and I044 in week 22.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-04-30 07:39:32', '2022-01-19 16:40:42'),
