(51, 19, 22, NULL, 5, 19, NULL, '2021-05-05', '1920', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Officer Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'PPE management Policy: Rev: 12-June-2020', 'Major', 'Not all required PPEs are available at the site. \n1. Riders suit: The policy require that riders have complete riding suits. This is not the case \n    since motorcycle users don\'t have all the riding gears. There are six motorcycles at the \n    site with only 2 helmets.\n2. Gumboots: Policy also indicates that the lifespan of a gumboot is 4 months. The last \n    stocking of new gumboots was in 2019 where 40 pairs were delivered. Most of the available gumboots are worn out.\n', 'closed', '2021-05-05', NULL, '2021-06-04', '2021-08-31', '2021-06-04', 'PPE schedules to be ready and approved by 15th June 2021', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-05 09:11:47', '2021-08-29 09:42:00'),
