(60, 18, 13, NULL, 8, 18, NULL, '2021-05-13', '9131', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', '1. Out growers training manual Rev.20720. Tending & management- pruning. 2. Group database training implementation report for March 2021.', 'Major', 'Four of the eight visited Kyusani and Mululini mukau growers group members have not implemented training on pruning. Munani Mwendwa; over pruned trees, Kiluti Mung\'ela; presence of double leaders saplings , Virginia Mwena Mbavu; Not pruned using either pruning saw or secateurs and Telesia Ngoloi has trees with branches that are over 2 cm thickness and below 5 meters height.', 'closed', '2021-05-22', NULL, '2021-06-04', '2021-10-31', '2021-06-03', 'The auditees responses are ok, however the Auditor needs to ask the farmer why they did not prune for the team to have a view of how to solve not only BGF issues but the non-conformances that are as a result of the farmer.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-13 15:43:54', '2022-08-10 16:20:56'),
(61, 18, 13, NULL, 8, 18, NULL, '2021-05-13', '1050', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', '1. Out growers training manual Rev 2/7/2020,tending & management- farm protection. 2. Group database training implementation report for March 2021.', 'Major', 'Farm protection by fencing is not implemented completely. There were openings in fences of five out of the eight Mululini & Kyusulani group members farms. The names of the farmers are; Telesia Ngoloi,Stephen Patel,Felistus  Sila,Munani Mwendwa and Virginia Mwena Mbavu.This will lead to high mortality due to livestock invasion.', 'closed', '2021-05-22', NULL, '2021-06-14', '2021-08-31', '2021-06-08', '1. We need to get the views of the farmers as to why they do not implement protection training.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-13 16:23:58', '2022-08-10 16:22:29'),
