(64, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, 44, '2021-05-21', '8266', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', '1.Tree counting Training records 2017-2018. 2.HR manual; It is not available at the site.', 'Major', '<p><a href=\"https://car.betterglobeforestry.co.ke/View/23/file\">https://car.betterglobeforestry.co.ke/View/23/file</a>- One of the two pms doing tree counting in E021 and E022 on 18th May of 2021 was not trained. There is no training record for Omar Barissa in the training list provided by the FTP. - 18 people were trained on tree counting in 2018. Training was done 5 times in 2018/17. 13 out of the 18 are currently employees of BGF as PMS. Omar Barissa is not in the list.</p>', 'closed', '2021-05-24', NULL, '2021-06-14', '2021-06-18', '2021-06-14', 'The approved training schedules to be hang on the noticeboards on all sites', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-21 12:08:57', '2021-06-18 07:43:02'),
(65, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, 66, '2021-05-21', '9716', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree counting Work instruction rev-6/2/2017 point #2. \"...making sure a stroke has been filled in the form representing the tree next to you in the designated tree counting form.\"', 'Major', 'Foolscaps were used to record  tree counts for E022 and E021 on 18/5/2021 in place of the designated tree counting forms. \r\nThis was because SFM did not make a request for the tree counting forms', 'closed', '2021-05-24', NULL, '2021-06-15', '2021-06-18', '2021-06-13', 'Follow up with the PM and SPM', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-21 12:20:20', '2021-06-22 14:01:25'),
(66, 19, 22, NULL, 5, 19, 44, '2021-05-21', '6947', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Officer Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', '1.Compartment map 2. GPS coordinates.  3. No standard reference for demarcation of compartments.', 'Major', '<p>Wooden sticks have been used in place of beacons for demarcation. They have no labels therefore it is not possible to identify compartments without referring to the map or making points of reference from the metallic beacons that are labelled. <a href=\"https://car.betterglobeforestry.co.ke/View/23/file\">https://car.betterglobeforestry.co.ke/View/23/file</a></p>', 'closed', '2021-05-22', NULL, '2021-07-01', '2021-08-31', '2021-06-04', 'IPR and LPO is done. On course', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-21 12:23:51', '2021-12-15 09:54:24'),
(67, 19, 22, NULL, 5, 3, 66, '2021-05-21', '480', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Officer Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', '1.Compartments map 2. Beacon Gps coordinates', 'Major', '<p>Tree counting was done without respect to compartment boundaries. Tree stock per compartment does not represent the stock as it is supposed to be with respect to the GRID. Counting in E022 was done in E022 and part of E090 while counting in E021 was done in E021, part of E089 and E022. <a href=\"https://car.betterglobeforestry.co.ke/View/23/file\">https://car.betterglobeforestry.co.ke/View/23/file</a></p>', 'closed', '2021-05-22', NULL, '2021-06-04', '2021-06-07', '2021-06-04', 'The Auditee is not SLO, it is the SFM\nMake the correction', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-21 15:05:45', '2021-06-08 11:59:40'),
(68, 8, 9, NULL, 8, 3, NULL, '2021-05-23', '2735', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Plantation Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', '210516 BGF Schedule of meetings 2021', 'Major', '<p>Unshared meeting minutes within the required time. Minutes must be shared latest by the end of the next day after the day of the meeting. These meetings were:</p><p>1 Implementation on-site Plantation Operations team Kiambere (Done on Thursday)</p><p>2 Implementation on site Plantations operations team Nyongoro (Done on Thursday)</p><p>3 HO Implementation &nbsp;Plantations management team KE (KIA) (Done on Friday)</p><p>4 HO Implementation &nbsp;Plantations management team KE (NYO) (Done on Friday)</p>', 'closed', '2021-05-24', NULL, '2021-06-15', '2021-06-18', '2021-06-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-23 22:01:36', '2021-06-23 16:15:30'),
(69, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, 44, '2021-05-24', '6290', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Record keeping.  Ref: FTP. \'\'...Training record book for 2019/20/21 was kept by the FTP at his house.\'\'', 'Major', '<p>M&amp;E requested for the training records on 20-May-2021 from the FTP who only gave one document. This affected timely verification. The two remaining documents were presented to the M&amp;E by the FTP on 24th Monday, 2021.</p><p>NC: FTP kept the book with training records at his house instead of storing it in the cabinet at the office. &nbsp;FTP said that it is risky to leave some of the documents in the office since it is easy for the document to get lost or someone making away with it. HR manual which was also available at the site is currently not available.&nbsp;</p><p>SFM: ‘’…the presence of the documents that are said to missing can only be confirmed after the cabinet is thoroughly searched.\'\'</p>', 'closed', '2021-05-26', NULL, '2021-06-28', '2021-06-30', '2021-06-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-24 09:55:10', '2021-06-30 08:09:40'),
(70, 4, 8, NULL, 8, 3, NULL, '2021-05-25', '1565', 'Communication Manager', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'REF: Email communication on PMS Resignation.', 'Major', '<p>1.Major communication breakdowns where Nyongoro PMS resigned without knowledge of EDF and HR.</p><p>2.PMS resigned on 13th May, HR and EDF received information on 24th May. 11 days later.</p><p>3.Plantations managers stated that it was recorded in minutes on 13th May and 15th May.</p><p>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://1drv.ms/b/s!As25tzmT79Zig9EEAW7ve4euRqItWQ?e=41r8pm\">Reference</a></p>', 'closed', '2021-06-08', NULL, '2021-06-14', '2021-06-15', '2021-06-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-25 08:35:46', '2021-06-14 10:10:27'),
(71, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, 66, '2021-05-27', '6784', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree counting. Ref: 1. Compartment map  2. GPS Coordinates', 'Major', '<p>Tree counting in compartments E022 and E021 on 18th of May 2021 was done without respect to the correct compartment Boundaries of the Map.</p><p>Trees were counted based on tree alignment and roads which shall cause errors in the number of trees in the compartments</p>', 'closed', '2021-05-29', NULL, '2021-06-21', '2021-06-25', '2021-06-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-27 12:40:23', '2021-07-01 10:38:13'),
(72, 16, 8, NULL, 8, 3, NULL, '2021-05-27', '5617', 'Human resource manager', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Ref: Weekly task report 15th May to 21st May', 'Major', '<ol><li>1.On Saturday staff are allocated tasks with targets for weekdays therefore not achievable due to less working hours.</li></ol><p>2.Some tasks are not adjusted according to different circumstances.</p>', 'closed', '2021-06-08', NULL, '2021-06-21', '2021-06-25', '2021-06-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-27 16:10:25', '2021-06-23 16:18:35'),
