(77, 18, 13, NULL, 8, 18, 73, '2021-05-28', '5133', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'BGF farmers\' out-growers manual rev 7/11/2019.Procedure for contracting farmers, point number 7.', 'Major', '<ol><li>1. 11 farmers that were contracted in 2018 and one in 2019 in Itinda, Kaisinga and Katimu and are under \'Onesmus Kyania have not been issued with hard copy contract agreement.</li><li>2. Six farmers from Kiomo were issued with hard copy contract agreement on 27/5/2021 after they have received and planted seedlings.</li></ol>', 'closed', '2021-05-30', NULL, '2021-06-10', '2021-08-31', '2021-06-08', '1. There needs to be a better transition for handing over when personnel leave. All records must be naded over to the personnel that shall take over and farmers notified of the change.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-05-28 20:44:35', '2022-08-10 16:23:49'),
