(80, 3, 9, NULL, 8, 3, 90, '2021-06-05', '2020', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Plantation Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Demarcation: Boundaries cannot be recognized away from the beacons.', 'Major', '<p>Beacons are not visible from one end to the other. 250 meters or 400 meters. Identifying compartments in the middle of plantation requires aid of a map and GPS coordinate</p><p>Tree counting can be done only by PMS who are familiar with the terrain of compartments and have been there since establishment of plantation. This makes it difficult to monitor without their Aid or for any new trained staff to do tree counting.</p>', 'closed', '2021-06-08', NULL, '2021-06-21', '2021-06-30', '2021-06-21', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-06-05 19:09:23', '2021-08-02 06:53:04'),
(81, 3, 9, NULL, 8, 3, 90, '2021-06-05', '7632', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Plantation Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Age of Trees: Accurate age of trees in compartments cannot be determined due to faded paint on trees', 'Major', '<p>The markers on trees have rubbed off. PMS estimate the compartments using memory and some of the trees which have paint on them</p><p>Age of gapped trees cannot be defined. There is no uniform age of trees. Compartments were gapped long after establishment. E.g. in 2018</p><p>Planting was done based on topography of the land</p>', 'closed', '2021-06-14', NULL, '2021-07-01', '2021-09-30', '2021-06-21', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-06-05 20:58:58', '2021-09-02 14:16:15'),
(82, 3, 9, NULL, 8, 3, 90, '2021-06-05', '3373', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Plantation Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Tree counting Task rate: Consistent under achievement of tree counting task rate', 'Major', '<p>Kiambere : The tree counting task rate is underachieved. The tree counting task rate in the back end is 2600</p><p>A new proposed task rate was 1800, proposed and indicated as Approved in the Forestry work plans.</p><p>FTP could not justified the new proposed task rate.</p><p>The current status of the newly proposed task rate is unknown to FTP</p>', 'closed', '2021-06-08', NULL, '2021-07-01', '2021-07-08', '2021-06-14', NULL, 'Training was done on Task rate management, record keeping in week 26 of 2021. Signed copies of trainings were shared', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-06-05 21:07:18', '2021-07-22 13:32:33'),
