(106, 2, 26, NULL, 8, 2, NULL, '2021-07-09', '6734', 'M&E Manager Uganda', 'Site Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Farmers\' list', 'Major', '<p>Some farmers were registered but didn\'t receive seedlings</p><p>Farmers were given seedlings before being sensitized about the programme</p><p>CR contracted farmers (76 farmers) in August 2020 but was not paid</p><p>Some farmers don\'t know BGF as a company. All they know is that they received seedlings for planting from their representatives</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2021-07-15', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-09-30', '2021-08-02', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-09 17:07:44', '2022-08-10 16:28:02'),
(107, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, NULL, '2021-07-11', '8575', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Back end results', 'Major', '<p>There is an incorrect result for mechanical pruning for 5th, 6th and 7th July 2020. Results in the back end is half of what was actually achieved. Task achieved were as follows; 202, 201 and 158trees respectively while in the back end it is 101, 100 and 79trees respectively.</p><p>Task in the back end indicates task achieved by one person instead of two people who should share the achievements. This could be as a results of differences in how results for this activity is handled by the system and how it is handled at the site. At the site the achievement is divided among two people-the operator and assistant.&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://onedrive.live.com/edit.aspx?cid=2ebeaa3beccad771&amp;page=view&amp;resid=2EBEAA3BECCAD771!228&amp;parId=2EBEAA3BECCAD771!101&amp;app=Excel\">https://onedrive.live.com/edit.aspx?cid=2ebeaa3beccad771&amp;page=view&amp;resid=2EBEAA3BECCAD771!228&amp;parId=2EBEAA3BECCAD771!101&amp;app=Excel</a></p>', 'closed', '2021-08-12', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-09-24', '2021-09-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-11 08:25:17', '2021-09-23 13:06:49'),
(108, 3, 9, NULL, 8, 3, NULL, '2021-07-11', '1937', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Plantation Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'T&A system results', 'Major', '<p>Task results are not achieved according to back end results</p><p>Examples:</p><p>20430 KIA-Temp-Nsy-Pricking out</p><p>20430 KIA-Perm-Est-Tools and equipment maintenance</p>', 'closed', '2021-07-21', NULL, '2021-08-03', '2021-08-06', '2021-08-02', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-11 12:59:54', '2021-08-03 10:43:58'),
(109, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, NULL, '2021-07-11', '6382', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Results/achievements', 'Major', '<p><strong>Under achievements of tasks</strong></p><p>Mechanical pruning targets was not achieved on 7th, 8th and 9th of July, 2021.&nbsp;</p><p>Target for the 3days was 600 trees while only 386trees were pruned.</p>', 'closed', '2021-08-12', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-09-24', '2021-09-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-11 14:41:21', '2021-09-17 20:10:38'),
(110, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, NULL, '2021-07-11', '9214', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Work instruction for manual cleaning. rev:29/01/2021.', 'Major', '<p>Glyphosate was not used in manual cleaning.</p><p>Work instruction requires that when using panga to cut down woody shrubs/weeds glyphosate is used permanently kill the shrub/weed to prevent it from re-sprouting.<a href=\"http://webmail.betterglobeforestry.com/Mondo/lang/sys/Forms/MAI/GetAttachment.aspx?&amp;MessageID=AEB6A58C7E5A40368AAC638D29B1FF95.MAI&amp;Folder=%2FInbox&amp;Filename=Work%20instruction%20for%20manual%20cleaning.docx&amp;Seq=1\">http://webmail.betterglobeforestry.com/Mondo/lang/sys/Forms/MAI/GetAttachment.aspx?&amp;MessageID=AEB6A58C7E5A40368AAC638D29B1FF95.MAI&amp;Folder=%2FInbox&amp;Filename=Work%20instruction%20for%20manual%20cleaning.docx&amp;Seq=1</a></p>', 'closed', '2021-08-12', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-09-24', '2021-09-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-11 19:01:33', '2021-09-25 20:47:34'),
(111, 2, 26, NULL, 8, 2, NULL, '2021-07-15', '9593', 'M&E Manager Uganda', 'Site Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Farmers list', 'Major', '<p>Some farmers have no contacts registered</p><p>Contacts are for CRs but they don\'t know the farmers</p><p>Farmers didn\'t get seedlings for gapping</p><p>Farmers claim that the trees were counted by their representative (CR)</p><p>Seedlings distributed from far (different subcounty) and some farmers have no means so couldn\'t collect the seedlings</p>', 'closed', '2021-07-15', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-12-31', '2021-08-02', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-15 11:16:53', '2022-02-11 16:24:49'),
(112, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, 155, '2021-07-26', '4798', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree stock management standards', 'Major', '<ol><li>The following activities have no work instructions</li></ol><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Activity&nbsp;</td><td>Department</td><td>How it is/was done</td></tr><tr><td>20647-NYO-Perm-Maint-Beacon sourcing</td><td>Forestry</td><td>Wooden materials sourced from the bush/forest by team.&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>20647-NYO-Perm-Maint-Demarcation</td><td>Forestry</td><td>Marking of points along boundaries of compartment at intervals of 50m. The activity was also recorded as marking of boundaries in the achievement records.</td></tr><tr><td>20547-NYO-Perm-Maint-Game damage assesment</td><td>Forestry</td><td>Count total number of trees/seedlings that have been damaged by game in compartments.</td></tr><tr><td>20647-NYO-Perm-Mant-Beacon installation</td><td>Forestry</td><td>Wooden materials collected in beacon sourcing were installed at points marked in demarcation activity. The wooden posts acts as guideposts showing the compartment boundaries.</td></tr><tr><td>20647-NYO-Perm-Maint-Compartment Gridding</td><td>Forestry</td><td><p>Initially, the person doing compartment gridding walked along boundaries showing the tree counting team the limits of the compartmen. He used GPS device.</p><p>Currently, the activity involves the use of rope to mark the boundaries. Unfortunately, the rope is not enough hence compromising on its effectiveness.</p></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://1drv.ms/w/s!AnHXyuw7qr4ugWZhloVtI6w5dPDa?e=EuH5Bz\">https://1drv.ms/w/s!AnHXyuw7qr4ugWZhloVtI6w5dPDa?e=EuH5Bz</a></p>', 'closed', '2021-08-12', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-09-24', '2021-09-17', 'This has been done. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-26 07:36:54', '2021-09-27 08:30:14'),
(113, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, 156, '2021-07-26', '5327', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree counting process and tree counting work instruction', 'Major', '<p>Compartment Boundaries are not permanent. The boundaries will vary from time to time due to frequent use of GPS device to mark the boundaries before the counting exercise.&nbsp;</p><p>GPS device performance is affected by the prevailing weather conditions</p><p>Having permanent boundaries will make it possible to stick to the same boundaries even without the use of GPS device.</p><p><a href=\"https://1drv.ms/w/s!AnHXyuw7qr4ugWZhloVtI6w5dPDa?e=EuH5Bz\">https://1drv.ms/w/s!AnHXyuw7qr4ugWZhloVtI6w5dPDa?e=EuH5Bz</a></p>', 'closed', '2021-08-12', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-09-24', '2021-09-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-26 07:43:44', '2022-01-12 04:19:03'),
(114, 3, 5, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-07-27', '2405', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Reference Documents', 'Major', '<p>Work instructions used for forestry activities are in editable word formats and with no signatures.</p><p>Work instruction for both Nursery and plantations have no signatures hence it is difficult to tell if they are approved.&nbsp;</p><p>Good example of an approved documents are the ones for HR on Health and safety policies. These documents are in pdf and have been signed and dates indicated. It is therefore possible to confidently say that the document is approved.</p>', 'closed', '2021-08-03', NULL, '2021-10-01', '2021-11-30', '2021-09-20', 'On progress, to be completed by 31/12/2021', 'The introduction and use of the document control app will take care of all these issues', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-27 09:44:25', '2022-03-16 18:46:00'),
(115, 18, 15, NULL, 8, 3, NULL, '2021-07-29', '2946', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Seedling production jobcard 2021.Nursery stock record.', 'Major', '<p>A high post germination mortality of 17.20% and a low germination of 50.71% as at 27/7/2021 in the ongoing seedling production in Kiambere.</p><p>Summary as &nbsp;at 27/7/2021.</p><p>Total seeds sown=50749</p><p>Total seedlings pricked out=25738</p><p>Post germination mortality=4428</p><p>Biological stock =15191.</p><p>Cause of mortality.</p><p>FT comment\" Fungal infection,we used ridomil but it wasn\'t effective,we switched to score on the last sowing and there was improvement\"</p><p>Impact.</p><p>The GIC might not receive the anticipated 20,000 seedlings in November 2021.</p>', 'closed', '2021-10-29', NULL, '2021-11-19', '2021-11-30', '2021-11-19', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-07-29 23:13:30', '2021-11-19 16:26:56'),
(116, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, 179, '2021-08-01', '1568', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree counting work instruction. Rev:24/5/2021', 'Major', '<p>Both game damaged trees and windthrows were counted by the tree counting team yet the two are not featured in the work instruction. &nbsp;After counting both alive, dead , game damage and windthrow, only alive trees which include trees in the alive section and game damaged that are alive are fed to the back end.</p><p>Report link <a href=\"https://1drv.ms/w/s!AnHXyuw7qr4ugWj8I2abHRNS9GXn\">https://1drv.ms/w/s!AnHXyuw7qr4ugWj8I2abHRNS9GXn</a></p><p>Image link <a href=\"https://1drv.ms/f/s!AnHXyuw7qr4ugW3WvKgzjV0p1PEE\">https://1drv.ms/f/s!AnHXyuw7qr4ugW3WvKgzjV0p1PEE</a></p>', 'closed', '2021-08-12', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-09-24', '2021-09-17', 'Done', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-08-01 08:35:28', '2021-09-22 18:56:10'),
(117, 19, 11, NULL, 8, 19, 183, '2021-08-08', '803', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree counting work instruction', 'Minor', '<p>Tree counting exercise in week 31 was done contrary to the work instruction.</p><p>Both game damaged, windthrows and dead trees were counted in a single exercise. Counting of game damaged and windthrows are not featured in the work instruction.</p>', 'closed', '2021-08-12', NULL, '2021-09-17', '2021-09-24', '2021-09-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-08-08 20:29:03', '2021-09-19 19:35:47'),
(118, 2, 26, NULL, 8, 2, NULL, '2021-08-16', '4210', 'M&E Manager Uganda', 'Site Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Farmers\' list', 'Minor', '<p>Some numbers are not available on the MTN network and yet recorded with different farmers</p><p>Incomplete number</p><p>Some numbers are consistently not reachable</p>', 'closed', '2021-08-22', NULL, '2021-12-01', '2021-12-31', '2021-09-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-08-16 10:52:00', '2022-02-11 16:25:08'),
(119, 3, 29, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2021-08-19', '2197', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Operations Manager', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Plantation Security/Maintenance', 'Major', '<p>On 18th August 2021: There was Fresh evidence of cattle in the plantation: Compartment A013 and A014 1. Fresh dung was seed during tree counting 2. Flat patches of grass in the compartments 3.Two cows tied to the outer fence in compartment A013 4.Security on duty in that Compartment was Kyalo Mwangangi at night: There was no patrol during the day for those compartments. 5. There is possibility of collusion with Security personnel and cows belonging to security according to Temporary workers.</p>', 'closed', '2022-07-08', '2022-07-08', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-15', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-08-19 14:31:58', '2022-07-26 17:14:07'),
(120, 3, 15, NULL, 8, 3, NULL, '2021-08-19', '435', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Plantation maintenance: Compartment cleaning', 'Major', '<p>Compartments with neem trees are inaccessible because they are bushy. Cleaning has not been done on these compartments.</p><ul><li>Compartments A018,A010,A011,A014, A019 have neem trees which are part of the tree stock.</li><li>This has made tree counting difficult and risky.</li><li>Inaccurate estimates for tree counts are used.</li></ul><p>For correct number of trees to be found, the compartments needs to be cleaned to be made accessible.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2021-08-19', NULL, '2021-09-20', '2021-12-31', '2021-09-17', 'Neem trees to be cleaned starting next week.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-08-19 14:39:05', '2021-12-03 16:55:05'),
(121, 2, 26, NULL, 8, 2, NULL, '2021-08-22', '7569', 'M&E Manager Uganda', 'Site Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Farmers list', 'Major', '<ul><li>Numbers not verified</li><li>Numbers consistently not reachable</li><li>Wrong numbers</li><li>Farmers require support</li><li>Planted in wrong season (towards end of the rainy season)</li><li>Some farmers didn\'t receive any trees</li><li>Mixed species (local species that produce flowers)</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2021-08-23', NULL, '2021-12-01', '2021-12-31', '2021-09-28', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-08-22 19:08:54', '2022-05-12 13:34:31'),
(122, 19, 22, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-09-09', '6620', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Officer Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Human resource manual', 'Major', '<p>Human resource manual requires that random calls are answered when they happen.</p><p>However, Anderson Kahindi Mendza, Work number 4 missed random calls on 12th August 2021 and Miriam Stephen Kadzo, Work number 704 &nbsp;on 7th September 2021. &nbsp;<br>Anderson Kahindi was called at 9.12am while Miriam Stephen was called at 1pm.<br>They missed random calls because they were not duly informed by the kit handlers.<br>Anderson Kahindi did not receive his one-day wage while Miriam Stephen may not receive her wage for 7th September 2021.</p><p>Random call for 12th August was from T&amp;A device managed by Gideon Barisa while the 2nd random call was from time capture device.</p>', 'closed', '2021-11-01', NULL, '2021-11-18', '2021-11-30', '2021-11-06', 'The sensitization has been done. Workers have been informed to always check for random calls when they clock out. Those deducted by Mistake were refunded', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-09-09 13:30:59', '2021-11-06 14:23:53'),
(123, 18, 13, NULL, 8, 18, NULL, '2021-09-11', '2232', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Farmer contract & week 32 of 2021 forestry verification report.', 'Minor', '<ol><li>&nbsp;Misinformation of partner farmer, incorrect and Incomplete farmer details.</li><li>&nbsp;</li></ol><p><i><strong>Farmer misinformation</strong></i>.</p><p>“I was told that when I have trees I’ll be assisted with school fees” Regina Mwende Mati from Tyaa kamuthale,Katieko.</p><p><i><strong>Incorrect and Incomplete farmer details.</strong></i></p><ol><li><i><strong>Contract number</strong></i></li></ol><p>&nbsp;Daniel Muneni Mailu.</p><p>Correct contract number: 16/TYK/000404.</p><p>Contract number provided :16/TYK/</p><p>2 <i><strong>National identification Number</strong></i>.</p><p>Joseph Munyoki Mbaluka</p><p>Correct ID number:0941040.</p><p>ID number provided: 226813170.</p><p>3 <i><strong>Cell Phone number</strong></i></p><p>Grace Kisai Kyondo</p><p>Correct phone number: 0725070645.</p><p>Phone number provided: 0725010648</p><p>Regina Mwende Mati.</p><p>Correct phone number: &nbsp;0718580078.</p><p>Phone number provided:07130336565.</p>', 'closed', '2021-09-15', NULL, '2021-10-01', '2021-12-31', '2021-09-17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-09-11 15:59:52', '2022-03-21 18:56:45'),
(124, 18, 12, NULL, 8, 18, NULL, '2021-09-11', '1728', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Farmer Group Formation and Coordinator Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'An ideal farmer group characteristics 210128', 'Minor', '<p><i><strong>Inactive group.(Nguka Mukau Growers)</strong></i></p><p>Four partners farmers from Ndoo, Ngugi village confirmed that their group is inactive.</p><ol><li>1.Rhoda Mwalale Mwinzi.</li><li>2.Juliet Kalunda Kinyili.</li><li>3.Josphine Muli Mwendwa.</li><li>4.Jacob Musee Mwangangi.</li></ol><p><i><strong>Root cause</strong></i>:</p><p>Internal group conflict</p><ul><li>“The group not having a permanent AA after the AA who was here by then left (Samora Salim)” Juliet Kanyili.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2021-09-14', NULL, '2021-09-30', '2021-10-31', '2021-09-17', 'Ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-09-11 16:13:13', '2022-04-05 16:56:26'),
(125, 32, 13, NULL, 8, 32, NULL, '2021-09-14', '8782', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Forestry verification report week 31 & 32,2021.', 'Major', '<p>14 farmers confirmed through farm visits and Phone calls were not visited and the list is as below;</p><p>Farmers Name&nbsp;<br>Phone number<br>Njeru Njeu&nbsp;<br>O706905103<br>Jane Ngithi Njuki&nbsp;<br>0705141149<br>Justa Wanjue Ngari&nbsp;<br>0703757571<br>Njiru Njuki&nbsp;<br>0724528475<br>Eliud Mbogo Kathiru<br>0713897259<br>Ephantus Njeru &nbsp;Ireri<br>0706797301<br>Jackson Njeru Ireri<br>0748639809<br>Edward Njeru Bernard<br>0728758116<br>Benjamin Nyaga Ngari&nbsp;<br>0701152327<br>Elkana Njeru Mumanthe<br>0715842358<br>Antony Nyaga Mwathi<br>0727415087<br>Phone calls</p><p>Julian Muturi &nbsp;Mbuva<br>0795194929<br>Orientation Wangari Ngari3<br>0705314841<br>Margaret Ngugi Namu<br>0708745764</p><p>AAs comment, John Njeru-farmers were not found in their homes,AA- Kamau said representatives were found in the farmers homestead.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2021-09-17', NULL, '2021-10-01', '2021-10-31', '2021-09-17', 'More details needed on the data collected ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-09-14 15:02:51', '2021-10-22 18:49:07'),
(126, 4, 8, NULL, 8, 3, NULL, '2021-10-13', '6194', 'Communication Manager', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Bribing at Kiambere site to do certain tasks', 'Major', '<p>Information was given by Joseph Muthukumi, &nbsp;a casual worker.<br>Apparently, everybody wants to be assigned watering?</p>', 'closed', '2021-10-22', NULL, '2021-10-25', '2021-10-29', '2021-10-22', 'ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-10-13 10:15:40', '2021-10-29 15:52:40'),
