(129, 4, 5, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-10-13', '5226', 'Communication Manager', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Some staff security personnel are suspected to have poured salted water on a bed containing  seedlings as the hope to get the forester fired', 'Major', '<p>From Joseph Muthukumi, a casual worker. He named team &nbsp;6 which after investigations are Maithya Makua, Peter Kakuli Mwinzi, Peter Mutinda Muthengi, and Muneeni Kyalo.</p>', 'closed', '2021-11-26', NULL, '2022-01-17', '2022-01-21', '2022-01-13', 'This was resolved and measures put in place', 'This CAR was addressed satisfactory!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-10-13 10:27:33', '2022-01-18 15:18:59'),
(130, 4, 5, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-10-13', '9385', 'Communication Manager', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Security is bullying casuals not to report occurances', 'Major', '<p>Casual Muthukumi asked the question and a security guard tried to address the issue by forcefully denying the right. (name?)</p>', 'closed', '2021-10-25', NULL, '2021-11-17', '2021-11-19', '2021-11-06', 'This was addressed during the meeting on site. Such emphasis are also done on other sites that people can directly report malicious activities on sites.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-10-13 10:37:05', '2021-11-06 14:20:42'),
(131, 16, 5, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-10-15', '8621', 'Human resource manager', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Kiambere site visit report on 6th and 7th October (Vetting of Kiambere Security)', 'Major', '<ol><li>1.Most guards are illiterate and can neither read nor write. This leaves room for HOS to manipulate the reports of daily occurrences.</li><li>2.There is a rivalry between the security related to HOS and the non-related security</li><li>3.Corruption and bribery is ongoing. Security gets bribes to allow cattle to graze on the plantation. E.g Peter mutinda Muthengi was mentioned by some security.</li><li>4.Approved security schedule not implemented.HOS does manual allocation.</li><li>5.Security uniform not well maintained. The uniform procured this year is old and in bad shape for some security&nbsp;</li><li>6.Random calls are missed as the device handlers fail to take the devices to them. None of the Bluetooth devices is working. The staff has to come to the nursery to answer the calls.</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2021-10-25', NULL, '2021-12-01', '2021-12-31', '2021-11-06', 'The above corrective action proposals are ok and ongoing.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-10-15 18:27:54', '2021-12-14 09:46:24'),
(132, 5, 29, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-10-17', '1224', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Vetting of security guards in KIA', 'Major', '<p>Theft of Irrigation pipes in the plantation and the nursery</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2021-10-18', NULL, '2021-11-17', '2021-11-19', '2021-11-06', 'We are working on having a gate at all sites to control entrance to site.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-10-17 21:12:28', '2021-12-14 09:41:54'),
(133, 5, 29, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-10-17', '6280', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Vetting of security in KIA', 'Major', '<p>Theft of PPE from site by workers.&nbsp;</p><p>Theft of Seedlings by workers</p><p>Back in 2019, casual workers were stealing seedlings as they left in the evening. They them in their bags.</p><p>Evidence of people wearing BGF Overalls outside BGF shows that we have overalls that have disappeared from site.</p>', 'closed', '2021-10-18', NULL, '2021-11-17', '2021-11-19', '2021-11-06', 'This has been handled by HR in KIA. NYO there are no such cases', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-10-17 21:15:54', '2021-11-06 14:16:45'),
(134, 5, 21, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-10-17', '5787', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Site Logistics Officer 7Forks & KIA', '7 Forks', 'Operations', 'Vetting of security, Site visit and investigations ', 'Major', '<p>Death of 1,000 seedlings in the nursery.</p><p>Alleged to have been poisoned.</p>', 'closed', '2021-10-21', NULL, '2021-11-17', '2021-11-19', '2021-11-06', 'To plan for the Training. to be done before end of this year.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-10-17 21:17:43', '2021-11-19 16:23:02'),
