(189, 19, 22, NULL, 5, 3, NULL, '2021-12-07', '1541', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Officer Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Security schedule', 'Major', '<p>There is unequal distribution of dayshifts and nightshifts assigned to security guard in December.&nbsp;</p><p>This has been verified after the analysis of December security schedule. This was as a result of one security guard raising a concern on the unsatisfying allocation of shifts. The result of the analysis has been attached in the evidence section.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-01-16', NULL, '2022-01-31', '2022-02-04', '2022-01-30', 'This has been implemented starting Feb 2022', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-12-07 20:03:14', '2022-03-01 21:00:32'),
