(192, 3, 4, 23, 23, 3, NULL, '2021-12-10', '3466', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Communication Manager', 'Head Office', 'Communications', 'Communication Gap: Human Resource department', 'Major', '<p>Changes in Human Resource are not updated in the Capture system as there is no official communication from HR department to IT department.</p><p><strong>Example:</strong></p><p>Change in reporting for M&amp;E officers, M&amp;E Manager to FOD from EDF.</p><p>Change in reporting for Agroforestry Agent to M&amp;E Manager</p><p>Resigned/Dismissed staff are still in the system</p><p><strong>Consequences:</strong> Leave notifications are not received by the correct HOD</p>', 'closed', '2022-01-19', '2022-05-04', '2022-05-06', '2022-05-13', '2022-05-04', 'Taken care of by HR', 'DDC made DDHR aware of the problem. DDHR informed the HOD\'s that they need to communicate changes in their department to IT through the ticket system. Apparently this has been addressed (not checked!)', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-12-10 10:29:25', '2022-06-24 16:15:14'),
(193, 3, 16, NULL, 23, 3, NULL, '2021-12-10', '6606', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Human resource manager', 'Head Office', 'HR', 'Communication Gap: Human Resource department', 'Major', '<p>Changes in Human Resource are not updated in the Capture system as there is no official communication from HR department to IT department.</p><p><strong>Example:</strong></p><p>Change in reporting for M&amp;E officers, M&amp;E Manager to FOD from EDF.</p><p>Change in reporting for Agroforestry Agent to M&amp;E Manager</p><p>Resigned/Dismissed staff are still in the system</p><p><strong>Consequences:</strong> Leave notifications are not received by the correct HOD</p>', 'closed', '2021-12-14', NULL, '2022-01-28', '2022-01-31', '2022-01-27', 'HAs been addressed in the management team meeting', 'We will develop a checklist with all that possibly need to be done, attended at, communicated etc.. PRIOR to the induction of the staff member or the changes in his/her position.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-12-10 10:29:26', '2022-01-27 16:01:31'),
(195, 18, 29, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2022-01-19', '5821', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Customer fuel statement form', 'Major', '<p>The columns for fuel balance and motorbike plate number were not filled as from 17 January 2022 to &nbsp;19 January 2022 on the customer fuel statement form at Gate way fuel station &nbsp;Kamuwongo.</p>', 'closed', '2022-02-01', '2022-03-03', '2022-03-08', '2022-03-11', '2022-03-08', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-01-20 01:19:24', '2022-03-14 13:37:01'),
(196, 19, 22, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2022-01-20', '4906', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Officer Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Mechanical cleaning work instruction', 'Major', '<p>Tractors slashed woody acacias during mechanical cleaning contrary to the requirements that requires woody weeds be manualy cut by manual cleaning team ahead of mechanical cleaning&nbsp;</p><p>The tractor that did mechanical cleaning on 19th January, 2022 were KTCB 563N-Patrick Safari</p><p>KTCB 156X- Justine Kombe and KTCB 153X- Rashid Mzee</p>', 'closed', '2022-02-01', '2022-03-03', '2022-03-08', '2022-03-11', '2022-03-08', 'Operations have adapted the mechanical cleaning schedule to follow Forestry Maintenance plan for prunning and removing shrubs.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-01-20 18:47:15', '2022-03-15 12:01:46'),
(197, 19, 22, NULL, 5, 19, NULL, '2022-01-20', '7481', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Officer Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Mechanical cleaning work instruction', 'Major', '<p>Tractor assistants moved behind the tractor instead of ahead of the tractor during mechanical cleaning on 19th January, 2022.</p><p>Work instruction requires that tractor assistant should assess working area before tractor driver starts brush cutting to ensure there is no obstacles such as wood debris for better results.&nbsp;</p><p>If wood debris are not removed, the tractor becomes vulnerable to punctures and potential damage to the slashing implement.</p><p>Tractors assistants were Muhammed Kahindi and Muhammed Gobu.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-01-24', NULL, '2022-01-31', '2022-02-04', '2022-01-30', 'OK. Prospection to be done the week prior to assess and plan for cleaning.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-01-20 18:51:12', '2022-02-18 18:56:46'),
