(201, 4, 8, 8, 8, 5, NULL, '2022-01-28', '4687', 'Communication Manager', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Uploading Photos on Google drive to be used for social media ', 'Minor', '<p>It was agreed that Forestry and Operations photos(with a caption or short description) showing activities will be uploaded on google drive, so I just have to select there for our social media use.&nbsp;</p><p>That is no longer happening, the last time photos were uploaded was week 39!</p>', 'closed', '2022-02-01', '2022-05-25', '2022-05-27', '2022-06-30', '2022-05-25', 'ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-01-28 14:08:30', '2022-08-10 16:28:34'),
