(228, 4, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-03-09', '6304', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', '7 Forks', 'Operations', 'Communications App', 'Major', '<p>I phoned Kiambere and Nyongoro security guards and very few knew about the communication App, about 35%.</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-18', '2022-04-08', '2022-05-24', '2022-05-27', '2022-05-18', 'This has been implemented through the document control app and shall come in the document revision 2 stage', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-09 21:35:31', '2022-06-08 17:52:09'),
(229, 32, 15, 10, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-11', '1204', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Improved seedling production Trial KIA 2021', 'Major', '<p>The improved seedling production Trial KIA 2021 indicates that seedling Measurements (height, stem base diameter and checking of rooting system is done once a month. The document is not specific when the Measurements of the seedlings should start.&nbsp;</p><p>Initial Measurements are baseline for the records.&nbsp;</p><p>Pricking in/out was done on 7/3/2022 ,From SB3,SB2 &amp;SB1 and pricked in to traditional and efford beds accordingly .No seedling Measurements was done at this stage.&nbsp;</p><p>FT is the activity owner.&nbsp;</p><p>This was observed on M&amp;E visit of 11/03/2022</p>', 'closed', '2022-04-06', '2022-04-13', '2022-04-19', '2022-04-29', '2022-04-19', 'The measurements are on schedule.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-11 19:19:02', '2022-08-10 16:37:39'),
(230, 18, 15, 9, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-15', '7803', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Methodology for Setting up and Execution of Improved Seedling Production Experiment.', 'Minor', '<p>Multiplication of the Mycorrhiza used in the experiment was not done yet all seedlings were pricked out in seedbed 2 .The Methodology for Setting up and Execution of Improved Seedling Production Experiment work instruction requires the soil mixed with Mycorrhiza to be used in the multiplication.</p><p>This was observed on 14/3/2022.</p><p>Forestry Technician’s comment “Pricking out ended over the weekend and the activity will be included in the plan and carried out on 16/3/2022”</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-16', '2022-03-22', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-30', '2022-03-24', 'There is no provision for failure in the write up for the set up and execution of the experiment for the improved seedling production. Activities must be done according to schedule.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-15 18:40:56', '2022-04-22 13:37:49'),
(231, 18, 15, 8, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-15', '9438', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Job cards 2022.', 'Minor', '<p>Incorrect recording of the seeds sown in the job cards. The seeds sown was 7360 seeds not 7150 seeds as indicated in the job card. The variation came from the seeds sown in seedbed 3.</p><p>This was observed on 14/3/2022.</p><p>The Forest technician kiambere is the activity owner.</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-16', '2022-05-25', '2022-05-27', '2022-06-03', '2022-05-25', 'ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-15 18:50:40', '2022-05-30 14:17:28'),
(232, 8, 15, 9, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-16', '7891', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Improved seedling production work instruction & work plan', 'Major', '<p>A very low germination percentage of seeds for the improved seedling production experiment. Only 1,142 germinated out of the expected 3,575</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-18', '2022-03-22', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-30', '2022-03-24', 'The root cause is in the job cards. Issues in propagation start at the point of collection, the materials used and poor sanitation at the nursery.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-16 17:12:25', '2022-08-10 16:43:40'),
(234, 18, 35, 10, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-17', '5489', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Accounts records, week 6 FOR report.', 'Minor', '<p>The M&amp;E verified that 28 partner farmers have not been issued with hard copy contract agreement.</p><p>The 28 partner farmers are from kalanga,Kakunike,Ukasi and Mbuvu sub-location,Nguni ward.</p><p>The verification was done in week 10 by M&amp;E from the data from week 6 of accounts record.</p><p>An AA is responsible for issuing contract agreement to his/her respective partner farmers.</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-19', '2022-03-23', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-01', '2022-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-17 20:05:46', '2022-08-10 16:47:35'),
(235, 18, 35, 10, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-17', '6020', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Accounts record,week 6 FOR report', 'Minor', '<p>The M&amp;E verified that 2 partner farmers had incorrect phone numbers.</p><p>The 2 partner farmers are from Kakunike and Mbuvu sub-locations,Nguni ward.</p><p>The verification was done in week 10 by M&amp;E from the data from week 6 of accounts record.</p><p>William Liyayi and William Odede are responsible for the records.</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-19', '2022-03-23', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-01', '2022-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-17 20:16:52', '2022-03-25 21:08:12'),
(236, 18, 35, 10, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-17', '8623', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Accounts record,Week 6 FOR report.', 'Minor', '<p>The M&amp;E verified that 2 partner farmers had incorrect identification numbers,</p><p>The 2 partner farmers are from Ukasi and &nbsp;Kalanga &nbsp;sub-locations,Nguni ward.</p><p>The verification was done in week 10 by M&amp;E from the data from week 6 of accounts record.</p><p>James Kihumba is &nbsp;responsible for the records.</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-19', '2022-03-23', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-01', '2022-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-17 20:23:04', '2022-03-25 21:08:38'),
(237, 18, 35, 10, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-17', '5866', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Accounts records,week 6 FOR report.', 'Minor', '<p>The M&amp;E verified that 8 partner farmers are not in BGF farmers\' group.&nbsp;</p><p>The 8 partner farmers are from Ukasi,Kakunike &amp; Mbuvu &nbsp; sub-locations,Nguni ward.</p><p>The verification was done in week 10 by M&amp;E from the data from week 6 of accounts record.</p><p>Attached is the evidence together with partner farmers\' comment. .</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-19', '2022-03-23', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-01', '2022-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-17 20:41:55', '2022-04-05 17:01:31'),
(238, 32, 35, 10, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-17', '432', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Accounts records, week 7.', 'Major', '<p>M&amp;E verified that 2 partner farmers were not visited as in accounts records.&nbsp;</p><p>The partner farmers are from Kiambere, Gacabari Sublocation and Mutindwa village.&nbsp;</p><p>Verification was done in week 10 by M&amp;E from the data from week 7 of accounts records.&nbsp;</p><p>The partner farmer &nbsp;confirmed throug &nbsp;physica farm visit ,AA John Njeru confirmed the same through a phone call.&nbsp;</p><p>The AA responsible for this record is John &nbsp;Njeru.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-22', '2022-03-23', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-01', '2022-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-18 03:32:42', '2022-04-05 20:30:58'),
(239, 32, 35, 10, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-03-17', '8460', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Accounts records, week 7', 'Major', '<p>M&amp;E verified that 16 partner farmers have not been issued with hard copy contracts.&nbsp;</p><p>The partner farmers are from Kiambere, Mavuria, Mumoni and Kiomo Kyethani wards.&nbsp;</p><p>The verification was done in week 10 by M&amp;E from the data of week 7 accounts records.&nbsp;</p><p>2 partner farmers confirmed through physical visits by &nbsp;M&amp;E,and &nbsp;14 through phone calls.&nbsp;</p><p>The AAs are the ones who are responsible in &nbsp;issuing the &nbsp;hard copy contracts to the partner farmers in their territories.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-19', '2022-03-23', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-01', '2022-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-18 04:10:12', '2022-08-10 16:48:21'),
(240, 32, 35, 10, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-18', '3391', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Accounts records, week 7', 'Major', '<p>M&amp;E verified that &nbsp;12 partner farmers are not in BGF mukau groups.&nbsp;</p><p>12 partner farmers are from Kiambere, Mumoni and Kiomo Kyethani wards.&nbsp;</p><p>The verification was done in week 10 by M&amp;E from the data of week 7 accounts records.&nbsp;</p><p>The 12 partner farmers confirmed that they don\'t attend group meetings/trainings.&nbsp;</p><p>AAs are &nbsp;responsible for partner farmers attending &nbsp;BGF mukau group &nbsp;trainings.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-03-19', '2022-03-23', '2022-03-25', '2022-04-01', '2022-03-24', 'We have been counting trees not forming groups in the past months.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-18 04:19:02', '2022-04-05 16:59:48');
