(257, 3, 35, 35, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-03-29', '8824', 'M&E Manager Kenya', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', '7 Forks records in accounts ', 'Major', '<p>Differences in the number of trees counted by Agroforestry Agents and M&amp;E Officers.</p><p>There were 10 farmers out of 17 who were found to have variances in the trees standing. This is 59% of those verified by farm visits. The variances range from 1 to 52 trees&nbsp;</p><p>The verification was from week 4,5,6,7 &amp; 8 of 2022 carried out in week 12 of 2022.</p><p>The farmers are from different Wards visited by different Agroforestry agents.(See list)</p><p>Attached list shows the farmers and their respective variances.</p>', 'closed', '2022-04-07', '2022-04-25', '2022-05-11', '2022-12-31', '2022-05-10', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-03-29 17:05:35', '2022-08-25 19:10:54'),
