(272, 16, 5, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-04-22', '1772', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Temporary workers payment for week 14 and 15 Nyongoro', 'Major', '<ol><li><strong>1. Variances in Nyongoro housekeeping Job card.</strong>&nbsp;</li><li>The temporary staff who signed the housekeeping job card vary with the attendance reports generated from the time and attendance system. Therefore ;</li></ol><ul><li>&nbsp; a. &nbsp;It’s not possible to know whether the job was done or not and who did it.</li><li>&nbsp; b. The payment for the two weeks (wk 14 and 15) cannot be done.&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'closed', '2022-07-15', '2022-07-18', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-04-22 21:01:19', '2022-07-26 17:39:25'),
