(312, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-05-05', '6756', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Site hygiene', 'Major', '<p>Littered compound.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed that site was untidy, there was unused pieces of pipes seen around the blue water tanks and along side the old debris .A plate, a short wood in form of a chisel and two stones beside .A cup in a plastic tin and a bottle beside the drinking water tank. A plastic container, fallen tree logs, muffin on top of a post and old debris lying on the old nursery beds.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed in Kiambere site.&nbsp;</p><p>The observation was done on 28/4/22.</p><p>DFO observed that Kiambere site was not clean, unused pipes, plastic containers and old debris were scattered on the site.&nbsp;</p><p>FT is responsible.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-18', '2022-05-20', '2022-06-21', '2022-06-30', '2022-06-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-06 01:20:24', '2022-07-26 17:47:59'),
(313, 32, 15, 10, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-05-05', '6378', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Site hygiene', 'Major', '<p>Incorrect positioning and &nbsp;arrangement of different items in site.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed the following items were Wrongly positioned, a broken ladder placed on top of three blue water tanks. Adjustable ladder placed beside a tree,another ladder behind the store. Watering guns on top of polythene sheets, polythene sheets on top of wheelbarrow. A power saw, a rope and &nbsp;a crate with pangas &nbsp;are not in the right place. Unfuctional and functional files behind the old store.&nbsp;</p><p>A shelf &nbsp;in the office had mixed item like ,office glue, stapler, paper punch, stamp pad, &nbsp;First Aid kit,medicine container, water guard, spirit, Eno box and uncovered bottle of water .</p><p>DFO observed these in Kiambere site.&nbsp;</p><p>The observation was done on 28/4/22 by DFO.</p><p>The observation made was that different items were Wrongly placed/positioned.&nbsp;</p><p>FT is responsible.&nbsp;</p><p>The attached is the evidence.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-08', '2022-05-09', '2022-05-27', '2022-06-03', '2022-05-25', 'ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-06 03:25:01', '2022-06-14 15:22:21'),
(314, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-05-06', '1351', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Stock and their labels', 'Major', '<p>Lack of labelling and numbering of site items.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed that a blue dustbin was not labelled and three pipes were not numbered.&nbsp;</p><p>Labelling indicates the use of an item and numbering provides easy identification of &nbsp;an item whether lost or not.&nbsp;</p><p>The observation was made by DFO in Kiambere site.&nbsp;</p><p>It was observed on 28/4/22 by DFO.</p><p>The observation was that a blue dustbin was not labelled despite the numbering of the pipes three were not numbered though assembled together.&nbsp;</p><p>FT is responsible.&nbsp;</p><p>Evidence is attached.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-18', '2022-05-20', '2022-06-21', '2022-06-30', '2022-06-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-06 05:25:40', '2022-07-26 17:50:09'),
(315, 32, 15, 10, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-05-06', '7878', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Site hygiene ', 'Major', '<p>Lack of tissue paper and a hand wash soap.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed that there was no tissue paper in the toilet and a hand wash soap on the hands cleaning points.&nbsp;</p><p>Tissue paper and hand washing soap is necessary for human hygiene.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed it in Kiambere site.&nbsp;</p><p>The observation was on 28/4/22.</p><p>There was no tissue paper in the toilet and a &nbsp;soap of washing hands.&nbsp;</p><p>FT is responsible.&nbsp;</p><p>Below is the evidence attached.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-06', '2022-05-09', '2022-05-27', '2022-06-03', '2022-05-25', 'ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-06 05:38:14', '2022-05-31 22:10:26'),
(316, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-05-06', '934', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Company\'s property', 'Major', '<p>Incorrect position and placing of company\'s property.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed that a black water tank was not placed on a flat surface and a manhole was also positioned on unraised &nbsp;surface.&nbsp;</p><p>Any company\'s property must be managed and maintained well by those who are given access to use for its functions.&nbsp;</p><p>A water tank on a flat surface is protected from damage.&nbsp;</p><p>Placing a manhole on a raised position provide easy management and maintenance of the meter.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed it in Kiambere site.&nbsp;</p><p>Date of observation was 28/4/22 by DFO.</p><p>Water tank was not on a raised surface and the manhole was also not in a raised position.&nbsp;</p><p>FT is responsible.&nbsp;</p><p>Attached is the evidence.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-18', '2022-05-20', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-06 06:03:53', '2022-07-26 17:54:43'),
(317, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-05-06', '439', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Site infrastructure-no reference document', 'Minor', '<p>Lack of door locks in the changing rooms.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;It was observed that there was no door locks to lock the doors during and after changing by the workers.&nbsp;</p><p>It was observed in Kiambere site.&nbsp;</p><p>This was &nbsp;observed by DFO on &nbsp;Thursday 28th April 22.</p><p>The doors of the changing rooms one was observed slightly remaining open and another door had a &nbsp;stick laid on to prevent it from being wide open.&nbsp;</p><p>SLO &nbsp;is &nbsp;responsible/FT.</p><p>The evidence is attached.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-18', '2022-05-20', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-06 20:55:07', '2022-07-26 17:55:30'),
(318, 32, 15, 10, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-05-06', '77', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Company\'s policy ', 'Minor', '<p>Un arranged and torn wall posters.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed that the lining posters hanged on the walls was not straight, lacked space and two posters was torn.&nbsp;</p><p>Observations was on Kiambere site.&nbsp;</p><p>The Observations was on 28/4/22 by DFO.</p><p>The posters hanged on the walls were not upright, lacked space that one poster was on top of another poster.&nbsp;</p><p>SLM Kiambere is responsible/FT.</p><p>The attached is the evidence.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-08', '2022-05-09', '2022-05-27', '2022-06-03', '2022-05-25', 'ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-06 21:30:50', '2022-05-27 19:42:10'),
(319, 32, 15, 10, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-05-06', '8661', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Healthy and safety ', 'Minor', '<p>Waste disposal.&nbsp;</p><p>DFO observed that there was kept &nbsp;dirty worn out polythene sheets, damaged solar battery and old debris lying in the nursery beds and items in a sack which dirty and occupies spaces for nothing.&nbsp;</p><p>This was observed in Kiambere site.&nbsp;</p><p>This was observed on 28/4/22 by DFO.</p><p>The Waste observed was dirt worn out polythene sheets, damaged solar battery, old debris in the nursery beds and items in a sack .</p><p>SLM Kiambere is responsible/FT.</p><p>Evidence is attached.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-08', '2022-05-09', '2022-05-27', '2022-06-03', '2022-05-25', 'ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-06 21:57:43', '2022-08-25 19:45:37'),
