(356, 36, 13, 8, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-05-13', '1692', 'FSC Officer', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'FSC-STD-01-001 (10.10) \"organization shall manage infrastructural development and transport activities\"', 'Minor', '<p>Infrastructure in the management unit not well maintained.</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-26', '2022-06-15', '2023-01-01', '2023-12-31', '2022-06-15', 'We shall handle FSC in uganda when we start it there. In the meantime we shall train the staff progressively and incorporate the principles in our manual.', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To start FSc in kenya first.&nbsp;</div>', '2022-05-13 15:33:32', '2023-02-22 16:51:23'),
