(367, 19, 11, 9, 8, 19, NULL, '2022-05-20', '8032', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Time and attendance', 'Major', '<p>Two employees clocked in late at 8.08am.</p><p>Gideon Benjamin and Ronald Muhkwana clocked in late on 20th May 2022. This was not because they reported late to work but it was the activity that was missing in the devices. The activity appeared late in the devices and the two were clocked in by Herbert Chobola(kit handlers).</p><p>This may lead to them being deducted as a result of inconvenincies they aren’t liable to.</p><p>Pruning less than 2 metres activity for 2pms was in the Friday plan. &nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-05-24', '2022-05-24', '2022-05-27', '2022-06-03', '2022-05-25', 'The auditee got a verbal warning letter for this. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-20 14:24:39', '2022-06-03 13:47:55'),
(368, 5, 22, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2022-05-24', '1873', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Email report from SMN on 21.05.2022', 'Major', '<p>Email from SMN</p><p>Please note that I received a concern from ABL (African Beekeepers LTD) staff who visited NYO site on 18th May 2022 that after assessing the 200 beehives installed in the plantation, 1 brooder and 3 frames were missing. I task security guards to check around the area if the lost properties could be traced but they could not access the area as the bees were still aggressive. I will follow up on this issue and update you appropriately.</p><p>Non Conformance:</p><p>lack of proper care of customer property. In the agreement, BGF was to provide security for the beehives.</p>', 'closed', '2022-07-04', '2022-07-04', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-24 14:23:46', '2022-07-27 15:11:42'),
(369, 19, 22, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2022-05-25', '8634', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Weekly plan', 'Major', '<p>Not conforming to the operations weekly plan</p><p>There have been instances where employees have been clocked in operations activity contrary to the plans.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>1. Clocked in labor not according to the plan.&nbsp;</li><li>2. Activity clocked in is not featured in plan</li></ol><p>Example</p><p>24th May 2022: 5 employees were to be clocked in electic fence maintenance according to plan yet 2 were clocked in.&nbsp;</p><p>24th May 2022: 4 employees were clocked in store construction activity which was not featured in the weekly plan for week 21.</p><p>The non-conformances also occured in week 19, and 20.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-02', '2022-06-15', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-25 12:03:19', '2022-07-27 15:30:05'),
(370, 19, 22, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2022-05-25', '5447', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Site water systems', 'Major', '<p>There was no running water at the toilet area from the start of week 21.</p><p>This was because the suction pipe at the water pump station was covered with sand/silt hence the water water couldn\'t be pumped into the tanks.&nbsp;</p><p>Management of sand/silt at the pump station hasn\'t been put into consideration in the preventive maintenance.&nbsp;</p><p>Attempts to remove silt by the site handyman team did not pay off since sand was recollecting back on the pipe.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-02', '2022-06-15', '2022-07-13', '2022-11-30', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-25 12:48:32', '2023-01-25 16:12:01'),
(371, 19, 22, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2022-05-25', '6370', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Dead donkey', 'Major', '<p>Donkey died out of an incident which could have been avoided.&nbsp;</p><p>1 donkey died on 25th May 2022. &nbsp;The cause of death was established after the donkey was already dead.&nbsp;</p><p>The assistant head of security received the information from the head of security who was on duty the previous day that the donkey sneaked into one of the tents and consumed rice, sugar and flour about ¾, ¾ and ½kg respectively. The donkey died of constipation</p><p>The zip for the tent is not functioning hence the donkey found an easy way into the tent.&nbsp;</p><p>The donkey consumed the items in the evening of 24th May during their return to the stable. Osman Dido was in charge of the Donkeys.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-02', '2022-06-15', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-25 18:10:07', '2022-07-27 15:33:23'),
(372, 19, 22, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2022-05-27', '9019', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Security uniform', 'Major', '<p>Security guard was wearing slippers while at work.</p><p>On 27th May 2022 M&amp;E met Ali Abaharo in slippers while entering the plantations. Security guard should be in full uniform.</p><p>Enquiry from The HOS-Abdulahi Bocha.</p><p>Feedback from the enquiry showed that the HOS was not aware about the security guard in slippers yet he had admitted that he had checked all the security guards and confirmed all were in full uniform contrary to the observation made by the site M&amp;E officer.&nbsp;</p><p>The HOS did follow up after information from the M&amp;E and found out that the security guard was in slippers because he was pricked by thorn. The HOS did not have prior information.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-01', '2022-06-15', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-27 13:05:51', '2022-07-27 15:34:43'),
(373, 19, 22, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2022-05-27', '2822', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Communication', 'Major', '<p>Communication breakdown in the Security team</p><p>With reference to CAR#9019 M&amp;E noted communication breakdown in the security team. &nbsp;</p><p>There is poor communication both vertical, horizontal and diagonal among the security team.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Ali Abaharo did not communicate to the HOS about condition that was not making him fit to wear boots on 27th May 2022.</li><li>Assistant HOS did not duly communicate to the SFM on the condition of the donkey that died on 25th May 2022.</li><li>HOS complaining about security guards not giving information especially on sick leave in the due time.</li><li>Head of security complaining that his assistant is letting him down at work. &nbsp;There is blame game between HOS and his assistant.</li><li>&nbsp;</li></ol>', 'closed', '2022-06-01', '2022-06-15', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-05-27 13:17:51', '2023-01-25 16:12:42'),
(374, 18, 15, 10, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-06-01', '6240', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Methodology for Setting up and Execution of Improved Seedling Production Experiment ', 'Major', '<p>Seedling mortality as a result of root rot.</p><p>The M&amp;E observed three seedlings from treatment E5 in the Efford bed that have been affected by root rot.</p><p>The observation was made on 31/5/2022.</p><p>FT Kiambere is responsible for the implementation of the experiment at a site level.</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-01', '2022-06-03', '2022-06-21', '2022-07-15', '2022-06-15', NULL, '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '2022-06-01 09:24:49', '2023-02-22 16:54:11'),
(375, 18, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-06-01', '2478', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Nursery infrastructure. No reference document', 'Minor', '<p>Broken nursery gate and a damaged water tank.</p><p>The M&amp;E observed one of the nursery gates was broken and the water tank located behind pricking area was damaged &nbsp;at the top.</p><p>The observation was made on 31/5/2022.</p><p>The FT Kiambere is responsible for repair and maintenance of nursery infrastructure.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-01', '2022-06-15', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-01 10:01:14', '2022-07-27 15:35:51');
