(400, 19, 11, 9, 8, 19, NULL, '2022-06-21', '8010', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Installed Bee Hives', 'Major', '<p>Damage of trees by swinging bee hives.&nbsp;</p><p>Some bee hives suspended on trees in compartments A014 and A031 are debacking the trees at the area they come into contact when they swing because of wind.&nbsp;</p><p>The injured parts of the trees may act as entry points of pathogens and also affecting the wood quality.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-27', '2022-06-29', '2022-07-04', '2022-08-31', '2022-07-03', NULL, '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '2022-06-21 17:25:50', '2023-02-22 16:46:53'),
(401, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-06-23', '8660', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Operations - Daily preventive maintenance.', 'Major', '<p>Daily preventive maintenance checklist of motorbike Reg no.KMDU 497Jand KMDU 308S was not filled.</p><p>In week 25 M&amp;E observed that daily PM of motorbike KMDU 497J &amp; KMDU308S were not filled on 21/6/22.Preventive maintenance of every motorbike should be filled, KMEG 825E its PM was filled on 21/6/22.</p><p>FT is responsible in filling the preventive maintenance of the machines.</p><p>Below is the FT report.</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-28', '2022-07-04', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-22', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-23 13:39:32', '2022-07-28 18:55:06'),
(402, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-06-23', '9165', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Health and safety - Housekeeping.', 'Minor', '<p>Cleaning and disinfecting surfaces are not done twice a day in kiambere.</p><p>M&amp;E observed that cleaning and disinfecting of surfaces that are extensively used were cleaned once and time (8:30 -9:00) indicated in the checklist.kiambere site housekeeping checklist states that cleaning and disinfecting surfaces that are extensively used twice a day.</p><p>This was observed in kiambere site &nbsp;on 21/6/22.</p><p>FT is responsible to ensure that cleaning and disinfecting surfaces that are extensively used is done twice a day.</p><p>Attached 21/6/22 kiambere housekeeping checklist.</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-28', '2022-07-04', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-22', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-23 17:02:41', '2022-07-28 21:08:09'),
(403, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-06-23', '8105', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Tools and equipments maintenance.', 'Minor', '<p>A grinder does not have a belt.</p><p>In week 25, date 21/6/22 M&amp;E observed that one grinder in kiambere site does not have a belt.A belt contributes to effectiveness of a grinder failure to which it cannot function.</p><p>FT is responsible in ensuring that tools and equipments are maintained and functional.</p><p>Below is the grinder.</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-28', '2022-07-05', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-22', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-23 17:27:26', '2022-07-28 21:08:39'),
(404, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-06-23', '5635', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Improved seedling production - Job card.', 'Minor', '<p>Inadequate space in a job card.</p><p>Job card has inadequate space to fill daily water consumption in the experiment.</p><p>A book has been used to record the quantity of water used in the experiment.</p><p>M&amp;E observed this on 21/6/22 in kiambere site.</p><p>FT is responsible to ensure that a job card has adequate space to record the quantity of water used to water seedlings.</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-28', '2022-07-05', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', 'in addition; we are developing a digital jobcard', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-23 18:10:52', '2022-07-28 21:09:20'),
(405, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-06-23', '7000', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Security/walkie talkies.', 'Major', '<p>8 walkie talkies are not functinal .</p><p>In week 25 ,date 21/6/22 five walkie talkies were to be used by five security guards during the day.only two were functioning and three were not functioning.The security team used only two walkie talkies during the day.FT and the security guard tested one walkie talkie in the presence of M&amp;E and was not responding/ functioning.FT &nbsp;and the security guard confirmed that 8 walkie talkies were not functioning.</p><p>This was observed on 21/6/22 in &nbsp;kiambere site by M&amp;E.</p><p>FT is responsible for ensuring that all walkie talkies are functional.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-28', '2022-07-05', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-20', '2022-07-13', 'DONE', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-23 21:20:32', '2022-07-28 21:10:52'),
(406, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2022-06-23', '8118', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Grass collection procedure.', 'Minor', '<p>No grass collection procedure.</p><p>On 21/6/22 M&amp;E observed that 4 people came for grass collection in kiambere site.M&amp;E observed them living their IDs at the office kiambere.The four went for grass cutting in comp A010.No other procedures was provided to show other steps in grass collection.</p><p>A procedure shows on how &nbsp;a task is done.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-28', '2022-07-05', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-22', '2022-07-13', 'This has been done and shared with site FT. All procedures are not yet formally approved but are in use.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-23 21:49:15', '2023-01-25 16:13:30'),
(407, 32, 15, 10, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-06-23', '9720', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Improved seedling production measurements -Job card', 'Major', '<p>Seedlings measurements (heights,DBH and roots) &nbsp;results not recorded in a Job card.</p><p>In week 25 M&amp;E &nbsp;observed that the heights and DBH of 240 seedlings from Efford and Traditional beds were measured and the results were recorded in an exercise book.On 13/6/22 FT provided root measurements from an exercise book the dates indicated was 9/6/22.This book was not signed to indicate the person who carried out the measurements.</p><p>A job card must be filled to show work done ,signed by the person who did the work and the date .</p><p>This was observed in kiambere site on 21/6/22 by M&amp;E.</p><p>FT is responsible for ensuring that there is enough Job cards.To ensure that Job cards are filled after every work done(measurements) on an experiment of improved seedling production 2021.</p><p>Attached is an exercise book which root measurement results were recorded.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-28', '2022-06-29', '2022-08-08', '2023-06-30', '2022-07-03', 'we are working on a digital job card. This is also an experiment whose design is not the same as the existing job cards. Records are therefore kept in predisigned forms from the protocol.', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '2022-06-23 23:17:29', '2023-02-22 16:51:58'),
(416, 32, 35, 35, 8, 18, NULL, '2022-06-24', '88508', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Outgrowers manual-Groups certification.', 'Minor', '<p>Two BGF farmers groups have not been issued with BGF certificates.</p><p>The two groups were Mukithyo mukau growers and Kathiani mukau growers.The two groups were from Mumoni ward.</p><p>In week 25 M&amp;E interviewed 4 farmers of Mukithyo mukau growers and 5 farmers of Kathiani mukau growers and they confirmed that they have not been issued with BGF certificates.</p><p>Farmers from Mukithyo mukau growers were:</p><p>Josephine Mwathi Muthui id 12624469 phone no.0791491424,</p><p>Joseph Musyoka Mutemi id 26245146 phone no.0718169996,(chair person),</p><p>Mbathe Mwinzi id 3517787 phone no.0789489866,</p><p>Kivivia Mutemi 3517789 phone no.0718169996 Representative(son),</p><p>From kathiani mukau growers were:</p><p>Kyambi Mukinya id 3734604 phone no.0759149971,</p><p>Mukel Kilonso id 21211600 phone no.0725984013,</p><p>Mutei Masya id 11208134 phone no.0704625147,</p><p>Mutei Musili id 3734824 phone no.0714612804,(chair person)</p><p>Peter Musyoka Mwinza id 16063825 phone no.0719248052.</p><p>SMFP is responsible to ensure that all registered BGF mukau groups have been issued with BGF certificates.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-06-27', '2022-06-29', '2022-07-04', '2022-07-15', '2022-07-03', 'Ongoing', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-24 23:03:07', '2022-07-18 22:36:24'),
