(420, 32, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-28', '83148', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Head Office', 'Communications', 'Plantation Management.', 'Minor', '<p>Not adhering to the weekly plan.</p><p>In week 26 kiambere site forestry plan,tree counting was scheduled to be done in compartment A013 by 5 PM(s) on 28/6/22 but it was verified that the activity was carried out in compartment A016,A018 and A019 by 5 PM(s).</p><p>There was no change of plan on the notice board.</p><p>This was observed on 28/6/22 in kiambere site by M&amp;E.</p><p>Attached is the field data as on 28/6/22.</p>', 'closed', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>There seems still to be a huge communication problem between HO managers and the site responsible\'s.<br>Further action after the primary auditee\'s response.</div>', '', NULL, '2022-06-29 01:01:39', '2022-07-13 15:36:14'),
(421, 32, 15, 9, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-06-28', '1494', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Plantation Management.', 'Minor', '<p>Not adhering to the weekly plan.</p><p>In week 26 kiambere site forestry plan,tree counting was scheduled to be done in comp A013 by 5 PM(s) on 28/6/22 but it was verified that the activity was carried out in comp A016,A018 and A019 by 5 PM(s).</p><p>There was no change of plan on the notice board.</p><p>This was observed on 28/6/22 in kiambere site by M&amp;E.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-07-02', '2022-07-12', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-20', '2022-07-13', NULL, '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '2022-06-29 01:01:40', '2023-02-22 16:46:12'),
(422, 32, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-28', '61138', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Communications Department', 'Head Office', 'Communications', 'Improved seedling production kia 2021.', 'Minor', '<p>Not adhering to improved seedling production kia 2021 plan.</p><p>The experiment of improved seedling production kia 2021 plan on activity schedule,seedlings establishment was supposed to have been done and watering of established seedlings once a week should be on going but the seedlings are still in the nursery and measurements(Height,DBH) taken on a weekly basis.</p><p>This was observed in week 26 in kiambere site by M&amp;E.</p><p>FT in kiambere is responsible in ensuring that improved seedling production kia 2021 plan is adhered to.</p><p>Attach is the evidence photo.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Has been addressed by EDF. However, the auditee\'s response to the above CAR is long overdue.</div>', '', NULL, '2022-06-29 02:43:40', '2022-07-13 15:36:34'),
(423, 32, 15, 9, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-06-28', '9478', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Project plan for improved soil for mukau production.', 'Minor', '<p>Establishment of project plan for improved soil for mukau production has not started.</p><p>According to project plan for improved soil for mukau production establishment was supposed to have started on 03/05/22 but as at 28/6/22 seedling measurements(Height&amp;DBH) was taking place in the nursery.</p><p>This was observed in week 26 in kiambere site by M&amp;E.</p><p>FT in kiambere is responsible in ensuring that project plans of improved soil for mukau production is adhered to.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-07-02', '2022-07-12', '2022-07-13', '2022-08-05', '2022-07-13', 'The establishment shall be done when the project plan is approved.', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '<div>To be closed.</div>', '2022-06-29 02:43:41', '2023-02-22 16:40:03'),
(424, 32, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-28', '32117', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Head Office', 'Communications', 'Daily preventive maintenance checklist.', 'Major', '<p>Daily preventive maintenance checklist of motorbike Reg No.KMEG825E &nbsp;and brush cutters not filled.</p><p>In week 26 M&amp;E observed that daily preventive maintenance checklist of motorbike KMEG825E-53260km and &nbsp;brush cutters were not filled.A preventive maintenance checklist of every machine should be filled daily to improve reliability and life of the equipment.</p><p>FT did not provide PM to M&amp;E on 28/6/22.</p><p>This was observed in kiambere site on 28/6/22.</p><p>FT is responsible in filling and updating daily preventive maintenance checklist of machines in kiambere site.</p>', 'closed', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>7th of July: Expecting an answer from the auditee before DDC\'s possible intervention.</div>', '', NULL, '2022-06-29 03:16:26', '2022-07-13 15:36:55'),
(425, 32, 15, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2022-06-28', '9124', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Operations-Daily preventive maintenance checklist.', 'Major', '<p>Daily preventive maintenance of motorbike Reg No.KMEG825E &nbsp;and brush cutters not filled.</p><p>In week 26 M&amp;E observed that daily preventive maintenance checklist of motorbike KMEG825E-53260km and &nbsp;brush cutters were not filled.A preventive maintenance of every machine should be filled daily to improve reliability and life of the equipment.</p><p>FT did not provide PM to M&amp;E on 28/6/22.</p><p>This was observed in kiambere site on 28/6/22.</p><p>FT is responsible in filling and updating daily preventive maintenance of machines in kiambere site.</p>', 'closed', '2022-07-02', '2022-07-05', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-29 03:16:26', '2022-07-28 21:15:03'),
