(427, 32, 15, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2022-06-29', '1461', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Health and safety-Occupational accident/disease.', 'Major', '<p>DOSH form not provided .</p><p>On 28/6/22 M&amp;E was not provided with a DOSH form by FT to check on a flow chart of addressing and reporting the site incidences to Human Resource until a DOSH form is filled.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E in week 26 &nbsp;in kiambere site.</p><p>FT is responsible to ensure that there\'s a flow chart on how site incidences are addressed.</p>', 'closed', '2022-07-02', '2022-07-05', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-31', '2022-07-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-29 04:45:54', '2022-07-28 21:16:11'),
(428, 5, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-29', '76652', 'FOD & Quality Coordinator', 'Communications Department', 'Head Office', 'Communications', 'Guidelines for Minutes taking and timelines shared by DDC', 'Minor', '<p>Late submission of NYO Health and safety Minutes for a meeting held on 25th June 2022 to DDC and DDHR.</p><p>The minutes of meetings held on a Saturday are submitted latest of or before end of day of the Monday that follows, where the Monday does not fall on a holiday. In our case, the minutes should have been shared on Monday the 27th June which was not the case, until a reminder was sent by DDHR.</p><p>No communication that the minutes will be late by the Team in NYO</p>', 'closed', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Has been addressed by DDC, DDHR, and FOD week 25<br>7th July: No response from the auditee in the system.</div>', '', NULL, '2022-06-29 12:50:45', '2022-07-13 15:37:34'),
