(436, 32, 15, 9, 8, 32, NULL, '2022-06-30', '5572', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Plantation management.', 'Minor', '<p>Tree counting was not done in compartment A013.</p><p>According to week26 forestry plans tree counting was supposed to be carried out in compartment A013 on 28/6/22 but tree counting was done in compartment A016,018&amp;019.</p><p>There was no amendments of week26 forestry plan on the notice board on 28/6/22.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E in kiambere site in week26.</p><p>FT is responsible in ensuring that forestry plans are adhered to.</p><p>Attached are the field results of date 28/6/22.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2022-07-02', '2022-07-12', '2022-07-13', '2022-07-16', '2022-07-12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-30 16:46:24', '2022-07-18 22:35:55');
