(549, 19, 11, 9, NULL, NULL, 1505, '2023-02-11', '5727', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tast rate achievements ', 'Major', '<p>Mechanical pruning targets for 10 pms was not achieved.</p><p>Pruning was done in compartments C079 on 9th February 2023. The overall pruning target was 1000trees and 966 trees were pruned. 3 pms out of the 10 pms did not achieve their targets.&nbsp;</p><p>Shadrach Lughanji and Abdula Salim achieved 87 trees each while Walter Oduor achieved 90 trees out of 100.</p>', 'closed', '2023-02-13', '2023-02-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>It has to be checked if there was timely communication and if the task was adjusted manually.</div>', '<div>Agree with DDC comment</div>', '<div>it is work in progress and there is good improvement. M&amp;E is monitoring well.</div>', '2023-02-11 15:28:42', '2023-05-11 15:35:49'),
(550, 32, 35, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-13', '6615', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Operations', 'HEALTH AND SAFETY', 'Major', '<p>Expired items in First Aid Kit. The following items have expired: Steri Swabs 2pieces, SumBow Eye Pad 6pieces, Gauze Bandage Triangular 2pieces, Cotton Crepe Bandages 2pieces, Adhesive Bandage 3pieces, Allerta(Cetirizine Tablets)50tablets, Methylated Spirit a quarter of 500ml and Biomol(Pacacetamol Tablets).</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E in 7F on 13/02/2023.</p>', 'closed', '2023-02-14', '2023-02-23', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>To be bought in Nairobi<br>Monitor weekly the expiry dates</div>', '', '', '<div>To be bought in Nairobi<br>Monitor weekly the expiry dates<br>To closely monitor the disposal of expired medicines<br><br></div>', '2023-02-13 13:15:21', '2023-05-11 15:40:01'),
(551, 32, 35, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-16', '5493', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Operations', 'HEALTH AND SAFETY', 'Major', '<p>There is no drinking water in 7Forks office.&nbsp;</p><p>This is contrary to a phrase in ABSTRACT OF THE OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ACT,2007, which says an adequate supply of wholesome drinking water must be provided.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 16/02/2023.</p>', 'closed', '2023-02-18', '2023-02-23', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>This is solved already</div>', '', '', '<div>This is solved already</div>', '2023-02-17 03:00:50', '2023-05-11 15:40:30'),
(552, 32, 35, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-18', '6772', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Operations', 'PREVENTIVE MAINTENANCE APPLICATION', 'Major', '<p>Machines/ motorbikes KMDU 296S,KMDW 941E,KMDW951E,KMEH 888B &amp;KMFB 001T were not scheduled for maintenance on 17/2/2023 in 7F.</p>', 'closed', '2023-02-18', '2023-02-23', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-18 17:41:48', '2023-05-11 15:41:44'),
(553, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-22', '7677', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'HEALTH AND SAFETY', 'Major', '<p>There was a leaking water tank in the nursery.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 22/02/2023</p><p>See the attach evidence.</p>', 'closed', '2023-02-23', '2023-02-27', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>This has been addressed.</div>', '', '', '2023-02-22 13:52:14', '2023-06-22 15:11:13'),
(554, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-22', '8233', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'PPE MANAGEMENT POLICY', 'Minor', '<p>Personal items were left in the changing rooms. 3 out of the 4 changing rooms had home clothes and slippers which is contrary to PPE MANAGEMENT POLICY which states that home clothes or any personal item should not be left on the changing room.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 22/02/2023.</p>', 'closed', '2023-02-23', '2023-02-27', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>A place to Hang home Clothes has been done in KIA and NYO. Pending is DKL</div>', '', '', '<div>ok</div>', '2023-02-22 14:08:35', '2023-06-22 15:12:34'),
(555, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-22', '1893', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'HEALTH AND SAFETY', 'Major', '<p>A PMS by the name Shadrack Masavi did not wear leather glove on his left hand.</p><p>The PMS was doing manual cleaning in compartment &nbsp;A005. After the interrogation the PMS said that he was issued with right hand glove only.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 22/2/2023</p>', 'closed', '2023-02-23', '2023-02-27', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-22 20:10:24', '2023-06-22 15:14:16'),
(556, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-02-22', '6788', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'PPE MANAGEMENT POLICY', 'Major', '<p>Two security guards were in gumboots instead of security boots while at work.</p><p>The two security guards were : Mathew Munyoki and Patrick Muthengi. It didn\'t rain on the previous day therefore there was no need of wearing gumboots.</p><p>&nbsp; After the interrogations Mathew Munyoki said,``My safety boots needs to be put a gum &nbsp;and I had informed the head of security\".&nbsp;</p><p>Patrick Muthengi said ``Gumboots are the best to be worn during patrols in the plantation because it prevents piercing from ``Unyoe\"- a grass with sharp pointed ends\".</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 22nd,Feb,2023.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-02-23', '2023-02-27', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>Forestry have put in the Plan to do strip cleaning to allow for workers to do patrols.<br>Not wearing the right PEE is not acceptable and it is a breach to the health and safety regulations.</div>', '', '', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-02-23 00:14:34', '2023-06-22 15:21:01'),
(557, 28, 28, 29, 5, 38, NULL, '2023-02-24', '964', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'PPE MANAGEMENT POLICY ON SITES', 'Minor', '<p>In Dokolo Site, there is no changing room for workers which is contrary to the PPE MANAGEMENT POLICY ON SITES, Revision number: 003, point 3 (a), which says, “the site shall have separate changing rooms for gents and ladies”.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-02-27', '2023-02-27', '2023-08-02', '2023-08-31', '2023-08-02', NULL, '<div>To be done by 30th July.<br>To be done together with a place for keeping home clothes</div>', '<div>Operations are aware. This is long overdue</div>', '<div>Long overdue. Operations department to Fastrack it.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-02-24 15:35:20', '2023-08-02 17:31:18'),
(558, 19, 22, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-01', '345', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Drinking water', 'Major', '<p>Drinking water has a bad odour and taste</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;EO on 28th February 2023 and situation is negatively advancing as checked on 1/03/2022.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-02', '2023-03-06', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-01 13:17:58', '2023-06-22 15:29:05'),
(559, 32, 26, 29, NULL, NULL, 1693, '2023-03-02', '2158', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Program', '7 Forks', 'Operations', 'PPE MANAGEMENT POLICY', 'Major', '<p>The house keeper was doing cleaning in 7F office without the required PPE.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 02/03/2023.</p><p>Attach is the evidence</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-06', '2023-03-06', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>The IPR is done and will be bought ASAP</div>', '', '', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-02 20:53:29', '2023-06-22 15:30:17'),
(560, 19, 11, 9, NULL, NULL, 1707, '2023-03-04', '6242', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Health and Safety', 'Major', '<p>PMS operating brush cutter while pruning trees in Compartment B002 on 2nd and 3rd of March were not in gloves.</p><p>The gloves are in stock. M&amp;EO counted 8 pairs and 1 piece of red leather gloves. PMS were not issued with gloves according to the issuance records for the dates mentioned.</p><p>M&amp;EO asked PMS why they didn\'t have the gloves and the answer was that the gloves that are available are over size and do not provide grip hence they chose not to receive the gloves.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-07', '2023-03-07', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>To be purchased. IPR is in the system.<br>Agree with the DDC.</div>', '<div>This should have been communicated and addressed before the task.</div>', '<div>Operations department to Fastrack on purchase of the right size gloves.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-04 17:51:04', '2023-06-29 15:24:35'),
(561, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, 1829, '2023-03-15', '1236', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'PPE MANAGEMENT POLICY', 'Major', '<p>One PMS Kyalo Muneni had a worn out PPE (overall) while he was doing boundary dermarcation and row marking in compartment A025.</p><p>After interrogation the PMS said that,``The last PPE replacement was done in February 2022 ‘’. This is contrary to PPE Management Policy which states that, `` The lifespan of overalls and gumboots shall be one year\'\'.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 15/03/2023.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>PMS have been issued with overalls meant for casuals and they are ok.<br>The IPR for their PPE is also in the system and will be addressed in due course</div>', '<div>This has been addressed</div>', '<div>Staff should ensure that they maintain the assigned PPEs in good condition at all times. In the meantime all the permanent staff have been issued with green overalls for use.</div>', '<div>ok</div>', '2023-03-16 00:27:59', '2023-06-22 15:36:57'),
(562, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-15', '6476', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Site structures (Nursery fence)', 'Minor', '<p>One post of the nursery fence near the nursery gate is sagging. This has made a length of around 3metres nursery fence to bend.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 15/03/2023.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>Adressed in another CAR<br>If it recurs it will be addressed differently.</div>', '<div>This has been worked on.</div>', '<div>This has been addressed.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 00:38:43', '2023-07-27 15:17:33'),
(563, 19, 22, 29, NULL, NULL, 1845, '2023-03-16', '7528', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Security reporting of observation of incidences ', 'Major', '<p>Fire incidences and human activities in Compartment D091 and D092 found in Block 7 had not been reported.</p><p>There were bomas in D091 which was evidence of long stay in D091. The impact of fire which burned greater parts of D092 and D091 was from fire that had already occurred and was not reported.</p><p>This was observed on 15th March 2023 by both M&amp;EO, SLM and security guard who had been assigned in that Block on 15th March.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-23', '2023-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>Addressed in another CAR</div>', '<div>This was addressed.</div>', '<div>This was addressed.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 10:21:28', '2023-07-27 15:19:43'),
(564, 19, 22, 29, NULL, NULL, 1846, '2023-03-16', '6666', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Reporting off occurrences', 'Major', '<p>Security giving incorrect reports</p><p>Fire incidences which occurred in D091 and D092 was not reported. The reports from Security guards about fire that was observed on Sunday 12th March 2023 was that the fire was far and didn\'t reach the plantation. This means fire at D091 and D092 and the activities were either not seen or seen and not reported. Therefore there is high chance that the fire went off naturally. &nbsp;Nothing about fire or activities in D091/D092 was reported in the OB on dates 13th and 14th of March.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-22', '2023-03-22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>Addressed in another CAR</div>', '<div>This was addressed.</div>', '<div>This was addressed.</div>', '<div>ok</div>', '2023-03-16 10:33:43', '2023-07-27 15:20:42'),
(565, 19, 22, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-16', '1583', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Health and Safety', 'Major', '<p>Team consisting of 3 pms doing manual cleaning at F029 on 15th March 2023 did not have hand gloves. From CAR #6242 about the mechanical pruning team not using the available gloves, the SFM in his root cause statements stated that the available gloves were purchased for use in manual cleaning activities.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-22', '2023-03-22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>Addressed in another CAR.<br>Gloves are of same size.</div>', '<div>This has been addressed.</div>', '<div>Addressed in another CAR.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 10:47:33', '2023-07-27 15:22:23'),
(566, 19, 11, 9, 8, 19, NULL, '2023-03-16', '8297', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Health and Safety', 'Major', '<p>Team consisting of 3 pms doing manual cleaning at F029 on 15th March 2023 did not have hand gloves. From CAR #6242 about the mechanical pruning team not using the available gloves, the SFM in his root cause statements stated that the available gloves were purchased for use in manual cleaning activities.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-22', '2023-03-22', '2023-07-01', '2023-07-31', '2023-06-29', NULL, '<div>1. Lack of taking responsibility by the SM to ensure the PPE policy is followed.<br>2. Lack of communication by the SM to the supervisor to immediately address the issue.</div>', '<div>An explanation of the importance of wearing PPE to the site responsible and from the site responsible to site the staff to be given and be adhered to</div>', '<div>Its mandatory for all staff to wear the right PPEs at all times when doing any activity. This an excuse.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 10:47:34', '2023-07-27 15:24:05'),
(567, 18, 29, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-16', '1865', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Nyongoro site visit-OM Report 21st Feb-24th Feb 2023', 'Minor', '<ol><li>Communication breakdown-Vertical communication</li></ol><p>Communication is still an issue, security meeting which was supposed to take place in day 1 was postponed to day 2 because all the guards did not get the communication. Only 50% of the guards showed up in day one.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>Meetings are happening as expected. If not communication is done to the guards.</div>', '<div>This now okay</div>', '<div>Addressed by DDC.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 14:57:28', '2023-07-27 15:26:50'),
(568, 18, 29, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-16', '5734', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Nyongoro site visit-OM Report 21st Feb-24th Feb 2023', 'Major', '<p>Poor handing over by the Former SLM.</p><p>&nbsp;Area of concerns from the SLM</p><p>&nbsp;Hand over was not properly done by former SLM.</p><p>Stock verification was not done for all stock at site he only verified sensitive items like walkies talkies as the former SLM was in a hurry to leave.</p><p>Provision of Laptop to the mechanic to assist with reports for maintenance app.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>People being handed over have to check and confirm before the other party leaves and if there is a problem, should be communicated to HR. The rest are excuses.</div>', '<div>Handover procedures should be adhered to.</div>', '<div>Thats an excuse we have systems with the transition process before a staff leaves.</div>', '', '2023-03-16 14:59:48', '2023-07-27 15:30:51'),
(569, 18, 29, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-16', '6198', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Nyongoro site visit-OM Report 21st Feb-24th Feb 2023', 'Minor', '<p>No security guard at the gate.</p><p>We didn’t have a guard at the gate it was opened by Emmanuel Katana who was not on duty he was coming for the security meeting.</p><p>The guard who was manning the gate showed up later from the nursery area.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>The gate should be closed all times when the guard is patrolling in the nursery.</div>', '<div>Security schedules to be respected</div>', '<div>The security guards to be trained on being vigilant at all times.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 15:02:19', '2023-07-27 15:34:34'),
(570, 18, 29, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-03-16', '722', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Nyongoro site visit-OM Report 21st Feb-24th Feb 2023.', 'Minor', '<p>Site structure-control room.</p><p>The padlock is not functional. It permanently locked itself cannot be opened.&nbsp;</p><p>Control room solar panel frame has rusted it needs painting.&nbsp;</p><p>Solar panel frame is not welded somebody can easily remove the solar</p>', 'follow up', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', '2023-08-31', '2023-09-08', '2023-08-31', 'Check for implementation', '<div>Implemented</div>', '<div>Overtaken</div>', '<div>Already addressed.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 15:04:49', '2023-08-31 17:33:11'),
(571, 18, 29, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-03-16', '356', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Nyongoro site visit-OM Report 21st Feb-24th Feb 2023', 'Minor', '<p>Site structure-Garage store.</p><p>Very untidy, it needs a lot of cleaning and arrangement.</p><p>Some boxes are attacked by termites destroying them completely.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', '2023-08-31', '2023-09-29', '2023-08-31', NULL, '<div>Continuous Maintenance of structures and proper housekeeping</div>', '<div>The housekeeper to be guided to ensure all areas are cleaned and properly organized. Supervision is key also&nbsp;</div>', '<div>Cleaning and maintenace is being done and the housekeeper is supervised by the SLR</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 15:08:13', '2023-09-07 14:44:58'),
(572, 18, 29, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-03-16', '4136', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Nyongoro site visit-OM Report 21st Feb-24th Feb 2023', 'Major', '<p>Plantation hygiene.</p><p>Emmanuel Katana: There is urgent need for plantation cleaning and road maintenance for their own safety and easy patrol in the plantation.</p><p>The plantation is very busy cleaning is urgently needed e.g., compartment E089.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', '2023-08-31', '2023-12-31', '2023-08-31', NULL, '<div>Cleaning is on-going</div>', '<div>Implementation ongoing.</div>', '<div>Cleaning and maintenance is ongoing.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 15:12:21', '2023-08-31 17:35:19'),
(573, 18, 9, 9, 8, 19, NULL, '2023-03-16', '2784', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Plantation Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Nyongoro site visit-OM Report 21st Feb-24th Feb 2023', 'Major', '<p>Plantation hygiene.</p><p>Emmanuel Katana: There is urgent need for plantation cleaning and road maintenance for their own safety and easy patrol in the plantation.</p><p>The plantation is very busy cleaning is urgently needed e.g., compartment E089.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-17', '2023-07-01', '2023-07-31', '2023-06-29', NULL, '<div>This has been overtaken by events. cleaning commenced.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>Forestry is addressing it. Cleaning updates to be given.</div>', '<div>To be addressed by forestry.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 15:12:22', '2023-08-02 16:15:32'),
(574, 18, 29, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-03-16', '7054', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Nyongoro site visit-OM Report 21st Feb-24th Feb 2023', 'Minor', '<p>Health and Safety- hygiene</p><p>Guards are not utilizing the drum for dirty clothes; some dirty clothes were put in a crate instead of the drum and the drum for dirty clothes had clean clothes.</p><p>We still have guards putting their uniforms in their bags instead of crates provided e.g Mwachinga changawa.&nbsp;</p><p>Most of the guards’ crates were disorganized, a few had their crates neatly folded e.g Maulid said and Hussein kani.</p><p>We have many old unused security boots which needs to be disposed.</p><p>The office is not clean the housekeeper is under-utilized. The office walls, windows and floor were very dusty.</p><p>One office chair for SMP(Stephen) was broken and moved to the store.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-03-17', '2023-03-20', '2023-08-31', '2023-09-08', '2023-08-31', NULL, '<div>This has been addressed. We keep monitoring</div>', '<div>This has been addressed.</div>', '<div>Already addressed.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-16 15:14:56', '2023-08-31 17:37:50'),
(575, 4, 28, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2023-03-21', '336', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'MTM Dokolo site visit', 'Major', '<p>Failing to report to work without authorization and not informing supervisor/HOD/ or DDHR&nbsp;</p>', 'follow up', '2023-03-23', '2023-03-24', '2023-08-31', '2023-09-01', '2023-08-31', NULL, '<div>Already Addressed</div>', '<div>This was addressed.</div>', '<div>The SLM left&nbsp;</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-21 13:32:38', '2023-08-31 17:38:36'),
(576, 4, 28, 29, 5, 38, NULL, '2023-03-21', '9481', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Major', '<p>Worn-out chairs and table: The candidates we interviewed were sitting on broken-down seats and using a worn-out table, which reflected poorly on the company. Also, the seats we were sitting on were in need of repair.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-03-23', '2023-03-24', '2023-08-31', '2023-09-30', '2023-08-31', NULL, '<div>This has been addressed by bringing the chairs that were in Dokolo town office.&nbsp;<br>The SLOs to be checking and taking action.</div>', '<div>This was addressed. In Future, the Site responsible have to be more vigilant and ensure the site is in order.</div>', '<div>Already addressed.SLO/M to ensure that all the company property is well maintained and in good condition.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-21 13:54:02', '2023-08-31 17:41:53'),
(577, 4, 13, 8, 8, 38, NULL, '2023-03-21', '6355', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Major', '<p>Worn-out chairs and table: The candidates we interviewed were sitting on broken-down seats and using a worn-out table, which reflected poorly on the company. Also, the seats we were sitting on were in need of repair.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-22', '2023-04-13', '2023-07-01', '2023-07-06', '2023-06-29', NULL, '<div>Addressed by operations.</div>', '<div>This has been addressed.</div>', '<div>This has been addressed.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-21 13:54:03', '2023-08-02 16:16:01'),
(578, 19, 11, 9, 8, 19, NULL, '2023-03-21', '662', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree stock verification', 'Major', '<p>There are still variances in the tree stock reports obtained from &nbsp;tree counting exercise.</p><p>M&amp;EO did recount for rows which had bigger variances in the compartments A049, A064, A014 &nbsp;and A033 on 8th March 2023.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-22', '2023-03-22', '2023-07-01', '2023-08-31', '2023-06-29', NULL, '<div>1. Mandatory daily checks and follow up on the figures by the HO Manager. This will oblige the site team to do the tree counting correctly.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>Tree counting and giving accurate figures is a crucial task that should be taken more seriously. Daily monitoring is required.</div>', '<div>Constant monitoring, timely communication and supervision of every activity is key to the right results. Its unacceptable to give wrong reports as they are used for decision making.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-21 13:55:00', '2023-08-02 16:18:34'),
(579, 16, 5, 29, 5, 38, NULL, '2023-03-22', '3375', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'FOD', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Dokolo site visit(27th Feb to 3rd March 2023)', 'Major', '<p>PPE policy compliance: Lack of compliance to the PPE policy</p><ul><li>a).Some overalls were torn, faded and needed to be discarded but were still in the PPE store and were issued to workers.</li><li>b).Permanent staff go home with their overalls to clean.(SMN and FTN)</li><li>c).There is no place designated for keeping home clothes after changing.</li><li>d).The riding clothes and other permanent staff PPEs are not numbered.</li><li>e).The repair of torn overalls is not neatly done. They just put patches which are visible and ugly.</li><li>f).Returned PPEs for the AAs who left are stored in the SLM office instead of the PPE store and had been covered by dust and mold.</li><li>g).We don’t have changing rooms.</li></ul>', 'follow up', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-29', '2023-08-31', '2023-12-31', '2023-08-31', NULL, '<div>Implemented except for the changing rooms which is also in another CAR</div>', '<div>Implementation ongoing</div>', '<div>Most things already addressed.FOD to work on having the changing rooms.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 13:58:37', '2023-08-31 17:43:07'),
(580, 16, 5, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2023-03-22', '1194', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'FOD', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Dokolo Site visit (27th Feb to 3rd March)', 'Major', '<ol><li>Maintenance of Company property;</li><li><strong>a).Clocking devices:&nbsp;</strong>There is poor storage and handling of the clocking devices. They are put in an area where there is constant movement and can easily fall.</li><li>b).Tablet for recording the security occurrences had no cover and had been kept at the crates.</li></ol>', 'follow up', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-29', '2023-09-07', '2023-12-30', '2023-09-07', NULL, '<div>We will have a stand alone Clocking device fixed on the wall which should be synchronized with the activities. FOD and EDF to write TOR.<br>The cover were purchased.</div>', '<div>The site responsible should ensure company property is taken care of and well maintained.</div>', '<div>To look at the possibililty of having the device at the wall instead of the portable devices and only have the manual device for answering the random calls.</div>', '<div>That is the right direction. should be implemented as soon as possible, according to the cost.<br>To make terms of reference and obtain a quotation.</div>', '2023-03-22 14:02:00', '2023-09-07 18:14:48'),
(581, 4, 8, 8, 8, 18, NULL, '2023-03-22', '787', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Major', '<ol><li>Confusion among the farmers on BGF and YICAFA, where some farmers thought it was the same organization.&nbsp;</li></ol>', 'closed', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-13', '2023-07-01', '2023-07-07', '2023-06-29', NULL, '<div>1. It is the responsibility of the AAs to ensure that the farmers get the correct information about our farmers\' program. The relationship between us and YICAFA. The SM should to also constantly remind his team and follow up to ensure the AAS have relayed clear and correct information about our program and partners.</div>', '<div>EDF to give an explanation of our partnership with YICAFA to SMD, Who will, in turn, explain it to the AAs.</div>', '<div>Dokolo team should be explained clearly and be in a position to explain to the farmers the difference between YICAFA and BGF.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 14:47:31', '2023-08-24 18:04:26'),
(582, 4, 13, 8, 8, 38, NULL, '2023-03-22', '5291', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Major', '<ol><li>Confusion among the farmers on BGF and YICAFA, where some farmers thought it was the same organization.</li></ol>', 'closed', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-13', '2023-07-03', '2023-12-31', '2023-06-29', NULL, '<div>1. It is the responsibility of the AAs to ensure that the farmers get the correct information about our farmers\' program. The relationship between us and YICAFA. The SM must also constantly remind his team and follow up to ensure the AAS have relayed clear and correct information about our program and partners. (Also addressed in the previous CAR)</div>', '<div>EDF to give an explanation of our partnership with YICAFA to SMD, Who will, in turn, explain it to the AAs.</div>', '<div>Dokolo team should be explained clearly and be in a position to explain to the farmers the difference between YICAFA and BGF.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 14:47:32', '2023-08-02 16:24:59'),
(583, 4, 8, 8, 8, 38, NULL, '2023-03-22', '7171', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'SITE VISIT DOKOLO', 'Major', '<ol><li>The radio talk show, publicity is more on YICAFA than BGF.</li></ol>', 'closed', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-13', '2023-07-03', '2023-08-31', '2023-06-29', NULL, '<div>1. The radio talk show schedules must be adhered to. There must also be a talk by the SM with YICAFA representative to emphasize this.<br>2. HOD to have a talk with MR. Odwe to address the issue.</div>', '<div>HOD to have a meeting with Mr Odwe.<br>Issues to be addressed should be discussed and clearly outlined before the radio talk show.<br>A meeting with BGF and YICAFA representative before the radio talk show.</div>', '<div>Agree with DDC</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 14:58:37', '2023-09-07 14:59:18'),
(584, 4, 28, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-22', '2917', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'DOKOLO SITE VISIT', 'Minor', '<p>Using local language that not everyone is conversant with at the site.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-23', '2023-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>This has been solved from HR perspective and the problem is no longer there.</div>', '<div>Local language should not be used as a way to discriminate, which was the case at times.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>We have a policy on communication at the workplace.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 15:05:20', '2023-09-07 15:04:38'),
(585, 4, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-22', '8764', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Major', '<p>Giving false information to farmers as a way to encourage them to enroll</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-22', '2023-04-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>This has now been addressed by the new site manager.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>I agree with the managers\' corrective action.</div>', '<div>Giving false information is misleading and its uncceptable.<br><br><br></div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 15:07:08', '2023-09-07 15:09:43');
INSERT INTO `audits` (`id`, `user_id`, `response_id`, `manager_id`, `hod_id`, `followup_id`, `checklist_id`, `date`, `number`, `auditor`, `auditee`, `site`, `department`, `clause`, `checkbox`, `report`, `status`, `response_date`, `manager_date`, `followup_date`, `followup_end_date`, `hod_date`, `comment`, `mt_comment`, `communication_comment`, `hr_comment`, `final_comment`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(586, 4, 5, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2023-03-22', '5630', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'FOD', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Minor', '<p>Security requested for introduction to the govt offices.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-29', '2023-08-14', '2023-08-31', '2023-08-02', 'This has been addressed', '<div>The letter was done and delivered to relevant authorities.</div>', '<div>Operations are addressing it.</div>', '<div>Done.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 15:11:41', '2023-09-07 15:12:26'),
(587, 4, 8, 8, 8, 38, NULL, '2023-03-22', '1036', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Minor', '<p>AAs love to feel appreciated, so sometimes a phone call or telling an individual he has done a good job during a meeting lifts their spirits and motivates them.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-13', '2023-07-19', '2023-12-31', '2023-07-19', NULL, '', '<div>Excellent performance should be acknowledged. Simply telling a staff&nbsp; \'good job\' it can boost their morale and encourage others to follow suit.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-22 15:16:33', '2023-08-24 18:05:15'),
(588, 4, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-22', '7499', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Major', '<ol><li>There was a farmer who was cutting down the trees, but this would have been easily and quickly addressed if someone had talked to him</li></ol>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-22', '2023-04-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>1. Continuous training of the farmer groups and follow-up.<br>2. Setting up a saw mill in future.</div>', '<div>Forestry is working on having all farmers in groups as this will encourage a sense of accountability. There should be a plan/strategy to ensure we keep in touch with all farmers also.<br><br></div>', '<div>Procedures have been put in place to address this.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 15:19:08', '2023-09-07 15:19:19'),
(589, 4, 28, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-22', '9450', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Minor', '<p>SMD is usually not aware of the IPR that are raised.</p>', 'closed', '2023-03-23', '2023-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>This has been addressed from HR perspective and the operations are now Smooth. All communications about the site for other departments are now done to the site manager.</div>', '<div>DDHR to be consulted.</div>', '<div>This has been addressed.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-03-22 15:21:04', '2023-09-07 15:23:27'),
(590, 4, 8, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-22', '2690', 'Deputy Director Communications', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Dokolo site visit', 'Major', '<ul><li>Provision of cassava cuttings (when questioned they don’t what to tell the farmers as they don’t know the agreements between BGF and YICAFA.</li></ul>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>AAs represent the company. in case of any questions, they are not able to answer they should inform the farmer that they will consult and give feedback. This question should have been raised a long time ago and feedback given</div>', '', '', '2023-03-22 15:24:08', '2023-04-19 17:52:35'),
(591, 16, 8, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '9483', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Dokolo site report', 'Major', '<ol><li>Staff used to clock in and then leave the office to go have breakfast or carry out personal errands.</li></ol>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>It is unfortunate that this used to happen. Monitoring should still be done to ensure it does not recur.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 14:47:19', '2023-04-19 17:42:27'),
(592, 8, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '5543', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Report by EDF from the Dokolo visit', 'Major', '<p>The dimension of the seedling beds is 1 meter by 10 meters each. However, the number of tubes in each bed is different despite having same dimensions.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-24', '2023-04-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Forestry to address this.&nbsp;</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 14:47:52', '2023-04-19 16:59:05'),
(593, 8, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '6962', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'EDF report ', 'Major', '<p>Massive use of glyphosate because of late intervention in weeding.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-24', '2023-04-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Need for proper planning to avoid misuse of company resources.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 14:50:17', '2023-04-19 16:54:36'),
(594, 16, 5, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '7894', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'FOD', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Dokolo site report', 'Major', '<ul><li>SLM &nbsp;went to the office on Sunday 26th Feb without authorization, and while there, broke the clocking in device.</li><li>&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Need to respect and follow company guidelines and policies. Also to work on communication skills.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 14:51:09', '2023-04-19 16:51:29'),
(595, 16, 5, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '8844', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'FOD', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Dokolo site report', 'Major', '<ul><li>SLM decided not to report to work on Monday(27th Feb 2023) and did not inform anyone including her supervisor. She also left all the company property that had been assigned to her including her staff ID, AAR card, Laptop and Motorbike.</li></ul>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>This shows a lack of respect and accountability. Addressed by DDHR.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 14:52:21', '2023-04-19 16:47:52'),
(596, 8, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '507', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'DDC field visit report of February', 'Major', '<p>Corruption by some of the AAs</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-24', '2023-04-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Agree with the manager\'s response.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 14:52:40', '2023-04-19 16:44:04'),
(597, 32, 35, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '7587', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Operations', '7Forks  office furnitures(chairs, a table and a door)', 'Minor', '<p>One table is broken, 4 chairs have no backrest and the windows panes on the back office door are broken. The window frame is sealed with a manila paper.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 23/03/2023.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-24', '2023-03-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Agree with the manager\'s response</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 15:13:19', '2023-04-19 16:41:20'),
(598, 16, 8, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '1000', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Absence from work on March 10th-Daniel Mukhongi Okumu', 'Major', '<p>SMP Nyongoro send the below communication;</p><p><i>\"Kindly note that Daniel Mukhongi is not at work today. Therefore, update mechanical pruning plan from 6 to 5. The aforementioned staff presented a complaint that he had a minor incidence where a branch fell on his abdomen while pruning. However, no injuries was sustained but I advised him to visit a health facility for a checkup</i>.\"</p><p>I took contact with him on 22nd March and he was doing well. He observed that this incidences happen often, the branch can fall on the hand, feet etc. and they don\'t report since they are minor.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Refresher courses/training should be in the plannings.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 16:22:48', '2023-04-19 15:08:32'),
(599, 16, 5, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '6546', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'FOD', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Dokolo Site Report', 'Major', '<ol><li>Chemical spraying Masks and googles are not labelled for easier issuance and management.&nbsp;</li></ol>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Upon receiving the PPEs and ensuring they conform to the requirements in matters of quality, colour, size etc.&nbsp;<br>Marking if not done by the supplier should be next on the checklist.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 20:57:01', '2023-04-19 15:03:18'),
(600, 16, 5, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-23', '3832', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'FOD', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Dokolo site report', 'Major', '<p>There are two toilets and two bathrooms. On the first day both were clean, and they had tissue paper. But on the second day the men toilet was not cleaned, and they only put tissue paper at the end of the day.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Is there a checklist with the daily activities indicating the time of each activity? Has the housekeeper been trained on the daily activities and the timings?&nbsp;<br>Supervision should also be ensured.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-23 21:00:04', '2023-04-19 14:55:58'),
(601, 32, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-27', '3225', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'WORK INSTRUCTION FOR MARKING OF PITS', 'Minor', '<p>Marking of pits in compartment A016 was done by 3 PMS . The work instruction for marking of pits states that,`` a steel cable has a length of 120 metres and is used by four people who do marking\".</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 27/03/2033.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-29', '2023-03-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Addressed by forestry.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-28 02:25:33', '2023-04-19 14:49:45'),
(602, 28, 28, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-28', '2409', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'Housekeeping activity', 'Minor', '<p>On Wednesday 22/3/2023, a watering can meant for watering seedlings was being used in PPE cleaning. The housekeeper was using the watering can to store water for cleaning PPEs.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-03', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>The housekeeper\'s immediate supervisor is the SLM. Is she aware of that?<br>1. The housekeeper cleaning PPEs should be advised to the cleaning near the water source.&nbsp;<br>2. Site supervisor to clearly communicate to the workers what tools and equipment they need to use for each activity.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-28 19:11:19', '2023-04-19 14:37:27'),
(603, 28, 28, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-28', '9198', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'Housekeeping Checklist', 'Minor', '<p>The area around the sowing beds untidy. Logs were observed in that area on 24/3/2023.&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-03', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Staff should be taught to work in a clean way and leave a place better than they found it.&nbsp;<br>Lack of ownership and responsibility by forestry on the polybags and operations on the construction logs.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-28 19:15:45', '2023-04-19 14:28:33'),
(604, 28, 28, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-28', '799', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'Site Infrastructure-Shed net structure', 'Major', '<p>The nets laid on the shed structure are weak and some areas are torn, which allows direct rain drops onto seedlings.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-03-30', '2023-04-03', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Timely communication and an IPR would have solved the problem.</div>', '', '', '2023-03-28 19:23:45', '2023-04-19 14:21:54'),
(605, 32, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, 2017, '2023-04-03', '5001', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'WORK INSTRUCTION FOR MANUAL CLEANING', 'Minor', '<p>Glyphosate nor a Jembe was not used in manual cleaning that was done in compartment A029 which is contrary to manual cleaning work instruction.</p><p>After the interaction the PMS Musyoka Masuko said, `` There is no glyphosate in the store\".</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 03/04/2023.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-05', '2023-04-06', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Taking responsibility as the site responsible is lacking. How can glyphosate be depleted for activity you knew was going to happen and not have been communicated for the tasks to be adjusted and an IPR raised?</div>', '', '', '2023-04-03 20:26:17', '2023-04-19 14:19:29'),
(606, 19, 11, 9, NULL, NULL, 2176, '2023-04-12', '8333', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree counting prospection report', 'Major', '<p>Tree counting activity was done in a compartment that was not prospected.</p><p>counting on 11th April 2023, was done in B004 which did not have prospection report for week 15.&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-08', '2023-05-09', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Response from the auditee is too slow. This CAR is repeated however is repeated.</div>', '', '', '2023-04-12 13:13:44', '2023-05-09 15:19:50'),
(607, 19, 11, 9, NULL, NULL, 2178, '2023-04-12', '6618', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Manager Plantation Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'week 15 Forestry plan', 'Minor', '<p>Tree counting was done in a compartment that was not planned for in week 15.</p><p>According to week 15 plan. Tree counting was to be done in B005 on 11th April 2023. Counting was done in B004 and it is in this compartment that the pms doing Tree counting was clocked into. There is no explanation for the change.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-08', '2023-05-09', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Vertical communication upwards and downwards and the management in the back office.&nbsp;<br>Lack of responsibility by the site responsible and supervision is also lacking.</div>', '', '', '2023-04-12 13:21:57', '2023-05-09 15:07:41'),
(608, 8, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-13', '6881', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Report DDC Kiambere Visit', 'Major', '<p>Task was not adjusted in the back office on 4th April for PMS that were seen around the seedling distribution truck for GIC that was stuck in the plantation.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-17', '2023-04-18', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Proper attention to the tasks and the timeframe is lacking. This should be addressed by all involved parties.</div>', '', '', '2023-04-13 14:53:17', '2023-04-19 13:58:16'),
(609, 18, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-13', '5349', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Kiambere site visit-site structure', 'Major', '<p>Site structures are not maintained.</p><p>The wooden gate at compartment A016, the structure holding the logs from the plantation and the nursery fence along the lakeside are not maintained.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-14', '2023-04-18', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Timely communication and taking responsibility by the site responsible is lacking. You are the person on the ground and you should have identified such issues a long time ago and had them addressed.</div>', '', '', '2023-04-13 15:06:18', '2023-04-19 13:54:44'),
(610, 18, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2023-04-13', '4717', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Kiambere site visit.', 'Minor', '<p>No mobile latrine in compartment A016.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-04-14', '2023-04-18', '2023-05-15', '2023-05-31', '2023-05-11', 'A temporary toilet has been built near compt 016', '<div>A temporary toilet was done and in Use</div>', '<div>Operations are addressing it.</div>', '<div>This is health and safety concern and should be addressed as soon as possible by operations department.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-04-13 15:10:43', '2023-08-02 16:28:51'),
(611, 18, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-13', '9055', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Kiambere site visit.', 'Major', '<p>No security lights in the nursery</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-14', '2023-04-18', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>Make a temporary pit Latrin with Mabati at the nursery.<br>When we resume activities, we will make metallic pit latrines from Nairobi properly welded and take to the site.</div>', '<div>Timely communication. Staff on site should not wait for HODs to visit the site to raise the points they want to be addressed or improved. The company has provided several channels of communication to ensure its timely. Let\'s put them to good use.&nbsp;<br>In this case, an IPR should also have been raised.</div>', '<div>To be addressed by FOD.</div>', '', '2023-04-13 15:12:10', '2023-04-27 16:54:32'),
(612, 8, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-13', '4180', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Seedling stock report during distribution of GIC seedlings (KIA & GIC)', 'Major', '<p>232 recorded rejects on the last day of distribution for GIC. This was in spite of there being no report of rejects during purchase and during the period in which the seedlings were in the nursery.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-14', '2023-04-18', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>There was no follow up by the head office manager to ensure that the FT is doing proper seedling management practices.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>Communication goes in two ways. The condition of the seedlings should have been on the daily phone call conversation with the HO manager. Do these conversations happen every day, including the feedback on ongoing tasks and activities?</div>', '<div>Proper planning and supervision was lacking both by the FT and the HO manager.</div>', '', '2023-04-13 20:57:24', '2023-04-27 16:48:20'),
(613, 8, 35, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-13', '3204', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Site Manager Farmers Programme 7Forks', '7 Forks', 'Forestry', 'Seedling stock report during distribution of GIC seedlings (KIA & GIC)', 'Major', '<p>232 recorded rejects on the last day of distribution for GIC. This was in spite of there being no report of rejects during purchase and during the period in which the seedlings were in the nursery.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-17', '2023-04-27', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>At the point of offloading seedlings from the supplier, the seedlings need to be sorted. The Bad from the good and records were taken as per the work instruction. There was also no followup from the HO manager to ensure proper managemnt of the seedlings in the nursery.</div>', '<div>Communication goes in two ways. As far as I know, there are daily phone conversations between the HO manager and the site responsible. The condition of the seedlings should have been on the checklist of the daily conversation. The daily conversation checklist should include feedback on ongoing activities and tasks. The daily interactions are important and should not only be done because staff are instructed to do so.</div>', '<div>Agree with DDC comment</div>', '', '2023-04-13 20:57:25', '2023-04-27 16:46:57'),
(614, 18, 29, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2023-04-14', '7294', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Finance Manual-Invoices.', 'Major', '<p>Late submission of an invoice.</p><p>The invoice for Rentokil Initial Kenya Limited came in February 2023 and the Procurement officer handed over it &nbsp;to accounts on 13th April 2023 which is against the policy that says “when Invoices come to the company, they are handed over to AM who records them in a book, puts a date stamp and gives to the account to post and file”</p><p>See the attached.</p>', 'closed', '2023-04-17', '2023-04-18', '2023-07-19', '2023-07-31', '2023-07-19', 'Ok, for implementation', '<div>This is bad. People do not do what they are supposed to do. Documents received by operations should be taken to AM same day, whether electronically or physical.<br>Suppliers are also advised to send invoices to accounts.<br>Documents taken to accounts to be kept in the in-tray.</div>', '<div>I suggest a meeting shared by FOD with all involved, latest Friday afternoon this week. DDC will be present for this meeting.</div>', '<div>To be addressed by the HOD.</div>', '<div>Ok</div>', '2023-04-14 12:22:44', '2023-08-02 16:26:38'),
(615, 19, 14, 29, NULL, NULL, 1845, '2023-04-18', '5660', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Backend clocking report ', 'Minor', '<p>Security Guard Hussein Kani was clocked in mechanical pruning on 17th April 2023. Instead of being clocked in Security.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-20', '2023-04-21', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>What probably happened the device was lying on the desk and the security did not check before clocking in. The device was not supervised.<br>The Manager responsible for the site should supervise the device handlers.</div>', '', '<div>This shows lack of supervision by the site responsible.Its the responsibility of the site responsibles to supervise and ensure their team members are clocked in the right activities and have all the right tools for the job.</div>', '', '2023-04-18 18:04:06', '2023-04-27 16:24:54'),
(616, 19, 9, 9, NULL, NULL, 2246, '2023-04-18', '3329', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Plantation Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Time and attendance; Forestry week 16 plan', 'Minor', '<p>According to Forestry week 16 plan, mechanical pruning was to be done in F098 on 17th April 2023.</p><p>Pms were clocked in F029. Work was however done in the planned compartment.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-19', '2023-04-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>This is not a communication issue. The plantations manager input the wrong compartment in the back office. The tasks should be input according to the approved plan.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>Need to pay better attention. This is not a communication breakdown.</div>', '', '', '2023-04-18 18:16:21', '2023-04-27 16:11:08'),
(617, 19, 14, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-04-19', '4378', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Plantation protection', 'Minor', '<p>There were cows observed in B006 on 17th April 2023 and at G036 on 18th April 2021.</p><p>The castle exposed soil hence increasing the chances of soil erosion which might lead to trees falling during rains or wind. From the slight interactions with one of the herds men, they revealed that these cows are from the neighbouring MOA and might be the reason why it has been difficult for the security guards to bar them from entering the plantation. The main entrances are from the south of the plantation.</p><p>These herdsmen are armed with knifes and dogs hence making them sometimes unapproachable.</p>', 'closed', '2023-04-20', '2023-04-21', '2023-05-13', '2023-06-30', '2023-05-11', 'To be addressed by Management during a ranch meeting on 13th May 23', '<div>To be addressed by management</div>', '<div>Senior Management will address it on 13th May during the meeting with the ranch committee. However, this should not stop the security from protecting the trees.</div>', '<div>To be addressed by senior management</div>', '<div>Addressed and process ongoing</div>', '2023-04-19 12:59:00', '2023-08-02 16:31:19'),
(618, 38, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-19', '2176', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Site hygiene', 'Major', '<p>The site is busy with tall growing grasses around the reserve tank and in the wood lot. Weeds were also observed in the nursery area.</p><p>This was observed on 19/4/2023</p><p>See the attached evidence.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-22', '2023-04-27', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>This should be taken care of by the weekly planning of tasks plus the Meeting on every tuesday for the managers.<br>The SMD should take charge of the site and highlight areas that need to be addressed.<br>Operations is also sleeping. Cleaning can also be done manually where Glyphosate is late in procuring.<br>We also need proper planning to spray weeds immediately it rains to suppress them.</div>', '<div>Timely communication and taking ownership is lacking. The site responsible should have noticed it and brought it up to have it addressed.</div>', '<div>This shows lack of planning by the site responsible.</div>', '', '2023-04-19 18:01:59', '2023-04-27 15:56:45'),
(619, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, 2314, '2023-04-20', '2440', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Tools and Equipments', 'Minor', '<p>On wednesday 19/4/2023, &nbsp;watering cans meant for &nbsp;watering the seedlings was being used in PPE cleaning. The housekeeper was using the watering cans to fetch and store water for cleaning PPEs.</p>', 'closed', '2023-04-22', '2023-04-25', '2023-05-15', '2023-06-16', '2023-05-11', NULL, '<div>Plan to have a good area for PPE cleaning.<br>We have Jerricans that are used when fetching water. Therefore no shortage of jerricans.</div>', '<div>There\'s a lack of supervision.&nbsp;<br>Staff should also be taught the right tools, materials and PPEs to use for the different activities.</div>', '<div>Agree with DDC comment. In addition ,we have to ensure there is a good working environment for the housekeeper when doing the cleaning.</div>', '<div>ok.&nbsp;</div>', '2023-04-20 15:14:10', '2023-08-02 16:33:15'),
(620, 38, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-04-22', '5513', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Corroded seeding by rain water', 'Major', '<p>The old net that the rain water can perculate through&nbsp;</p><p>Stich net areas and holes&nbsp;</p><p>Difficulty in stretching the old net since it just get torn&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-04-22', '2023-04-27', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>The site manager needs to take responsibility and point out all the issues that are not ok regardless of the department because ultimately it shall affect the objectives of forestry.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>This communication is not timely. This should have been communicated the moment it was realized the net was faulty. The focus should not have been on which department was supposed to address the issue. When mortality occurs the whole company is affected.</div>', '', '', '2023-04-22 14:12:33', '2023-04-27 15:58:38'),
(621, 28, 28, 29, 5, 38, NULL, '2023-05-02', '7042', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'Weekly task management', 'Major', '<p>On Sunday 30/4/2023, the SLM went for lake sand collection, and the changed plan was not updated in the weekly task management folder.&nbsp;</p><p>On the same day, during the same activity of sand collection, the truck got stuck upon return before reaching the site, and had to stay out of the site for the night.</p>', 'closed', '2023-05-04', '2023-05-08', '2023-05-15', '2023-06-12', '2023-05-11', NULL, '<div>This is a wrong planning and should never have been done on a Sunday. With complete communication with Forestry responsible and this should have made it clear if the sand was really needed then this would have been done the right way.</div>', '<div>Lack of proper planning and poor communication.</div>', '<div>Agree with DDC comment. In addition, there must be authorization to work during non working days.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-05-02 13:36:01', '2023-08-02 16:56:31'),
(622, 32, 15, 9, 8, 32, 2570, '2023-05-03', '4050', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Work instruction for manual chemical weeding', 'Minor', '<p>On 3/5/2023,a target of 3.84ha for chemical weeding was not achieved. The activity was done in compartment A016 by 6 PMS and they achieved 2.83ha.&nbsp;</p><p>The target is 0.64ha per manday.</p><p>1.Kyalo Muneeni</p><p>2.Shadrack Munyoki.</p><p>3.Masyuko Musyoka</p><p>4.Musyoka Kithome</p><p>5. Joseph Mwendwa</p><p>6. Josphate Musyimi.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-05-04', '2023-05-09', '2023-07-03', '2023-07-31', '2023-06-29', NULL, '', '<div>When there are challenges or changes they should be communicated immediately so that the tasks are adjusted or appropriate action to be taken is given.</div>', '<div>Planning and communication is critical for every activity. FT is simply not doing his job right and dwells on excuses.</div>', '', '2023-05-03 22:47:32', '2023-08-24 18:06:50'),
(623, 23, 5, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-06', '8998', 'Managing Director', 'FOD', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Site visit to Dokolo on 3/5/2023', 'Major', '<p>The truck in Dokolo got into an accident with damages and nobody communicated to head office</p>', 'closed', '2023-05-09', '2023-05-09', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>I am not satisfied with that answer. There is no way this is from 2021 or somebody (SLM) really doesn\'t do its job as nobody knows. What about the broken exhaust. This truck is critical for our distribution.<br>Will a warning help. What would help is deducting all the costs related to the sunday incident and the repairs.</div>', '', '', '2023-05-07 00:42:12', '2023-05-11 16:16:51'),
(624, 23, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-06', '1768', 'Managing Director', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Site visit to Dokolo on 3/5/2023', 'Major', '<p>The truck in Dokolo got into an accident with damages and nobody communicated to head office</p>', 'Auditee responded', '2023-05-16', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-07 00:42:13', '2023-05-16 17:41:54'),
(625, 8, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-07', '5574', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Weekly planning records and the back office tasks list', 'Minor', '<p>The codes for the daily nursery activities for Dokolo site have not been updated to match the approved chart of accounts.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-23', '2023-05-25', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-08 00:38:12', '2023-05-25 13:33:46'),
(626, 8, 29, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2023-05-07', '5411', 'Executive Director Forestry', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Weekly planning records and the back office tasks list', 'Minor', '<p>The codes for the daily nursery activities for Dokolo site have not been updated to match the approved chart of accounts.</p>', 'closed', '2023-05-09', '2023-05-09', '2023-05-21', '2023-05-31', '2023-05-11', 'URGENT', '<div>This is urgent as it affects accounts and budgets.</div>', '<div>This should be addressed immediately as it\'s creating a mess in the whole system.</div>', '<div>EDF/FOD to plan and have a meeting immediately and explain.</div>', '<div>This is an implementation problem. Only comment is that it needs to be addressed immediately.</div>', '2023-05-08 00:38:13', '2023-08-02 16:56:49'),
(627, 18, 28, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-08', '7915', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'Truck Maintenance', 'Major', '<p>Failure to maintain the Truck leading to breakdown and damage.</p><p>See the attached.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-05-09', '2023-05-11', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>The SLM know what is expected of her when it comes to maintenance of company property. all the toold for communication have been provided. The preventive Maintenance app, the IPR system, the communication app and still she does not use them.<br>SLM should get a warning with costs incurred due to the CAR</div>', '<div>Issues like this should not wait for a CAR to be addressed. The management has provided several platforms for communication and the maintenance app which are not efficiently utilized.<br>HR and Operations will address the issue</div>', '<div>Its the responsibility of the SLM to ensure that all the company property is well maintained and in good condition. This is unacceptable.</div>', '', '2023-05-08 13:20:58', '2023-05-11 16:01:08'),
(628, 38, 28, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-09', '6722', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'PPE Management Policy, Revision 003.', 'Major', '<p>On 9/5/2023, a temporary worker removed his gumboots while harvesting fruits in the nursery. This is contrary to the PPE management policy that says \" temporary worker shall sign for and wear the respective PPE before clocking in and be dressed in the PPE all day during work\"&nbsp;</p><p>See the attached.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-12', '2023-05-16', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-09 16:03:59', '2023-05-17 02:13:36'),
(629, 38, 28, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-09', '7625', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'PPE management policy Revision 003', 'Major', '<p>On 9/5/2023, a temporary worker removed his gumboots while harvesting fruits in the nursery. This is contrary to the PPE management policy that says \" temporary worker shall sign for and wear the respective PPE before clocking in and be dressed in the PPE all day during work\"&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-12', '2023-05-16', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-09 16:04:00', '2023-05-17 02:14:23'),
(631, 32, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, 2921, '2023-05-17', '5482', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'TREE COUNTING(COMPARTMENT STOCK ASSESSMENT) WORK INSTRUCTION', 'Major', '<p>On wednesday 17/05/2023, tree counting which was done in compartment A039&amp;A040 with 3 PMS and 2400 trees task rate was not achieved. The team achieved 1571 trees. This is contrary to work instruction which states that the task rate is 800 trees per man-day.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-19', '2023-05-22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-17 23:08:00', '2023-05-22 20:30:31'),
(632, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-17', '7214', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'SITE STRUCTURES', 'Major', '<p>On wednesday 17/05/2023, it was observed that two crocodile cages in the nursery are broken.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-19', '2023-05-25', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-17 23:32:53', '2023-05-25 12:51:30'),
(633, 38, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, 2946, '2023-05-22', '1998', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Task rates, 30180 DKL Temp Nsy potting', 'Major', '<p>On the 19th/5/2023</p><p>The task rates for potting was not achieved at the nursery by the workers during potting, the target was 15000 and the worker achieved 9696 pot potted&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-23', '2023-05-25', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-22 14:00:30', '2023-05-25 13:15:22'),
(634, 19, 22, 29, NULL, NULL, 3013, '2023-05-23', '2076', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site logistics Manager Nyongoro', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Maintenance of brush cutters', 'Major', '<p>There have been frequent brush cutters breakdown which have resulted to change of plans during the day.</p><p>Site handyman has always been informed about breakdowns from the time the mechanic became absent. However, the Site handyman don\'t critically diagnose the machines to find the problem or the root cause to the problem but instead unbolts and unscrew parts of the machine and try and repair what he thinks is the problem only to realize that there is another problem that is leading to the machine not working after struggle.</p><p>The handyman is not open to opinions, observations, and or questions from the team and always dismisses ideas, opinions, and question from other team members.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>e.g., on 22nd May 2023, Machine used by Sulubu and Walter was reported to have developed mechanical problem. Handyman opened the carburetor and air cleaner and cleaned it up and screwed it back, reassembled the manual starter, pulled spark plug and cleaned it. These attempts did not make the machine function.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Breakdowns affected activities on 15th May and 22nd May 2023 where workers had to be assigned another task.</p><p>He then observed the machine and identified problem with the fuel pump. The pump was punctured making the machine to suck in air. He concluded this needed another pump hence the machine could not be repaired, and the team was reassigned another task. NB: the material of the fuel pump in question is silicon like.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-26', '2023-05-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-23 12:55:25', '2023-05-29 16:11:33'),
(635, 38, 26, 10, NULL, NULL, 3092, '2023-05-26', '3722', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Nursery Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Task achievements  30180 Dkl Temp Nsy Potting', 'Major', '<p>0n 25/5/2023</p><p>The task rates for potting was not achieved by the workers at the nursery. Achieved 11016 by 8 workers over 12000 pots&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-05-27', '2023-05-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-26 12:03:46', '2023-05-29 12:29:09'),
(636, 19, 14, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-26', '6661', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'CAR work instruction', 'Minor', '<p>Late responding to CAR&nbsp;</p><p>CAR work instruction requires that new CARs are responded to within 48hrs from the time they are opened.</p><p>CAR 2076 opened on 23/05/2023 was responded to on 26/05/2023 which was beyond 48 hours as per the Monitoring and Evaluation requirement.</p>', 'closed', '2023-05-27', '2023-05-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>OK.</div>', '', '', '<div>ok</div>', '2023-05-26 15:28:12', '2023-06-22 16:04:17'),
(637, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, 3239, '2023-05-30', '9099', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'TREE COUNTING WORK INSTRUCTION-Compartment demarcation.', 'Minor', '<p>Broken pointers for the beacon in compartment A030. Further assessment of the pointers suggests they were cut.&nbsp;</p><p>This was observed on Tuesday 30/05/2023.</p><p>See the attached evidence.</p>', 'closed', '2023-06-02', '2023-06-06', '2023-06-28', '2023-07-14', '2023-06-22', NULL, '<div>Improve on security patrols<br>Repair the beacons</div>', '<div>The repair was done. Collective measures to be put in place.</div>', '<div>Company property is important to all of us and its the responsibility of every employee to ensure that they communicate any malicious activity by their team members. Also, security team should be vigilant when doing patrols.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-05-30 22:33:57', '2023-08-02 16:57:07'),
(638, 32, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-06', '9768', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'HEALTH AND SAFETY-COMPARTMENT HYGIENE', 'Major', '<p>Compartments A030,A039 and A040 have tall grasses which needs to be weeded. This has affected task rate achievement for maintenance activities such as tree counting.</p><p>Date &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Activity &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Target &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Achievement &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Variance</p><p>17/5/23 &nbsp; &nbsp; tree counting &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2400 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1571 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;829</p><p>30/5/23 &nbsp; &nbsp; tree counting &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2400 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2357 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;43</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-06-12', '2023-06-13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-06 10:08:32', '2023-06-13 14:43:51'),
(639, 38, 28, 29, 5, 38, NULL, '2023-06-06', '2223', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'House keeping', 'Minor', '<p>Lack of drying lines for hanging washed PPEs ( overall). In regards to this, the house keeper has been hanging the overall on top of shrubs (duranta species) within the nursery site compound towards the site gate. This was observed on 31/5/2023&nbsp;</p>', 'follow up', '2023-06-08', '2023-06-09', '2023-06-22', '2023-07-31', '2023-06-22', NULL, '<div>Hanging Wires to be installed ASAP.</div>', '<div>This is long overdue and the issue should have been identified and addressed the first time the laundry duties were allocated to the housekeeper. Leadership is lacking.</div>', '<div>The housekeeper should be supervised and guided on what to do by the SLM which is not the case here.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-06-06 11:56:12', '2023-06-23 00:25:38'),
(640, 38, 28, 29, 5, 38, NULL, '2023-06-06', '1149', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Logistic Manager Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Operations', 'Sand collection', 'Major', '<p>Poor planning for sand collection on 31/5/2023</p><p>It had rained the previous night and forestry had a sand to use hence the SLM DKL ought to have postponed the activity.&nbsp;</p><p>The SLM went for sand and the truck developed a mechanical breakdown on the way, the truck driver, SLM and casual spent the night in the field.</p>', 'closed', '2023-06-08', '2023-06-09', '2023-06-22', '2023-07-31', '2023-06-22', NULL, '<div>This has been addressed through proper planning and communication with the site manager and forestry department.<br>We shall weigh the sand to ascertain the exact level when the truck has right load.<br>We shall have a person&nbsp; on the truck during sand collection to ensure the instructions are followed.&nbsp;<br>Proper maintenance of the truck all the time even when it is not working.</div>', '<div>Lack of communication between operations and forestry on site and to the HO to&nbsp;</div>', '<div>This is unacceptable as it shows that staff are not taking responsibility of their work. To be effectively addressed by Operations and Forestry department.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-06-06 12:05:24', '2023-08-02 16:57:47'),
(641, 38, 13, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-06', '3168', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Pricking Task rates achievement', 'Minor', '<p>The task rates for Pricking out is not realistic, from the hourly measurement and analysis done for week 21, date 26/5/2023 there was an over achievement of 13632 seedlings pricked by 4 temporally staff over 12000 seedlings Variation of 1632.&nbsp;</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-06-08', '2023-06-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-06 12:50:32', '2023-06-29 14:10:44'),
(642, 5, 29, 5, 5, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-06', '3986', 'Director of Finance & Operations', 'Operations Manager', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Purchase Manual', 'Major', '<p>Buying wrong Specs of Laptop which overpriced. ( TEST)</p>', 'closed', '2023-06-06', '2023-06-06', NULL, NULL, '2023-06-06', 'OK, with the Correction action taken', '<div>Ok</div>', '', '<div>Ok</div>', '<div>Ok</div>', '2023-06-06 14:36:01', '2023-06-06 14:46:55'),
(643, 32, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, 3487, '2023-06-14', '4722', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'WORK INSTRUCTION FOR MANUAL CLEANING', 'Major', '<p>On 14/06/2023, Glyphosate &nbsp;nor a Jembe was not used in manual cleaning that was done in compartment A039 which is contrary to manual cleaning work instruction.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-06-16', '2023-06-19', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-14 22:29:05', '2023-06-19 13:24:08'),
(644, 19, 14, 9, NULL, NULL, 3417, '2023-06-16', '4448', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Week 24 forestry plan', 'Minor', '<p>Employees were clocked into compartment they didn\'t work in on 13th June 2023.&nbsp;</p><p>Plan indicated mechanical pruning in E094 where the team was clocked in but work was done in compartment E091 and results uploaded for compartment E094.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-06-16', '2023-06-19', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-16 14:42:21', '2023-06-19 13:39:32'),
(645, 19, 14, 9, 8, 19, 3433, '2023-06-16', '2006', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Records- tree counting forms', 'Major', '<p>Tree counting forms for C010 have sheets bearing same row numbers in different sheets with different tree stock values.</p><p>This compartment was counted in week 22. &nbsp;An instance in the sheets is stock for row one which has 4 trees in one form and 34trees in the other form. Forms belonging to diffent compartments have been steppled together.</p>', 'closed', '2023-06-23', '2023-06-26', '2023-07-01', '2023-07-31', '2023-06-29', 'for follow up', '<div>1. Pre-assessment must be done to help devise a proper execution plan.&nbsp;<br>2. The HO manager must follow up on a daily basis to ensure that tree counting is being executed correctly.<br>3. The tree counting should follow the cleaning.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>I agree with the manager\'s response.</div>', '<div>This shows lack of prospection and supervision by the site responsible. Also, HO manager should constantly take contact with SLR and guide him.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-06-16 14:52:00', '2023-08-24 18:06:14'),
(646, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-21', '5655', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'KIAMBERE SITE FURNITURE- CHAIRS', 'Minor', '<p>On 21/6/2023, it was observed that 14 chairs in kiambere nursery office have torn chair covers.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-06-23', '2023-06-24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-21 23:59:46', '2023-06-25 02:39:33'),
(647, 32, 15, 9, 8, 32, 3627, '2023-06-21', '7938', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'WORK INSTRUCTION FOR PRUNING MUKAU- Health and safety', 'Major', '<p>Two PMS Kyalo Muneni and Shadrack Munyoki did not wear gloves and helmets while they were doing pruning in compartment A043.</p><p>&nbsp;This is contrary to work instruction which states that other PPEs to be worn during pruning are gloves and a helmet.</p>', 'closed', '2023-06-23', '2023-06-26', '2023-07-03', '2023-07-14', '2023-06-29', 'For followup', '<div>1. The permanent maintenance staff to get a warning if they were issued with PPE but refused to wear.<br>2. The FT to get a warning if he did not issue PPE to the staff that were doing pruning.</div>', '<div>HR will address the issue as it keeps recurring.</div>', '<div>Wearing of PPEs by staff is mandatory for their own safety and also its a requirement by law, the two staff to be given a warning. Also, the supervisor should ensure everybody is on the right PPEs at all times.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-06-22 01:09:39', '2023-08-24 18:05:37'),
(648, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2023-06-22', '6983', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'PREVENTIVE MAINTENANCE OF TOOLS  AND EQUIPMENTS', 'Minor', '<p>Lack of maintenance of tools and ewuipments.</p><p>The 8 knapsack sprayers do not have springs and nozzles,9 pangas do not have handles,an axe is broken on the butt,4 long pruning have broken blades and 14 have worn out blades,4 mattocks have no handles,a spade has a broken socket and10 slashers do not have handles. This was observed on 21/06/2023 after assessment of tools and equipments in the store.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-06-23', '2023-06-24', '2023-07-19', '2023-07-31', '2023-07-19', 'Ok, for implementation', '<div>The site responsible is aware of what to do, not to just maintain the tools that are in use but also the tools in the store. He however did not do it despite reminders in meetings.<br>OM to address the repairs with FT<br>The FT gets a warning.</div>', '<div>Poor leadership and communication skills. The maintenance schedule is also clearly not respected&nbsp;</div>', '<div>This shows lack of taking responsibility by the FT. FT is in charge of all the company property and this is unacceptable as it affects the task rates and its a health hazard to the staff. FT to get a warning.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-06-22 23:31:08', '2023-07-19 18:03:29');
