(665, 19, 14, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-06-30', '1829', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Health and Safety; Drinking water', 'Major', '<p>Drinking water run out of stock on 26th June 2023. Restocking has not been done.</p>', 'closed', '2023-07-04', '2023-07-04', '2023-07-19', '2023-08-31', '2023-07-19', 'Ok, for implementation', '<div>1. Plan to have an extra 3rd tank to act as buffer as the other 10,000ltrs is being refilled.<br>2. There is lack of or untimely communication of LPO to the supplier and the reason for bowser breakdown is an excuse.<br>Same to be done to the other sites to ensure all time access to drinking water.</div>', '<div>Lack of follow-up and poor communication skills. SLR should have followed up with the supplier to ensure they deliver the water on time and if the supplier was not complying it should have been communicated in time for advice on the way forward.</div>', '<div>Drinking water is essential to staff. SLR to ensure there is proper planning to ensure timely delivery of the water. Breakdown of the bowser is just an excuse.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-07-01 02:44:18', '2023-08-02 16:58:39'),
(666, 19, 14, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-07-10', '2831', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Handling or Radio call devices', 'Major', '<p>Blocked walkie talkies</p><p>6 walkie talkies have been blocked &nbsp;as a resulted of incorrect attempts to tune to the agreed channel</p>', 'closed', '2023-07-12', '2023-07-14', '2023-07-24', '2023-09-01', '2023-07-19', 'Ok, for implementation', '<div>Refresher Training is necessary and continuous monitoring on usage of the walkie talkies.<br>SLR to be firm on the instructions on use of walkie talkies.</div>', '<div>I agree with the managers response</div>', '<div>The site logistics responsible should make all the guards aware of the consequences of switching to other channels. Also, everybody has to be well trained on how to use them and sign that they understood and records shared.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-07-10 12:15:44', '2023-08-23 22:08:29'),
(667, 38, 13, 8, 8, 34, NULL, '2023-07-10', '620', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Farmers registration report 30/06 2023', 'Major', '<p>&nbsp;Incorrect partner farmers information, from 9 farmers in Okwalongwen Sub County, three names incorrect, 5 phone numbers repeated and 1 NIN number incorrect</p>', 'follow up', '2023-07-17', '2023-07-18', '2023-08-31', '2023-09-30', '2023-08-31', 'This issue had been first addressed in a meeting with all the AAs. Afterwhich if instructions are not followed the AAs are issued with warnings.', '<div>1. The AA will get a warning for failing to follow instructions knowingly.</div>', '<div>Poor communication skills.&nbsp;<br>Such occurrences should be communicated immediately and the correct action would be advised.&nbsp;<br>The system however will not allow such occurrences.</div>', '<div>All the staff were well trained and should ensure that correct information is shared at all times. Sharing wrong info is unacceptable and the staff responsible should get a warning.</div>', '<div>This is unacceptable. It jeopardizes the whole team\'s work and brings us back to where we come from.<br><br></div>', '2023-07-10 22:12:59', '2023-08-31 17:44:10'),
(668, 19, 14, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-07-11', '7817', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Storage of walkie talkies', 'Major', '<p>Lockers without padlocks. There are 36 lockers in the security office designed for walkie talkie storage. There are 14 padlocks on the locks among which 4 have been left with keys attached and 6 padlocks not locked. Two lockers are locked temporarily with nails. This raised concern on the possibility of other or some security guards intruding into others boxes and messing their colleagues radios.</p>', 'closed', '2023-07-14', '2023-07-17', '2023-07-24', '2023-07-31', '2023-07-19', 'Ok, for implementation', '<div>Mishandling of Company property (locks).<br>Poor Planning. Structures plan shall be complete with everything thought through and included..<br>We shall put a system to manage the lockers and the security office. By 21/07/2023</div>', '<div>Poor leadership skills/Mismanagement. Items procured should be used for the intended purpose and the need for extra items should be communicated immediately and an IPR initiated.</div>', '<div>Site logistics responsible should strive to do things right first time at all times. The locks should be well locked and keys put in secure places. This is a door open for friction and theft cases.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-07-11 12:35:06', '2023-08-23 22:08:08'),
(669, 19, 14, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2023-07-12', '2067', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Tree counting: Row number marking', 'Minor', '<p><strong>imperceptible row numbers on trees.</strong></p><p><strong>Compartments in the Ds moving north have some trees with barely visible row numbers. This has been as a result of the tree growth leading to increased girths that split the markings apart. Counting in trees in these Compartments might be challenging especially when several rows have the imperceptible row numbers.&nbsp;</strong></p>', 'closed', '2023-07-14', '2023-07-17', '2023-07-19', '2023-07-21', '2023-07-19', NULL, '<div>see former CAR</div>', '', '<div>See former CAR</div>', '<div>ok</div>', '2023-07-12 16:42:20', '2023-08-02 18:18:58'),
(670, 19, 14, 29, 5, 18, NULL, '2023-07-12', '8473', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Tree counting: Row number marking', 'Minor', '<p><strong>imperceptible row numbers on trees.</strong></p><p><strong>Compartments in the Ds moving north have some trees with barely visible row numbers. This has been as a result of the tree growth leading to increased girths thay split the markings apart. Counting in trees in these Compartments might be challenging especially when several rows have the imperceptible row numbers.&nbsp;</strong></p>', 'closed', '2023-07-14', '2023-07-17', '2023-07-19', '2023-07-21', '2023-07-19', NULL, '<div>See former CAR</div>', '<div>There should be a plan to remark the trees after an agreed-upon period. Communication on the provision of paint and the remarking of trees on the tasks should be planned.</div>', '<div>See former CAR</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-07-12 16:42:21', '2023-08-02 18:18:22'),
(671, 32, 15, 29, 5, 32, NULL, '2023-07-12', '3184', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'Site structures-office window', 'Minor', '<p>3 window glasses in the office are missing. This was observed on 12/7/2023.</p><p>Attached is the evidence.</p>', 'closed', '2023-07-14', '2023-07-14', '2023-07-24', '2023-08-15', '2023-07-19', 'Ok for implementation', '<div>I agree with the Manager. The checks should be done well and correct feedback given.&nbsp;<br>Measures to be taken immediately to maintain the company property:&nbsp; the office buildings and structures to prevent them from being damaged.&nbsp;<br>FT is incharge of the company property and its maintenance.<br>OM to review the checklist for office maintenance by 21/07/2023</div>', '<div>Lack of taking responsibility and pride where one works. This should be on the daily maintenance checklist.</div>', '<div>FT is responsible for the company property and must ensure everything is well maintained. This shows don\'t care attitude and its unacceptable.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-07-12 20:24:04', '2023-08-23 22:07:06'),
(672, 19, 14, 9, 8, 19, NULL, '2023-07-18', '1124', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Tree counting: row number marking', 'Minor', '<p>Imperceptible row numbers on trees&nbsp;</p><p>Compartments in the Ds moving north have some trees with barely visible row numbers. This has been as a result of tree growth leading to increased girths that split the markings apart. Counting trees in these Compartments might be challenging especially when several rows have the imperceptible row numbers.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-07-18', '2023-07-18', '2023-08-02', '2023-08-09', '2023-07-27', 'ok', '<div>1. Lack of having and following a maintenance schedule for repainting the marks on the trees. It is common knowledge that trees must be repainted after a period of time because of growth.&nbsp;<br>2. The marking of the trees shall be added in the maintenance app. by 21/07/2023. The schedule toshall be introduced in the app by the Plantations manager by friday 21st July 2023.</div>', '<div>There should be a plan to remark the trees after an agreed-upon period. Communication for the provision of paint and the remarking of trees on the tasks should be planned.</div>', '<div>Agree with DDC comment.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-07-18 10:27:03', '2023-08-24 18:04:09'),
(673, 19, 14, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-07-19', '6763', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Communication: Communication on the status of machine after work by PMS', 'Major', '<p>PMS dont promptly report issues with the machine as soon as they occur or they are realised.</p><p>On 18/07/2023 mechanical pruning saw used by Barisa and Ali had mechanical issues in the morning. This meant that the issues were from previous day that is 17/07/2023. The machine had to be repaired because it needed a major repair which consumed alot of time for both Barisa, Ali, Wachira and Rashid.</p><p>Impact</p><p>Team was not able to start work early and this mean that for task rate to be achieved the machine will have to be subjected to too much work that in the long run may lead to other mechanical issues.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-07-22', '2023-07-23', '2023-08-03', '2023-08-31', '2023-08-02', NULL, '<div>This is a leadership and supervision problem of the PMS by SLR.<br>Failure of the PMS to report is also a problem.</div>', '<div>Breakdowns of tools should be reported immediately. There should be a procedure in place to record the state of tools and machinery after use.</div>', '<div>There is a problem with leadership and taking of responsibility by the SLR.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-07-19 11:59:10', '2023-08-23 22:06:37'),
(674, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-07-21', '5953', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', '2023 GIC Budget 230630 - Nursery shade', 'Minor', '<p>The constructed tunnels shade is against the plan. The measurements of the actual constructed tunnels shade in the nursery is 20×8 meter square and in the plan &nbsp;the area for tunnels shade is 43×17 meter square. This was observed on 19/07/2023.</p>', 'closed', '2023-07-22', '2023-07-25', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>There was no plan<br>There was no communication of the plan.&nbsp;<br>Infuture, an approved plan should be communicated in time.</div>', '<div>There was no communication between forestry and operations on the adaptation of the plans</div>', '<div>The tasks rate have not been adopted according to reality meaning there was no coordination and supervision and its unacceptable.</div>', '<div>Communication between departments and verticals is still lacking.<br>No use of Microsoft Project.<br>Lousy job on the construction itself.<br>Job to be redone properly with plan and drawings.<br>ALL PROJECTS SHALL START WITH AN APPROVED DRAWING AND AS A PROJECT!</div>', '2023-07-21 20:31:11', '2023-07-27 18:07:14'),
(675, 32, 15, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-08', '6335', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Operations', 'HEALTH AND SAFETY/ DRINKING WATER', 'Major', '<p>There was no drinking water in kiambere site.</p><p>This was observed on 08/08/2023</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-09', '2023-08-15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-08 22:07:44', '2023-08-16 00:21:23'),
(676, 19, 14, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24', '3853', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Preventive maintenance of brush cutters', 'Major', '<p>Frequent breakdown of brush cutters&nbsp;</p><p>There has been frequent breakdown of brush cutters which led to four out of the 6 brush cutters not functioning from the start of week 34. This affected the plan.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-26', '2023-08-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24 16:39:31', '2023-08-29 19:07:35'),
(677, 32, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24', '7109', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'GIC SEEDLING PRODUCTION 2023', 'Major', '<p>There was low seedling germination of 54% in GIC seedling production. 11500 seeds were sown and 6210 seedlings pricked out. This overall percentage of seedlings was pricked out from 07/08/23 to 16/08/23.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-28', '2023-08-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24 18:00:20', '2023-08-30 17:27:16'),
(678, 32, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24', '3080', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'GIC SEEDLING PRODUCTION 2023', 'Major', '<p>Seedling mortality. There was mortality of 4% of seedling pricked out as from 16th August 2023 to 23rd August 2023. 6210 seedlings was pricked out and 262 seedlings have died.</p><p>This was observed by M&amp;E on 23/08/23 in the nursery kiambere.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-28', '2023-08-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24 18:37:12', '2023-08-30 18:05:39'),
(679, 32, 15, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24', '8861', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer 7Forks 2', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'GIC SEEDLING PRODUCTION WORK PLAN,BACK-END REPORT 170723-180823', 'Minor', '<p>More manday was used in depulping,cracking,sowing,pricking out and potting than what was planned in the GIC seedling production plan.</p><p>See the attached.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-28', '2023-08-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24 20:05:45', '2023-08-30 18:13:10'),
(680, 38, 26, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24', '8255', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Nursery Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Task rate achievement', 'Major', '<p>The task rates for Pricking out was &nbsp;not achieved &nbsp;10224/12800 by 4 temporally staff on 24/08/2023</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-30', '2023-08-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-24 21:31:43', '2023-08-31 15:48:49'),
(681, 19, 14, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-25', '4903', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Status of forest stretch along the electric fence', 'Major', '<p>Security concerns on the forest stretch along the electric fence.&nbsp;</p><p>There has been security concern and the status of the forest along the electric fence both sides.</p><p>Most of the terrorists attacks happens at the bridge which is about 4kms from the site and whenever the terrorists are pursued they take off and hide in the forests along the fence and their footprints found to have crossed into the plantation. with the area cleaned, security will be enhanced and it will be easy for the forces to carry out their patrols and other security related activities.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-26', '2023-08-29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-25 16:08:13', '2023-08-29 18:03:47'),
(682, 9, 14, 9, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-25', '3159', 'Plantation Manager', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'Biological stock records - PMF Melia, nursery stock record and Moringa stock.', 'Major', '<p>Failure to update weekly stock report on time. The stock is supposed to be updated by Thursdays every week and be submitted to accounts before Friday Mid-day. Stock report for Nyongoro Week 34 are yet to be updated on Friday 25/08/2023 at 1:43 Pm.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-30', '2023-08-30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-25 17:44:12', '2023-08-30 17:46:40'),
(683, 18, 10, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-25', '4551', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Head Office Nursery Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Back -end report 21/08/2023, Site results report 21/08/2023', 'Minor', '<p>Missing of watering of seedling beds results in the back-end report for 21/08/2023.</p><p>See the attached.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-28', '2023-08-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-26 00:49:41', '2023-08-31 15:45:53'),
(684, 18, 14, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-25', '2632', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Back-end report 19/08/2023, Site results report 19/08/2023.', 'Minor', '<p>Variation of site &amp; back end results for preventive maintenance that was done on 19/08/2023.</p><p>See the attached.</p>', 'Manager responded', '2023-08-30', '2023-08-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<div>Omitting or inputting wrong figures is unacceptable. A permanent solution will be implemented.</div>', '', '', '2023-08-26 00:59:22', '2023-09-07 16:46:54'),
(685, 18, 15, 9, 8, 18, NULL, '2023-08-25', '3283', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', 'Kiambere', 'Forestry', 'Back-end report 18/08/2023 & 19/08/2023, Site results report 18/08/2023 & 19/08/2023.', 'Minor', '<p>Variation of site &amp; back end results for Manual strip cleaning on 18/08/2023 and watering kei apple on 19/08/2023.</p><p>See the attached.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-08-28', '2023-08-30', '2023-09-08', '2023-09-30', '2023-09-07', NULL, '<div>1. The forest technician shall get a warning.</div>', '<div>The job card is going to highlight all the weaknesses that have not been communicated.</div>', '<div>Sharing of wrong figures is unacceptable as this info is used in decision making .We have our systems in order and we shall continue cleaning&nbsp;</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-08-26 01:10:00', '2023-09-07 18:15:42'),
(686, 38, 26, 8, 8, 38, NULL, '2023-08-28', '3423', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Nursery Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Task rates achievement for potting ', 'Major', '<p>Task rates for potting was not achieved at nursery. Target was achieved 12862/15000 by 10 temporally staff&nbsp;</p>', 'follow up', '2023-08-30', '2023-08-31', '2023-08-31', '2023-09-09', '2023-08-31', 'ok. to be implemented.', '<div>1. There was no proper planning by the site manager.<br>2. Lack of commitment<br>3. Lack of communication.<br>4. The site nursery manager to get a verbal warning as this issue keeps recurring even after addressing it several times.</div>', '<div>Lack of proper planning and poor communication.&nbsp;<br>This should have been communicated immediately and the task rates adjusted on time.</div>', '<div>This shows lack of planning,commitment and communication by the Site nursery manager and its unacceptable.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>Time we address that recurrent lack of willingness to understand, improve and commit to a job well done right first time every time.&nbsp;</div>', '2023-08-28 19:44:20', '2023-08-31 17:53:21'),
(687, 38, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-29', '7521', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Nursery Dokolo', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Melia Azedarach seedling production work instruction-Pricking out.', 'Major', '<p>On 28/8/2023, 4 temporary employees &nbsp;did not have latex gloves while doing pricking out of seedling. This is contrary to the work instruction.</p>', 'Auditee responded', '2023-08-31', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>1. Pre-assments are mandatory before doing an activity. This is a line that shall be added in the projects.<br>2. The site nursery manager got a recorded verbal warning.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>Lack of supervision.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>This shows lack of supervision by the site Nursery manager.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-08-29 14:14:42', '2023-09-07 15:55:54'),
(688, 19, 14, 29, 5, 19, NULL, '2023-08-30', '911', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Tractor canopies', 'Major', '<p>Two tractors have worn out canopies. This allow rain and sun rays to go through ti the operter and the tractor.&nbsp;</p><p>These are canopies for KTCB 530T and KTCB 356V.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-09-01', '2023-09-04', '2023-10-01', '2023-10-07', '2023-09-07', 'Operations to implement', '<div>We shall improvise the canopies by putting a box file Mabati on the roof then monitor.</div>', '<div>A way forward has been advised and it\'s being implemented. Follow-up on the timeframe.</div>', '<div>To be addressed by the operations department.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-08-30 11:38:00', '2023-09-07 18:16:53'),
(689, 38, 10, 8, 8, 18, NULL, '2023-08-31', '8113', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Head Office Nursery Manager', 'Head Office', 'Forestry', 'Forestry & Operations Week 35 plan', 'Minor', '<p>Lack of prospecting the &nbsp;resources needed for implementation of activities.&nbsp;</p><p>On 30/8/2023, 38 temporary employees were supposed to be clocked in for various activities only to realize the site has 35 gumboots on the implementation&nbsp;day.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-09-01', '2023-09-07', '2023-09-07', '2023-09-30', '2023-09-07', NULL, '<div>1. Manage the inputs in the projects. A line for checking the availability of inputs shall be added in the projects.<br>2. The Site Nursery manager already got a recorded verbal warning.</div>', '<div>Proper planning involves ensuring all required items for the activity are available and in good working condition.</div>', '<div>This shows poor planning by the site nursery manager. He got a verbal written warning.<br><br></div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-08-31 13:15:22', '2023-09-07 18:18:11'),
(690, 16, 5, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-08-31', '4675', 'Deputy Director Human Resources', 'Director of Finance & Operations', 'Head Office', 'Operations', 'Nyongoro site theft case', 'Major', '<p>FOD received a directive from MD to report the theft case to the police and the ranch representatives but nothing was done.&nbsp;</p>', 'closed', '2023-09-01', '2023-09-07', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div>This has been addressed.&nbsp;<br>In future all criminal activities shall be reported to the police immediately.&nbsp;<br>FOD to prepare a FC for handling criminal activities.</div>', '<div>The way forward has been advised and will be implemented this week. A flowchart on handling criminal activities to be made</div>', '<div>Already addressed.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-08-31 14:24:35', '2023-09-07 15:40:34'),
(691, 18, 14, 9, 8, 18, NULL, '2023-09-01', '159', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer HO', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Forestry', 'FOR & operation Week 35 plan, Back-end result 29/08/2023.', 'Minor', '<p>Communication breakdown-Vertical.</p><p>The target for Mechanical pruning was not adjusted in the back-end on 29th August 2023 after one PMS failed to report to work. HO PM confirmed that the SLR never communicated for the plan & back-end to be adjusted.</p><p>See the attached.</p>', 'follow up', '2023-09-01', '2023-09-01', '2023-09-07', '2023-09-30', '2023-09-07', NULL, '<div>1. The Site responsible will get a warning because this has recurred many times.&nbsp;</div>', '<div>Will be addressed by DDHR.</div>', '<div>EDF to give us input for the warning.</div>', '<div>OK</div>', '2023-09-01 17:55:39', '2023-09-07 18:13:26'),
(692, 38, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-09-09', '9396', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Seedling Distribution  Report dated 17/7/2023, 18/7/2023 and 19/7/2023', 'Major', '<p>Incorrect partner farmers name. Three farmers namely Otile Nelson misspelt as Toilet Nelson, Obong Geoffrey Kelly misspelt as Oblong Geoffrey, and Obong Simson misspelt as Oblong Simsim. This was observed on week 36 during M &amp;E field Monitoring in Agwata Subcounty&nbsp;</p>', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-09-09 16:06:02', '2023-09-09 16:56:26'),
(693, 38, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-09-09', '414', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer Dokolo', 'Site Manager Dokolo site', 'Dokolo', 'Forestry', 'Seedling Distribution Report dated 17/7/2023, 18/7/2023 and 19/7/2023', 'Major', '<p>Seedling Mortality as a result of poor storage before planting. This was observed during M&amp;E field Monitoring week 36 in Agwata Subcounty.</p><p>Okuja Alfred loss 20 Seedlings, Aceng Hilder 40 Seedlings, Ongom Peter 40 Seedlings&nbsp;</p>', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-09-09 16:19:12', '2023-09-09 16:50:34'),
(694, 19, 14, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-09-12', '537', 'Monitoring & Evaluation Officer Nyongoro', 'Site Logistics Responsible', 'Nyongoro', 'Operations', 'Moringa woodlot', 'Major', '<p>High mortality in moringa plantation.</p><p>800 moringa seedlings were planted in 2020 and only 217 moringa were alive as at 9th September 2023 which is 27.125% survival. This is too low considering that expected servival is 100%.</p><p>Cause for mortality&nbsp;</p><ol><li>1. Attack by pest and diseases which was as a resulted of the trees not being attended to.</li></ol>', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-09-13 00:39:59', '2023-09-13 00:39:59');
