(231, 199, 'The rooms were newly built.', 'Corrective action: To put a proper lock in the changing room', '2022-02-16', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-02 14:19:39', '2022-02-02 14:19:39'),
(232, 204, 'Inconsistency of data e.g administrative boundaries,tree count of a partner farmer in the first correction(verification) and the ongoing correction(Re-verification).', 'To minimize error and collecting the correct partner farmer\'s data at the first time.', '2022-07-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-04 22:55:12', '2022-02-04 22:55:12'),
(233, 206, 'Communication was not done formally to the SLM on lack of water for cleaning activity', 'All communication to be done formally and follow up to be made', '2022-02-11', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-10 14:16:29', '2022-02-10 14:16:29'),
(234, 207, 'The shade net frames are worn out', 'To repair the frame after the budget and plan for 2022 is approved', '2022-04-01', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-10 14:29:06', '2022-02-10 14:29:06'),
(235, 208, 'Repairs were not done for lack of approved budget and labor allocation for nursery', 'Repair of the tunnels to commence once the budget is approved ', '2022-04-01', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-10 14:42:35', '2022-02-10 14:42:35'),
(236, 205, 'Verbal Communication between the SLM & Nursery Team on issues relating to the Nursery.', 'Correction: Water was made available, the nursery has been cleaned and is no longer bushy.\nCorrective Action 1: Use of Official Means of Communication i.e Email Address adopted while conveying information between the SLM& Nursery Team.\nCorrective Action 2: Training was conducted at the HO by the Deputy Director Communication.', '2022-02-18', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-14 17:01:57', '2022-02-14 17:01:57'),
(237, 209, 'land use change and change of ownership of land', 'According to the records, the farmer who cut down more trees is not a BGF farmer. The team is in the process of identifying more farmers with similar cases and make a report.', '2022-02-28', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-14 17:58:58', '2022-02-14 17:58:58'),
(238, 203, 'Late requisition of Fuel by SLM', 'Correction: An IPR 1613 was initiated and approved. Fuel was delivered on site. Site is okay now.\nCorrective Action: Fuel Requests to be made 2 Weeks Prior to completion to allow time for approval.\n', '2022-02-25', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-14 23:14:49', '2022-02-14 23:14:49'),
(239, 211, 'There was no minimum requirements on academic qualification for the position of security.', 'The set minimum requirement for security personnel is to have completed Primary education.', '2022-02-18', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-17 21:32:45', '2022-02-17 21:32:45'),
(240, 211, 'Late approvals of security schedules led to SLM calling them security personnel to notify them of their shifts.', 'To make sure security schedules are always approved on time.', '2022-02-18', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-17 21:37:32', '2022-02-17 21:37:32'),
(241, 211, 'SLM was not keen on the reporting times of security because deductions are automatic', 'OM communicated to the SLM to ensure that security adhere to security schedule', '2022-02-18', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-17 21:41:54', '2022-02-17 21:41:54'),
(242, 210, 'The issuance of PPEs allowed casuals to enter PPE store to pick overalls for themselves.', 'PPE issuance is given from outside. Every worker signs for it when taking and returning.\r\nFT takes stock with the Housekeeper before issuing PPEs for cleaning', '2022-02-22', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-21 15:02:09', '2022-04-07 18:01:08'),
(243, 212, 'Giving Toyota Kenya (Supplier) Orders on short notice. They require time to assemble all spare parts. ', 'OM to give orders early and push the supplier to deliver all required as agreed in good time.\nTo increase physical visits and give feedback on service delivery.', '2022-08-01', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-21 18:27:47', '2022-02-21 18:27:47'),
(244, 214, ' The M&E GIC report to Forestry(EDF) and their employment files are with Human Resource. FOD has nothing to do with this CAR', 'The M&E GIC report to Forestry(EDF) and their employment files are with Human Resource. FOD has nothing to do with this CAR', '2022-02-25', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 21:42:24', '2022-02-25 21:42:24'),
(245, 220, 'Some partner farmers have planted their own trees and the person who is found at the homestead doesn\'t know the trees that were issued by BGF and the ones planted maybe by the husband or wife.', 'To encourage family ownership of the program during group training.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 22:41:58', '2022-02-25 22:41:58'),
(246, 220, 'Some partner farmers with less tree survival takes the agroforestry agent to a different farm which is not her/his in fear of being victimized or ashamed of the low tree survival.', 'To explain the importance of correct tree count in group training hence motivating the farmer to always provide the correct information.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 22:52:59', '2022-02-25 22:52:59'),
(247, 220, 'Mortality between the period when forestry and M&E did the tree count.', 'Monitoring of the tree count verification to be done a week after forestry have done verification.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 22:59:42', '2022-02-25 22:59:42'),
(248, 219, 'Changing of the phone numbers time to time by partner farmers.', 'To always call the number provided by the partner farmer to verify if it\'s correct or not.', '2022-08-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 23:07:13', '2022-02-25 23:07:13'),
(249, 218, 'Inputting less or more digits of the identification number.', 'To always check the identification number of a partner farmer during verification and before submitting reports.', '2022-08-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 23:13:17', '2022-02-25 23:13:17'),
(250, 217, 'The farmers group came into inception in 2018 and the farmers that were contracted in 2015,2016 and 2017 were not informed about being in groups.', 'To encourage the partner farmers to be in group since working with groups  is the way to go.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 23:20:10', '2022-02-25 23:20:10'),
(251, 217, 'Some farmers were contracted after groups have implemented IGAs hence find it difficult to pay registration fees.', 'To encourage short term income generating activities.This will allow contracted non-members farmers to join group when implementing an IGA.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 23:31:00', '2022-02-25 23:31:00'),
(252, 217, 'Internal group conflicts.', 'To sort out internal group conflicts through group  training.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 23:36:44', '2022-02-25 23:36:44'),
