(254, 216, 'Some farmers were contracted after groups have implemented IGAs hence find it difficult to pay registration fees.', 'To encourage short term income generating activities.This will allow contracted non-members farmers to join group when implementing an IGA.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-25 23:43:17', '2022-02-25 23:43:17'),
