(256, 217, 'The area agroforestry agent who was their never issued the hard copy agreement form to respective partner farmers', 'Issuance of the agreement form to partner farmer with the help of the group officials', '2022-08-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-28 17:40:14', '2022-02-28 17:40:14'),
(257, 217, 'Some partner farmers do not remember if they were issued with a copy or not and some misplaced their copy.', 'To photocopy the chief\'s copy and issue to the partner farmers.', '2022-08-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-28 17:52:46', '2022-02-28 17:52:46'),
(258, 217, 'Some partner farmers were contracted both manually and digitally.', 'To print and issue the partner farmers with a copy.', '2022-08-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-02-28 17:56:31', '2022-02-28 17:56:31'),
(259, 220, 'Some partner farmers have planted their own trees and the person who is found at the homestead doesn\'t know the trees that were issued by BGF and the ones planted maybe by the husband or wife.', 'The field team will going forward be clearly communicating and explaining to farmers the importance of tree counting and providing correct information. this will be done through field visits and group leaders', '2022-12-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-03 19:02:40', '2022-03-03 19:02:40'),
(260, 219, 'Changing of the phone numbers time to time by partner farmers', 'We are also collecting phone numbers of the spouses and guardians.', '2023-01-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-03 19:13:45', '2022-03-03 19:13:45'),
(261, 159, 'The requirements are low', 'We have increased the minimum educational qualifications. A security guard must have a class eight certificate.', '2022-03-03', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-03 19:31:53', '2022-03-03 19:31:53'),
(262, 216, 'Some farmers were contracted after groups have implemented IGAs hence find it difficult to pay registration fees.', 'We are going to work with farmers in groups and the farmers not in any group we are going to have them either join existing group or form new group ', '2023-01-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-03 19:33:33', '2022-03-03 19:33:33'),
(263, 204, 'Inconsistency of data e.g administrative boundaries,tree count of a partner farmer in the first correction(verification) and the ongoing correction(Re-verification).', 'The verification report will be shared on a daily basis to the SMFP for quality check as opposed to weekly so that screening of errors is done error to avoid re-verification', '2023-01-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-03 19:42:42', '2022-03-03 19:42:42'),
(264, 196, 'Poor planning and prospecting before allocating the tractors in the compartments', 'Ensure the compartments are manually cleaned one week before the mechanical cleaning exercise ', '2022-03-10', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-03 19:51:13', '2022-03-03 19:51:13'),
(265, 209, 'Land use change and change of ownership of land', 'The field team in the process of verification will be identifying and compiling reports of our farmers with such cases.', '2023-01-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-03 19:51:34', '2022-03-03 19:51:34'),
(266, 217, 'The area agroforestry agent who was their never issued the hard copy agreement form to respective partner farmers', 'We are going to print contracts and issue to those farmers who were never issued with a copy', '2023-01-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-03 19:54:26', '2022-03-03 19:54:26'),
(267, 221, 'Lack of assistant to SLM/SLO at the site.', 'Employ an SLO to assist in operations work at the site.', '2022-05-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-04 20:35:18', '2022-03-04 20:35:18'),
(268, 222, 'There was repair of the nursery fence and the pieces of remaining logs were not removed.', 'Correction: The scattered pieces of logs to be collected and arranged behind the stores.\r\nCorrection action: To always collect the pieces of remaining logs after any activity that involves the use of logs is done.', '2022-04-08', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-07 22:47:42', '2022-03-25 17:31:42'),
(269, 222, 'Continuous dumping of the waste in the site bin without burning hence accumulation of waste to brim.', 'Correction: To burn the waste.\r\nCorrective action: To always assess the site bin on a weekly basis and burn the waste if need be.', '2022-04-08', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-07 22:54:52', '2022-03-25 17:31:42'),
(270, 223, 'There are only 3 staff who can operate the water pump,2 of of them are under forestry.OM and SLM did not foresee and communicate the need to request for assistance from 2 other experienced water pump operators in Nyongoro.', 'To train the mechanic and drivers in operations on how to operate the pump', '2022-03-28', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-10 14:14:26', '2022-03-10 14:14:26'),
(271, 223, 'It is against the HR policy to borrow skilled workers temporarily from their assigned roles unless communicated.', 'To communicate and request for permission to the HR to use workers who have been trained on specific skills when needed. ', '2022-03-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-10 14:20:39', '2022-03-10 14:20:39'),
(272, 226, 'The USSD code was communicated to the teams and put up on the notice board. Their understanding could be a challenge.', 'A Practical demonstration on the use of the USSD shall be done to all the staff.', '2022-03-21', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-10 14:35:42', '2022-03-10 14:35:42'),
(273, 221, 'SLM allocating employees special tasks without prior approval from the HR', 'It was communicated to the SLM he has to stick to the approved policy of seeking approval from HR before assigning an employee any special task. ', '2022-03-15', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-10 20:53:28', '2022-03-10 20:53:28'),
(274, 221, 'SLM overwhelmed by the the various activities under his docket but he has nobody to delegate to.', 'OM to communicate to the HOD need for SLM to have an assistant', '2022-03-16', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-10 21:00:31', '2022-03-10 21:00:31'),
(275, 215, 'The steering committee of GIC had not updated the MOU', '1. The senior director will address it in the next steering committee of GIC.\n2. Their salary shall be raised by 5% and this will be implemented starting January 2022. The changes shall be made on March 2022 salaries.', '2022-03-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-11 17:37:54', '2022-03-11 17:37:54'),
(276, 229, 'The improved seedling production Trial KIA 2021 ,states that measurements of the seedlings in the nursery shall be done once a month which does not specify when it should start.', 'The activity owner will discuss with his supervisor when the baseline measurements of the seedlings should start.', '2022-06-30', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-12 15:59:49', '2022-04-06 21:10:13'),
(277, 227, 'SLM did not communicate the new application to his security', 'Correction: Print the Communication App Notice and pin it on the notice board.\r\nCorrective Action: To always respond to email communication by confirming that the message has received, understood and cascaded to the team whenever a communication has been made.', '2022-03-12', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-14 14:28:36', '2022-04-07 18:07:56'),
(278, 207, 'Inadequate checks on the nursery status.', 'Weekly nursery status report to establish maintenance needs.', '2022-04-01', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-14 14:51:14', '2022-03-14 14:51:14'),
(279, 206, 'Poor horizontal communication on site coupled with lack of follow up.', 'Proper follow up on pending issues and weekly reports on the progress of pending issues which shall be discussed with the supervisors and documented.', '2022-03-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-14 15:12:55', '2022-03-14 15:12:55'),
(280, 199, '1: Inadequate communication on the expectations of the housekeeping chores to the worker assigned.\n2: Poor organization of Ppes issuance activity.', '1: Clear communication of the expectations and target of housekeeping activity.\n2: Ppes to be issued to one worker at a time and recorded, returning of ppes to follow the same, one worker at a time and recording with signs against the issuance.', '2022-03-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-14 15:41:37', '2022-03-14 15:41:37'),
(281, 210, 'Lack of restrictions to access to sensitive areas.', 'Restrictions to access to individuals without approval, those with approval to register upon access.', '2022-03-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-14 15:47:06', '2022-03-14 15:47:06'),
(282, 222, 'Incomplete activity.', 'Activities requiring cleaning after should include the cleaning after in the target.', '2022-03-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-14 15:50:22', '2022-03-14 15:50:22'),
(283, 229, 'Activity done for the first time, some parameters to be set during the project process.', 'Determine the specific time within the month for measurements and include it in the work instruction and schedules.', '2022-03-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-14 15:56:02', '2022-03-14 15:56:02'),
(284, 227, 'SLM had not put emphasizes on the use of the communication app to the team. ', '1.Have the communication app mail pinned on all site notice boards.OM did a mail to all site managers on 7th of March instructing them to have it pinned on the notice board.\n2.A Practical demonstration on the use of the USSD shall be done to all the staff', '0222-03-21', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-15 17:47:54', '2022-03-15 17:47:54'),
(285, 231, 'There was minimum seed loss in nipping & slitting hence excess seeds and all were sown. The FT only recorded 3250 seeds which was required in the experiment in the job cards. ', 'Correction: To record all the seeds sown in SB 3 in the job cards. Proposed corrective action: To always record all seeds sown in the job cards.', '2022-03-23', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-16 13:20:03', '2022-03-16 13:20:03'),
(286, 230, 'The expected seedling germination was not met, still there\'s no communication if there will be another sowing or not hence the soil mixed with the inoculant in SB2 was not removed and used in the multiplication. ', 'The multiplication of the inoculant shall start once communication on whether there will be another sowing or not is done by the HOD.', '2022-03-23', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-16 13:32:33', '2022-03-16 13:32:33'),
(287, 231, 'Extra 210 seeds nipped and slit.', 'Activity owner to give description of the process and related details in remarks section of the jobcards. ', '2022-03-18', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-16 13:53:16', '2022-03-16 13:53:16'),
(288, 215, 'The steering committee of GIC had not updated the MOU', '1. The senior director will address it in the next steering committee of GIC. \n2. Their salary shall be raised by 5% and this will be implemented starting January 2022. The changes shall be made on March 2022 salaries.\n', '2022-03-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-17 12:15:24', '2022-03-17 12:15:24'),
(289, 225, 'A vertical Communication gap between site managers and site staff', 'Correction: To print the instruction of the communication app and put it up on the notice board.\nCorrective action: When a message is passed to site staff, the recipient to confirm receiving, explain to staff on site and they understand and send an email to confirm the actions.', '2022-03-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-17 13:22:23', '2022-03-17 13:22:23'),
(290, 224, 'A vertical communication gap between managers and site staff', 'Correction: To print the instruction of the communication app and put it up on the notice board. Corrective action: When a message is passed to site staff, the recipient to confirm receiving, explain to staff on site and they understand and send an email to confirm the actions.', '2022-03-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-17 13:23:47', '2022-03-17 13:23:47'),
(291, 228, 'Vertical Communication gap ', 'Correction: To put the application procedure up on the notice board and to train security on how to use.\nCorrective action: To always confirm email communication by confirming that you received, understood and disseminated the message to the staff.', '2022-03-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-18 16:11:16', '2022-03-18 16:11:16'),
(292, 232, 'The low germination is because of the fungus attack. There were no treatments against Fungi in SB1 and SB2 . In SB2 , Mycorrhizae could not function within the germination period of Mukau.', 'Correction: Propose carry out sowing to get required seedlings to continue with research.\nCorrective action: To use Fungicide to control fungus in sowing beds', '2022-03-25', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-18 16:50:18', '2022-03-18 16:50:18'),
(293, 241, 'The representative interviewed through a phone call gave M&E her own Id number instead of the partner farmer\'s Id. ', 'The CAR is invalid because the Id number belongs to the representative interviewed. Therefore I request this CAR to be approved then closed. ', '2022-03-18', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-18 21:19:26', '2022-03-18 21:19:26'),
(294, 236, 'Mismatch of a single digit of the identification number. This was as a result of an AA not finding the partner farmer and given  identification number of the partner farmer by the representative.', 'Correction: The SMFP to follow up with the respective partner farmers and update correct identification number.\nProposed corrective action: The AA to always call the partner farmers to get the correct identification number when he/she  gets a representative.', '2022-03-26', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 13:02:41', '2022-03-19 13:02:41'),
(295, 235, 'Mismatch of a single digit of one of the partner farmer\'s phone number. The AA input the old phone number as per the database of the other partner farmer which is incorrect.', 'Correction: The SMFP to follow-up with the respective partner farmers and update the correct phone numbers.\nProposed corrective action: To always input the correct phone number and updating the current phone number of partner farmer.', '2022-03-26', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 13:33:32', '2022-03-19 13:33:32');
INSERT INTO `responses` (`id`, `audit_id`, `cause`, `proposed_solution`, `proposed_date`, `owner`, `progress`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(296, 234, 'Some partner farmers\' contract have not been printed and delivered to the site for issuance.', 'Printing of the contract copies and issuing to the respective partner farmers.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 13:45:06', '2022-03-19 13:45:06'),
(297, 234, 'Some partner farmers misplaced their copies.', 'To photocopy the chief\'s copy and issue to the partner farmers.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 13:50:13', '2022-03-19 13:50:13'),
(298, 237, 'Some partner farmers joined the program before working with groups was introduced in 2018 hence have no idea on BGF farmers group.', 'To encourage the partner farmer to be in group and also highlight the importance of working with groups.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 13:59:28', '2022-03-19 13:59:28'),
(299, 237, 'Some groups have active IGAs thus high membership registration fees which a new member can not afford.', 'To encourage the partner farmers to join other existing groups that are nearby and  have pocket friendly membership registration fees.', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 14:06:57', '2022-03-19 14:06:57'),
(300, 240, '1. 2015 - 2018 farmer recruitments, BGF had not initiated grouping partner farmers. \n\n', 'To sensitize partner farmers on importance of BGF mukau groups. ', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 19:56:33', '2022-03-19 19:56:33'),
(301, 240, 'Social class/not interested partner farmers. ', 'To encourage partner farmers to join existing BGF mukau groups or form new BGF mukau groups. ', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 20:01:13', '2022-03-19 20:01:13'),
(302, 239, '1. Partner farmers Misplaced/forgotten about their hardcopy contracts. ', 'To reprint and issue the hardcopy contracts to partner farmers. ', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 20:11:09', '2022-03-19 20:11:09'),
(303, 239, '2. Partner farmers who were not issued with hard copy contracts. ', 'To print and issue hardcopy contracts to partner farmers. ', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 20:15:54', '2022-03-19 20:15:54'),
(304, 239, '3. Issuing of hardcopy contracts to partner farmers. ', 'To have a good procedure on how to issue hardcopy contracts to partner farmers. ', '2022-12-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-19 20:29:31', '2022-03-19 20:29:31'),
(305, 238, 'Divorced/not around  partner farmers and those that have zero survival. ', 'Whenever the partner farmers name is in the forestry week plans, whether divorced or with zero survival he or she must be visited. ', '2022-04-01', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2022-03-22 15:23:22', '2022-03-22 15:23:22'),
(306, 232, 'Fungal attack: signs of fungal attack observed.\nTree no. 269 was sown in 2 beds, one with fungicide and another without fungicide. Seeds (of same tree number 269) sown with fungicide had 40% germination while those sowed without fungicide had 12% germination. ', '1. Fumigation of the sowing area before production to reduce fungal attack.\n2. Trial production with a small sample (100 or 200 seeds) before actual production to check and correct potential threats which might affect the germination.\n', '2022-03-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-22 16:37:31', '2022-03-22 16:37:31'),
(307, 230, 'Low germination in the first sowing.\n A second sowing proposed to get enough seedlings to fill all the treatments of the trial. ', 'Specification of time period of multiplication after production considering all factors such as continued propagation. \n', '2022-03-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-22 17:07:50', '2022-03-22 17:07:50'),
(308, 234, 'Some partner farmers\' contract have not been printed and delivered to the site for issuance.', 'For the farmers who have never received contracts, their contracts are going to be generated, printed and issued to them', '2022-12-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2022-03-23 13:18:14', '2022-03-23 13:18:14'),
