(796, 538, 'Staff fear to misplace their documents.', 'Communication on the need for every staff to have their IDs with them has been communicated to the staff severally by the SMP, SMN , M&EO and SLO.\nHowever, the checking of IDs is in the security Docket under Operations Department hence the SMN declines the CAR.', '2023-02-02', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-02 03:49:15', '2023-02-02 03:49:15'),
(797, 539, 'The corrective action request(3962) had been identified and the correction is currently being done.', 'The M&E was enlightened on the compartment condition and she is aware of the correction which is currently taking place.\n\nThe FT also visited the compartment during M&E stock verification to ensure there is no confusion during the exercise.', '2023-02-09', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-02 13:53:21', '2023-02-02 13:53:21'),
(798, 536, 'As IAM was transferring documents and Data from my old laptop to the new one,  I had oversight and requested email passwords via email instead of sending a ticket and copied the wrong Alex.', 'Correction: The Moment I realized this, I immediately phoned ISO and informed him of my mistake.\nCorrective action: To always raise a ticket when having system issues.', '2023-02-02', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-02 15:17:03', '2023-02-02 15:17:03'),
(799, 538, 'Staff not following instructions and lack of follow up by site  by managers (SMP, SMN & SLM) to ensure compliance. ', 'Staff to produce IDs at the site entry always and have them while on site, site managers to ensure compliance. ', '2023-02-02', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-02-02 15:58:36', '2023-02-02 15:58:36'),
(800, 533, '1.	The site manager/FT not taking responsibility of inputting results themselves.2.	Site manager/FT not verifying results from the field before inputting in the back office.3.	The head office manager not ensuring the above happens.', '	The head office manager must follow up daily to ensure the site managers have input correct results.\n\n', '2023-02-02', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-02 17:13:22', '2023-02-02 17:13:22'),
(801, 539, 'Initial lack of supervision during the rows marking activity. Poor planning leading to delayed implementation of re-marking activity which is also related to another CAR on rows marking.', 'FT and PM to coordinate and do an audit of all compartments boundaries, rows, beacons and planting years marks. Correct all arising errors schedule for repainting and document the 4 activities under tree counting documents.', '2023-02-28', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-02-03 14:13:04', '2023-02-03 14:13:04'),
