(803, 540, 'It rained on 1st October 2022 and the Crocodile cage was washed away by floods and got submerged. The occurrence was reported and documented in the digital occurrence book by the security guard who was on night shift. The team has been searching but due to the water levels it was impossible to find it until recently when the water level reduced.', 'Correction: The crocodile cage was retrieved back to site.\nCorrective action: Storage of the crocodile cage at the site during rainy season.', '2023-02-13', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-06 21:51:09', '2023-02-06 21:51:09');
