(805, 532, 'On the said dates the SLM had meetings the whole day hence could not manage to fill the schedules timely.\n', 'A list indicating what machines goes to daily and which ones shall go to weekly to be done and shared for approval.\nNote: This CAR was raised before the SLM went on leave.', '2023-02-15', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-10 13:17:50', '2023-02-10 13:17:50'),
(806, 532, 'Failure by SLM to comply to daily booking of machines in the maintenance app', 'SLM to ensure booking of machines is done on a daily basis as required and by any chance if he is not in a position to do so communication to be done in advance to all the relevant parties.', '2023-02-11', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-02-10 16:05:20', '2023-02-10 16:05:20'),
(807, 549, 'Faulty switch of brush cutter.', 'Correction \nThe issue was communicated and repair was done and it took less than one hour to repair the machine. However, the task rate was affected.', '2023-02-13', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-14 01:00:15', '2023-02-14 01:00:15'),
(808, 536, 'Even when it\'s an emergency, the right channels still have to be followed. ', 'Always make a ticket first and you can follow it up with an email or a phone call.', '2023-01-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-02-14 13:45:05', '2023-02-14 13:45:05'),
(809, 527, 'Lack of follow-up on the changes to the objectives by staff and Supervisors', 'Quarterly or mid-year reviews should be conducted to ensure any major changes have been updated', '2023-12-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-02-14 13:54:55', '2023-02-14 13:54:55'),
(810, 550, 'Most of the items expired late 2023 and the report was to be shared to OM for approval.', 'The list of expired items was shared to OM on 3/2/2023 for approval. The list was approved and shared with the supply  who is yet to provide the quotation.', '2023-03-15', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-15 03:13:13', '2023-02-15 03:13:13'),
(811, 549, 'Lack of communication of the breakdown to adjust task rate.\nIdentical to CARs 2576 which is under follow up.', 'Immediate communication of breakdowns to adjust task rate or change activity.', '2023-02-15', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-02-15 14:17:29', '2023-02-15 14:17:29'),
(812, 551, 'IPR 2357 was raised on 13th Feb, 2023 but pending for approval.', 'Correction: SMFP to make sure that drinking water is always available.\nPrior assessment should be done and initiate an IPR before the drinking water is depleted.', '2023-02-24', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-19 00:59:05', '2023-02-19 00:59:05'),
(813, 552, 'Pending of motorbikes in the system.', 'Correction: SMFP to check if all motorbikes are in the system for booking.\n\nThere is need for alignment of the system to ensure all machines are not pending for booking.', '2023-02-24', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-19 01:05:41', '2023-02-19 01:05:41'),
(814, 556, 'Negligence by the security guards on site. The security guards have been informed on use of a polished boots while on site. After confrontation by M&E, Mathew Munyoki  went and changed to his boots.', 'Correction: The FT to emphasize on use of the right PPE at work during security meetings.\n\nCorrective Action: To follow up with OM to allow the guards to use gumboots while in the field since the guards prefer gumboots to boots due to long sharp grass \'\'Unyoe\" which pierces through the PPE.', '2023-03-01', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-23 15:33:10', '2023-02-23 15:33:10'),
(815, 555, 'The available hand leather gloves are worn out.', 'Correction: To fast track delivery of already purchased gloves from head office with procurement officer.\n\nCorrective Action: To always ensure the right PPE are available on site.', '2023-03-01', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-23 15:44:17', '2023-02-23 15:44:17'),
(816, 554, 'Lack of a store for keeping personal items for PMS during working hours.', 'To construct a structure for storing personal items once the staff have changed to their PPEs.', '2023-04-22', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-23 15:50:02', '2023-02-23 15:50:02'),
(817, 553, 'The tap fitting loosen due to disturbance during fetching of water over the week for watering Kei Apple and the water used for house keeping.\n', 'To create a watering systemin the nursery which leads to a permanent water tap for fetching water for use on site instead of connecting pipes every now and then.', '2023-03-23', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-02-23 15:58:36', '2023-02-23 15:58:36'),
