(821, 551, 'Frequent visit by AAs in the office during motorbike assessment, repairs and training interfered with the reorder level.', 'SMFP to monitor the reorder levels frequently and incase of any change of plans raise IPRs in advance in cater for that .', '2023-02-24', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-02-23 18:11:44', '2023-02-23 18:11:44'),
(822, 556, 'Failure by security team to comply to PPE policy', 'FT and OM to emphasize to the guards to adhere to the PPE policy. All guards are supposed to be on full security uniform at all times when on duty including security boots. Gumboots are only supposed to be used when we have heavy rains.', '2023-03-01', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-02-27 16:14:26', '2023-02-27 16:14:26'),
