(962, 613, 'Reject were not identify during first loading of the seedlings that why there was no report for the reject, but the second loading and distribution of the seedlings there was 250 rejects that were identified this was due to root rot that was discovered during the exercise and also some road in Kitui county were not in good condition. Some seedlings were out of the pots as a results of the commotion and detachment of soil. ', 'Sorting to be done immediately before loading to identify the reject and also during distribution the drivers should be careful, report on what has been distributed and reject to be shared daily and updated', '2023-04-21', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-04-17 13:05:18', '2023-04-17 13:05:18'),
