(1085, 664, 'Delay in EIA approvals by NEMA', 'To make EIAs that cover a longer period than two years. It should follow the management plan for a period of 5 years.', '2023-07-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 12:24:23', '2023-07-18 12:24:23'),
(1086, 667, '1. This is simply negligence and lack of following instructions knowingly. ', '1. The system has now been restricted such that a phone number or an ID number if already existing in the system cannot be repeated.', '2023-07-07', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 12:33:33', '2023-07-18 12:33:33'),
(1087, 672, 'Environmental conditions and dbh increase causing the marks to fade or get distorted.', 'Prospection to maintain tree monitoring pre-requisites (rows and boundaries marks) before tree counting is conducted.', '2023-07-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 12:36:22', '2023-07-18 12:36:22'),
(1088, 663, 'Delay in EIA approval by NEMA', 'To make EIAs that cover a longer period that matches the managment plans. ', '2023-07-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 12:36:31', '2023-07-18 12:36:31'),
(1089, 649, '1. The GPS coordinate system was network-based.', '1. This was corrected. Now the coordinates can be taken in offline mode.', '2023-07-14', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 12:44:33', '2023-07-18 12:44:33'),
(1090, 650, '1. Different systems for proof of land ownwership', '1. FSc recognises that small holder farmers own land but do not necessarilly have land titles with maps done professionally. Sketch maps showing clear bounderies are acceptable. Chiefs letter supporting ownership is acceptable too. ', '2023-07-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 12:58:26', '2023-07-18 12:58:26'),
(1091, 655, '1. There are records of disputes but are not recorded in a register.', '1. Digital register of disputes', '2023-08-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 13:16:39', '2023-07-18 13:16:39'),
(1092, 661, '1. Prior management practices were not based on the FSC principles', '1. Completion of the management plans based on the FSC guidelines. This for both the plantations and the Farmers. ', '2023-07-28', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 13:35:58', '2023-07-18 13:35:58'),
(1093, 659, '1. Management plans have not been previously done. The drafts had not strictly followed the FSC requirements. For the farmers the management plan had been done but there was minimal involvement of the farmer which is a requirement.', '1. Making the managemnt plans following guidelines of FSc. \n2.  Involvement of the farmers in developing their MGT plans', '2023-07-28', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 13:39:51', '2023-07-18 13:39:51'),
(1094, 657, '1. the previous draft had not considered all the FSC requirements and therefore this must be redone.', '1. Check existing plans and provide guidance for addressing all FSC requirements by the FSC intern.', '2023-07-21', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 13:49:31', '2023-07-18 13:49:31'),
(1095, 653, '1.This has not been taken as an important issue in the managent of the plantations in the previous years. The management of the plantations was not based on the FSc principles. ', '1. Make a poster and esplay publicly in our management units.\n2. Add the policy in the management plans', '2023-07-21', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-18 14:01:36', '2023-07-18 14:01:36'),
(1096, 673, 'Procrastination\nThe thought that the breakdown was minor and can be repaired within few minutes. ', 'Correction \nMachine was repaired.\nCorrective Action \nImmediate communication whenever breakdowns occur.', '2023-07-22', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-07-22 13:53:08', '2023-07-22 13:53:08'),
(1097, 674, 'The initial plan was to have a permanent sowing area of (43×17)M2 including metallic tunnels.\nThe plan was approved and the production was to commence immediately so we had to construct a temporary structure having the dimensions of (20×8)M2 to accommodate both sowing and bricking area.', 'To construct a permanent sowing structure.', '2023-10-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-07-22 16:26:17', '2023-07-22 16:26:17'),
(1098, 673, 'Communication breakdown-Failure by PMS to communicate machine breakdown immediately.', 'Emphasize to be done to the PMS that any breakdown is supposed to be communicated immediately whether minor or major.', '2023-07-24', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-23 18:15:27', '2023-07-23 18:15:27'),
(1099, 674, 'Change of plan to do temporary structure instead of the metallic structure in the plan.', '1. Good planning- Preparations and structures to be done on time not waiting for the last minute. \n2. Construct a permanent sowing area', '2023-08-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-07-25 23:39:42', '2023-07-25 23:39:42'),
(1100, 675, 'The main supplier delayed in delivering the drinking water.', 'A different supplier was engaged and delivered 800 litres on 09/08/2023.To source for a reliable supplier.', '2023-08-23', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-09 20:06:05', '2023-08-09 20:11:47'),
(1101, 675, 'Power outrage at the main waterbody in Mwingi town.', 'Correction: A local supplier was engaged and delivered 800 liters on 09/08/2023. Mwingi water body delivered 10,000 ltrs on 14/8/2023\nCorrective action:  Get a reservoir tank. A water platform is under construction after which we will purchase a 10,000 ltr tank for drinking water and the existing 5,000llrs tank will be used as reservoir.', '2023-08-23', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-16 00:20:48', '2023-08-16 00:20:48'),
(1102, 676, 'Machines are subject to breakdowns when in use. However, emphasis to avoid breakdowns has been put to operators.', '1.To stock spareparts e.g carburettors, spark plugs, chains, nuts and bolts since they are the ones that frequently break down.\r\n2. To have qualified mechanic to do proper diagnosis and repair the machines.\r\n3. Train operators on minor repairs.\r\n4. Specify duration in which machines shall be replaced or be written off.\r\n5. Assign specific machines to operators for accountability.', '2023-12-30', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-26 15:33:02', '2023-08-26 15:34:09'),
(1103, 681, 'Cleaning of the forest stretch in the CAR was never planned for.', 'Cleaning this stretch to be done upon decisions made by management.', '2023-12-30', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-26 16:01:31', '2023-08-26 16:01:31'),
(1104, 678, 'Seedlings got stressed after sorting out on 19th August 2023.The seedlings withered and failed to sprout.', 'Correction: the seedlings which had withered were taken through a special treatment by watering and adding NPK fertilizer to boost their growth.', '2023-10-31', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-28 12:44:09', '2023-08-28 12:44:09'),
(1105, 677, 'In the GIC production plan for 2023,the germination percentage planned for was above 50%.This is because the staff who were to be used in the production process have not specialized in nursery production, a lot of losses were recorded in nipping and slitting.', 'The team to get a well trained staff who will be engaged in nursery production throughout instead of relying on the PMS.', '2023-11-28', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-28 12:50:05', '2023-08-28 12:50:05'),
(1106, 685, 'Wrong update of achieved results. The results uploaded in the device was the target instead of the actual results.', 'FT to be  very keen while updating the results in the kit and to double-check after synchronizing the device. ', '2023-09-04', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-28 12:54:06', '2023-08-28 12:54:06'),
(1107, 683, 'The FT nursery was not keen while uploading the site results hence skipped the activity.', 'Daily check of uploaded site results and back end monitoring by the acting Site Manager.', '2023-09-02', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-28 18:55:15', '2023-08-28 18:55:15'),
(1108, 679, 'During planning, the previous task rate were used to calculate the man-days required for various activities. However, on implementation, measurements was done for these  activities and new task rate was proposed. The plan was adjusted and communicated. ', '1. Refresher training before implementation of an activity. 2. To have permanent nursery employees.', '2023-09-28', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-28 19:16:46', '2023-08-28 19:16:46'),
(1109, 681, 'Cleaning of that area was not planned. Our plan along the electric fence was to clean 1 meter inside and 1 meter outside which we have complied.  ', 'Do prospection of the area, present it for approval, and plan for its cleaning to improve security.', '2023-09-30', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-29 18:03:38', '2023-08-29 18:03:38'),
(1110, 676, 'Lack of proper maintenance', 'Correction-Operators manual shared with the SLR to guide him, the handyman involved in repairs, and the operators.\nCorrective action: Continous training of the operators on proper handling and usage of the machines and allocating each machine to specific operators for accountability.', '2023-09-16', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-29 19:05:33', '2023-08-29 19:05:33'),
(1111, 680, 'The seedlings in the sowing beds were not well established for Pricking ', 'Pricking were possed for 3 days that week to give time for seedlings to fully established', '2023-08-28', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 12:14:11', '2023-08-30 12:14:11'),
(1112, 686, 'The target for potting was too high for the new inexperienced casual ', 'Task rates for potting for new inexperienced casual should be measured per hour ', '2023-09-30', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 12:26:43', '2023-08-30 12:26:43'),
(1113, 685, 'Lack of full concentration on the task at hand. The FT performs this task daily and such errors are not expected from him.', 'Currently the results are uploaded first, and a screenshot of results on the hard copy shared later. \nCorrective action - Sharing 2 screenshots simultaneously (1 of uploaded results on the device screen and 1 for hard copy book on site).', '2023-09-02', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 13:40:03', '2023-08-30 13:40:03'),
(1114, 684, 'Result for Rashid erroneously omitted during upload', 'Emphasis on keenness  during result uploading to avoid occurrence of the same error.\n', '2023-08-30', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 14:32:46', '2023-08-30 14:32:46'),
(1115, 682, 'Tree raw data confirmation and verification.\nVerification done on Friday by noon therefore delayed update.\n', 'Communication to PM whenever there is delay in update.', '2023-08-30', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 14:43:11', '2023-08-30 14:43:11'),
(1116, 677, 'Planning based on previous germination %.', 'Experiments for improving germination %. Then a minimum germination % requirement set for all production.', '2023-09-30', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 17:26:46', '2023-08-30 17:26:46'),
(1117, 682, 'Negligence. Communication and follow up had been done on the submission of the report before the CAR was raised. ', 'Escalation to HR if the same keeps on recurring. ', '2023-08-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 17:45:39', '2023-08-30 17:45:39'),
(1118, 678, 'Poor handling causing shock during acclimatization. ', 'Increased supervision throughout especially when there is movement of seedlings during pricking out and sorting out.', '2023-09-15', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 18:05:20', '2023-08-30 18:05:20'),
(1119, 679, 'Lack of experience by pms on production activities especially cracking, nipping and slitting and pricking out resulting in reduced task rates as opposed to the plan.', 'Continuous training to a number of pms to be assigned seedlings production activities whenever they are planned. Training can be done with experimental production. ', '2023-09-30', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-30 18:13:01', '2023-08-30 18:13:01'),
(1120, 686, 'Task rates were not changed based on circumstances. ', '1. Task rates are dynamic and can be changed according to circumstances. It is known that new workers cannot achieve task rates of experienced workers.\n2. Use individual task rates instead of group task rates because a team sometimes has experience and new personnel. ', '2023-09-01', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-31 15:42:05', '2023-08-31 15:42:05'),
(1121, 683, 'Lack of taking responsibility and checking by the site manager  to ensure all results have been uploaded.', '1. The (Acting) site manager must check the results from the nursery, verify and input them personnaly in the device.', '2023-08-28', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-31 15:45:48', '2023-08-31 15:45:48'),
(1122, 680, 'Pre-assessment was not done before planning. ', '1. Mandatory task of pre-assessment in the nursery of the work that needs to be done like we do in the plantations. ', '2023-08-30', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-31 15:48:44', '2023-08-31 15:48:44'),
(1123, 684, 'Wrong entry by the SLR', 'SLR to be very keen while uploading the results.', '2023-08-31', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-08-31 15:57:12', '2023-08-31 15:57:12'),
(1124, 687, 'The mode of application used', 'Leaf surface mode of application to be use when pricking in is done', '2023-09-30', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-08-31 17:01:25', '2023-08-31 17:03:30'),
(1125, 689, 'No oversight of the available PPE during planning.', 'To always plan activities based on the available PPE on site.', '2023-09-04', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-09-01 15:33:16', '2023-09-01 15:33:16'),
(1126, 688, 'Ware and tear.', 'Procure new metallic canopies for the tractors. \nIPR #2912 was raised.', '2023-09-30', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-09-01 17:25:36', '2023-09-01 17:25:36'),
(1127, 691, 'There was no communication breakdown.', 'This was communicated to HO PM through phone call on 29/08/2023 and communication was to have the plans changed.', '2023-09-01', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-09-01 20:01:40', '2023-09-01 20:01:40'),
(1128, 691, 'Communication breakdown. On this date there was no communication from the SLR as all other instances whenever there is communication the tasks are adjusted in the backend.', 'Email communication on any absenteeism and respective plan changes coupled with a call to adjust plan before clocking in workers in the morning.', '2023-09-05', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-09-01 20:43:04', '2023-09-01 20:43:04'),
(1129, 690, 'The directive was to report when the culprits are dismissed. These culprits are not yet dismissed.\nIn addition, this was to be addressed from HR perspective.\n', 'However we have agreed in future when such occurrence happens, this will be immediately be reported to the police and the ranch chairman.\n\n', '2023-09-04', 'auditee', 'ongoing', '2023-09-01 20:51:19', '2023-09-01 20:51:19'),
(1130, 688, 'Wear and tear', '1. Proper utilization of the maintenance app which will help in monitoring the condition of the tractors.\n2. Fast-track purchase of the canopies ', '2023-09-30', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-09-04 21:05:19', '2023-09-04 21:05:19'),
(1131, 690, 'Communication breakdown- Incident not recorded in the OB.', 'OM to sensitize the security team on reporting all happenings in the OB. The OB could have helped when reporting to the police.', '2023-09-07', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-09-07 13:51:50', '2023-09-07 13:51:50'),
(1132, 689, 'Poor Planning', 'The planning did not incorporate pre-assessment. This shall be mandatory even for the nursery activities.', '2023-09-06', 'HOD', 'ongoing', '2023-09-07 14:42:13', '2023-09-07 14:42:13');
